Item_Response: It was in the beginning of summer that Mr. Levy decided to create a robot. He had always wanted to make a robot since he was a little kid. So now he has a chance to. Mr. Levy is graduate from the University of California (Cal). He planned making a robot with his best friends Mia, Ben, and Dylan. So now here he is in his lab working with his a friends, who are now his assisitants.             The first thing they needed to do was to buy all the other tools they needed and materials. Then, they went back to their lab and got everything ready. 'Do you think we need anything else?', Mr. Levy asked Ben. 'No I don't think so', Ben replied. When they were done getting everything ready they began building the robot. Mr. Levy was very exicited on making his first robot in his life. 'I'm going to need you to get that piece over there', Mr. Levy said as he pointed it out to Dylan. While Dylan was getting the piece Mia came up with an idea. 'What if we add something to the robot that could make it fly, right here', Mia said as she pointed at the blueprints that were next to Ben. Mr. Levy thought for a second and then said, 'That is a great idea, but we don't have the certain parts to build something like that, unless if you want to order the parts from online', Mr. Levy said. 'I will be glad to', Mia said. Then, Dylan came back as soon as Mia left to her office. When Dylan handed Mr. Levy the part he asked for, he said, 'Where is Mia going.' 'She thought of an idea, that we should build something to make our robot fly, and so she is going to her computer to order the parts', Ben said. The four friends worked on the robot until got it got dark. 'I think it's time to take rest you guys', Mr. Levy said. 'Ok', all of the other friends said. And then each of them went home.               The next day Mr. Levy was the first person there to the lab. While he waited for the rest of his friends, he started working on the robot. About 20 minutes later all Mia, Dylan, and Ben came. They all said, 'Sorry that were a little late.' 'It's okay', said Mr. Levy. Then they all got to work. 'Oh, I forgot to tell you that the parts we need to make the robot fly will becoming in tomorrow at 2:00 p.m.' 'Okay, we will be done with this robot probably the day after tommorrow because we got a quarter of it done yesterday. So if work really hard today we could probably finish half of it.' So all four friends got to work. While Mr. Levy and Mia worked on the robot. Dylan and Ben worked on how they were going to fit the things to make the robot fly into the robot. Later on, when they figured out how to Ben told Mr. Levy, 'We finished the blueprints, would you like to see them?' 'Yes', Mr. Levy answered. While Mr. Levy was looking and the blueprints with Ben, Dylan went over to help Mia with the robot. Then once you know it they were all working on the robot as a team. If you there watching them you would things like 'pass me the screwdriver' or 'hand me that piece over there right next to you' and 'no not that piece the other one'. They worked so hard that that they did finish half of the robot just like Mr. Levy said. So then they all went back home to rest.               On the next day this time it was Mia who got their first. While she waited for the others to come she called the people who were going to bring the pieces she ordered. Right when she finished the call all the others came. Then like yesterday they worked as a team. 'Today we would work on the robots feet because the parts to make the robot fly are coming in today. Right Mia.' 'Yes, I just called them and they said that they parts are ready and that they are coming in today at 1:00 instead of at 2:00', Mia said with a little exicitement in her voice. 'Alright, Ben can you go get those two pieces that are over there, those pieces are the main ones for the feet.' While Ben was getting the pieces they needed, the others started working on the robot. Then when Ben came back they were half-ways done with the feet. Right when they were done connected everything, they heard a knock. Mia said, 'I got it', and ran to the door. When she opened the door a man stood there with two boxes in his hands. The man handed the boxes to Mia. Then she said, 'Thank you', and went back inside the lab. When she got inside the lab all the others crowded around Mia as she opened the box. 'Wow', Dylan said amazed. Then they all went back to were the robot was at, and started putting all the new pieces were they belonged. 'So when we finish you and Dylan should go outside and test the feet', Mr. Levy said to Ben. Then Dylan and Ben both nodded at the same time.               On next day they were going to finish to finish there robot. So yesterday when they finished with feet Dylan and Ben went outside to test them. When they came back inside the lab they had said it worked. Now they only need the head and then they are done. Today all of the four friends got their at the same time. Mia told everybody, 'Good morning', as they entered the lab. As soon as they got to the robot they started working. 'So today were going to finish this robot', Mr. Levy said. Then each of them started to work ton their part of the body that Mr. Levy each gave them. They worked really hard. 'I finished my part', Dylan said. Then it was Ben who finished, then it was Mia, and last but not least was Mr. Levy. As a team they connected all their parts, and then they connected everything together. Then all of a sudden as they were putting some kind of battery into the robot an alrm went off. Which meant that there was a fire. So they put all the batteries in the robot really fast, but as soon as they finished the fire burst out. Mr. Levy said, 'Let's all get out of here.' Right when they got out of the building the whole thing collapsed. Then somehow the fire department came to clear the fire and to check if they were all okay. When they were checking if they were all okay they found a big cut on Dylan leg from a big piece of glass. While they were fixing Dylan up, each of them were really because they made a robot that is no crushed in that building. But then a firefighter came to them and said, 'I think we found something that's moving.' Then they all knew who was that moving thing in the building. There robot.

Item_Response: On the planet of Saturn there is a small robot named Carol. She is a robot that was built to collect research on Saturn. She is a little less than three feet tall, and can climb and steer herself over any bump in the road. She is a very smart robot that is programmed to take pictures of Saturn, and once she takes a picture it gets sent immediatley to the scientists in the lab on Earth.          Carol comes across a moving shadow while riding over craters. Carol is very smart and she at once senses danger. She turns around and sees a black blob in her path. She quickly takes a picture, and the scientists see it and worry about Carol. The black blob with squinty eyes jumps on Carol and the connection between Carol and the scientists breaks down. The scientists try all they can, but they cant find Carol.           Meanwhile, Carol is face to face with the blob and the blob is trying to figure out what he just stumbled upon. Carol is smart and of course does not fear, but when the blob spoke to her that was a surprise. Luckily Carol could speak as well because she was taught thousands of different phrases in case she did come across life on this planet. She spoke to it and said she came in peace. The blob looked confused, but just as scary. The black blob spoke to it with respect and asked if Carol would be the queen of his planet. She didn't answer and that made him angry. He jumped on her again, and somehow she reconnected with the scientists on earth.               The scientists told her what to do, and she followed the orders. She outwitted the blob and escaped him, and the scientists were glad to see that they never came across the blob again. The guessed that since he was out witted by a three foot robot he was embarrassed to show his face, so the scientists guessed that he hid forever.              Carol returned to Earth, and there wasn't a soul on Earth who had never heard about Carol's exciting adventure on Saturn.

Item_Response: The Recycling Robot                    One day while a girl named Sophia was taking the cans and paper to get recycled she found a what looked like a drawing of a robot. That gave Sophia an idea, Sophia decided to invent a robot that would help keep the world a clean place. She recycled the trash and ran home. Sophia asked her dad Bob if he could take her to his work and get some car parts. Bob said 'Yes.' and he drove her to the car shop. Sophia was looking for different types of  car parts such as a engine.          Once her dad said it was time to go they got in the car and drove home. Sophia was kind of a genius so she went in the garage and started building her robot. It took a couple of months for her to finish building it, especially with school. Finally the day came when she finished her robot and she took her robot to the park, because that seemed to be in need of a good cleaning.         Sophia carefully turned the robot on and then slowly drove it over to a candy wrapper. The robot sensed that there was garbage and picked it up and rode over to the trash can. Sophia was so happy and after a couple of years the town won a medal for the cleanest town, not only did the town win a medal so did Sophia for inventing such a terrific robot that helped the town look clean.           Sophia was so happy with herself and the school was proud of her to. From then on Sophia lived a clean and happy life.

Item_Response: Feline Flyer          I made this robot named Feline Flyer. I made it because there's a lot of stories about dogs running away, drowning or getting shot. Same with cats or other house pets. So my robot Feline Flyer does all sorts of things. He can sense if animals are hurt or scared. He also can fly very fast. He has medicine,food,water,casts,and more packed when he is on a mission which is all the time.         Feline Flyer has 6 legs, he looks like a bird but way bigger. He weighs about 350. He can carry around 250. he charges for 3 hours and can work for 48 hours.When he flies he goes about 250 mph even if its around the world. He has never broke or even got injured.He is water proof so he can swim.         His worse mission was when a dog was stuck in a volcano. He had to go about 150 miles till he found the dog. The dog was very hurt. When he rescued him he founds out he had a vest on and it was a service dog . After a couple months it was recovered so they put the dog on the internet 3 months went by nobody claimed it so I decided Feline Flyer can have him a body. I named the dog spark. But don't worry because he doesn't get to go with Feline Flyer when he is on missions . But when he isn't busy on missions they love playing with each other.

Item_Response: 2012                               In the middle of the year 2012, a meteor hit the earth. '...Many died, but thousands survived because of ROBOTS a- woah, woah, woah, oh god ,what is that! Is that another, wait the aaahhhhh ,NNNNNNNNNNNOOOOOOOOOOOOO!'                                        24 hours before...                                                     ' Well goooooood morning New York! It's a good day to be alive isnt it!' , said the talk show host from Buenos Dias NYC.  Hi, I'm Johnny Dover.I was sitting on the couch with my robotic dog, Spiky.Anyways, while I watched the show they said ,' Excuse us for the interruption, but please listen to the words of our leader.' Obama, the president, came up on the screen, ' We have just discovered from NASA that there will be a meteor hitting the Earth at approximately 8:00 pm. Calling all army soldiers to go to your nearest database. Everyone stay calm and have faith. Thank You.'                                                                      I put on my equipment and headed out in my Google car. It was like a family reunion seeing all my colleagues again. Joe, Bob, Tony, Richard, and Peter. The general began to speak before I could say a thing to my buds.' I have loved working with all of you on many fights and struggles, so let's make this one worth it!'                                                    7:30 pm                                       You could see the meteor coming fast we all said our goodbyes and we could save the world. Some were worried about their families. 'WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN!' , yelled a soldier.                                                          7:59:58                                           I felt the impact from miles away. It was so big and green. Little and big aliens began to rampage from the rock.   Every robot ever created sprang into action. Before we knew it , it was all over. We were reported that it landed in central park killing lots of people. The talkshow host was killed by one of the aliens in his studio.                                              The robots were extrordinary. Since that very day all robots have been appriciated. We still all care for them and play with them, even me. Those things saved lives and they still do. Now I've become one of them.                                                Brandon Segura

Item_Response: The Robot that Came Alive           Hi, my name is Robi Bautista. It is the year 2060. This is my replica robot R2D2. I built this robot last year. It took me thousands of Muggle money to build this. I live in Zedov on Earth.       My robot has bionic parts in it and is controlled by the mind. It has a tiny microchip in it's arm. It is voice activated, but it won't work.       'Uh oh,' I said.       'There is a electric storm outside,' I said.       'I better go in,'' I said.       'Oh no,' I yelled.       'R2d2 is outside,' I yelled again and again.       The next day the storm has passed.       ' Where did R2D2 go,' I said?       ' I think R2D2 came alive,' my assistant said.       ' He is,' I said.       There he is walking over the pool.       'Maybe the lightning triggered him to move by himself,' I said.       'Maybe the voice activated chip still works,' my assistant said.       I said,' Stop.       ' Look it worked,' I said.                                                                                             Epilogue:           After a few months of repairing, making control robots, and making improvements to R2D2. R2D2 is now a search and rescue robot                                                             The End

Item_Response: Dreams Can Come True                     In the beginning I believed much in robots. I always wanted to see one in person or maybe even try to make one. I, to be exact would like to invent the most coolest robot EVER! It would be fun, but if everything comes out wrong. The creation would be ruined and nobody would appreciate my horrible work.                  Fist of all my name is Kimberly Marquez. I enjoyed everything about robots, their figure, the size, and everything else of it. I wanted to build a robot, so I asked my friends to help me out. It was one sunny Saturday my friends and I were coming up with what my robot was going to be like . 'My robot is going to look just like a normal person, but can turn small into a computer ' I told them. They agreed and gathered a lot of materials to start building.                  We stayed up almost all night trying to work out our invention. It was 10:30 p.m. my friends stayed for a sleep over to start right in the morning. Starting tomorrow we needed to have at least half of the robot done. We worked and worked on it, but we just couldn't understand what to do first. It was 7:00 a.m. There was a morning chill, and the sun was out. I came to think that everything was just a bad thought and just stop everything. 'You guys I think we should just, forget about the robot,' I said. They gave me a confusing look. One of them said sadly, ' Why should we forget about it, we have almost half of the robot.' I just shook me head no.                 The next day was Monday, a school day. I was walking down the hall when I noticed a black and purple paper laying on the floor. It said ' STARTING WEDNESDAY WE ARE HAVING A SCIENCE CLASS', ' THIS SCIENCE CLASS WILL BE A COMPETITIVE CHALLENGE AGAINST OTHER STUDENT FROM DIFFERENT SCHOOLS' ,' IN AFTER SCHOOL  WE WILL HAVE A PRESENTATION FOR BUILDING YOUR OWN ROBOT' ,' STUDENTS ITS AN OPPORTUNITY, SO PLEASE ANYONE IS WELCOME.' I was happy to know there is now an opportunity for me to make my robot.                 I saw my friends coming my way really excited, 'Kim did you hear ', one said, 'You can make your own robot now.' Happily I said, ' I know you want to come with me and make one, it will be fun. They nodded yes.Two days passed , its Wednesday the classroom is empty. Then my friends and the rest of the students come in. A man starts a presentation, then after 30 minutes have past he tells us we will be stating our robots this day.  Mr. Jonson the teacher gave us really different materials to use more differ than the ones we used at home. He gives us instructions on how to start. We actually did make a robot this time and it did not take that long 4 hours straight. Now we were all ready to go to the competition this Saturday.                We arrived at the museum Academy Of Science. 'This place is crowded' I said. We stopped at a ticket stand a man asked for our ticket, 'Ticket Please.' Mr. Jonson gave him our tickets. We entered in an enormous room with different robots everywhere. Another tall man walked to the microphone . He said to get our robots ready to start the competition. Our small robot competed with a lot of other robots. Although it was not at all how I wanted mine, our special robot won the competition! All of us we proud that our robot actually did come alive I thought it wouldn't work but it did. And now you see many dreams do come true but you just have to struggle though some obstacles to get to that dream. That was the most amazing experience I ever had.

Item_Response: Jimmy Cambell, he was alone one afternoon and decided to build a robot. Not expecting it to work, Jimmy set his robot aside so that he could look at him. Scout, he named him. One day while Jimmy was at school, scout came alive. Jimmy returned to find scout missing. He was freaking out! A missing robot! He lied down on his bed and slept. He was awoken to the sound of rustling papers. He looked and there was scout, looking through his school-work. 'Scout?!' Jimmy asked amazed. 'Yes of course Jimmy' scout responded in a robotic voice. Jimmy thought to himself, Oh My Gosh!!I've created a talking robot!         Later that night, Jimmy tested out what else scout had the ability to do. He was quite intelligent. He understood Jimmy speaking to him, he performed tasks like feeding the dog, taking out the trash, and putting the dishes away.Jimmy was excited about all the possiblities and great adventures this robot was able to have.While Jimmy was sleeping, Scout had a change of mind of what his 'master' would make him do. Scout was turning evil.        That next morning, Jimmy woke to Scout yelling, and throwing papers everywhere. 'Scout! Scout! Scout what is going on?' Scout looked angrily at Jimmy, beady red eyes, a robotic grimace. 'You are NOT my master!You do NOT control me!' Scout then proceeded to break Jimmy's door and rush downstairs. Jimmy had created a mess he needed to clean up. 'Awwww man!' Jimmy uttered under his breath. 'great'. By then scout was already down the street screaming his little robot head off.        Jimmy chases after him, in his footed pajamas, with a teddy bear in his arms. He was so frightened. 'Scout?' 'Scooouuutt???' Jimmy continuously called out. 'Where is that dang robot?' Just then scout leaped up out of the bushes and tackled Jimmy, 'Scout? SCOUT?! woah...woah! Dude chill out!' Jimmy was able to wrestle the robot off of himself and onto the ground. 'You are not my master! Puny human!' Scout yelled out furiously. 'I created you, didn't I?' Jimmy thought, 'So, yeah, that DOES make me your master!'         Later that day, Jimmy was able to disable Scout, 'You were a good friend to start with, but this had to happen.' Jimmy was heartbroken, but he understood this was the right thing to do. Jimmy's mother, called him faintly, her voice getting louder. 'Jimmy? Jimmy wake up sweetie!' Jimmy popped out ogf bed. 'Oh my gosh! Thank goodness it was only a dream! Whew!' Jimmy's mother was confused,' What happened sweetie?' Jimmy replied to her, 'I'd be glad to tell you over some nice, warm, robot-free breakfast.'

Item_Response: One stormy night on April 25, 2075 there was a little robot looking for help. Her name was giggles and she was always happy. When she ran out of fuel, she had fallen and lost power. 25 years later the same storm had arrived and it shoked the little robot with all the electricity it had. Giggles awakened confused about all the changes that had happened. When she reached the city she found out that that all the humans were enslaved by the robots. Now it was up to her to save them all.               Poor little Giggles first had to get fuel for her empty tank. She didnt realize that all the robots were even more generous than when she had left. They gave everything out for free, but now they hated humans. It was up to her to figure out why. The most obvious thing was that there was a large suspicious building. She decided she would start her investigation over there.  When she reached the tower she saw that it was heavly gaurded by newer improved robots. Thats when Giggles decided to come at night . At night she had found a little gap on one of the walls. It took her a couple of minutes but she finally squeezed through. The building was still gaurded by even more menacing robots. Then she heard loud footsteps coming so she went into a room that she had seen. The room was filled with old robots scraps. She decided to look through the junk and get a little upgrade. After a while she had found all the pieces that she would need. Then she quickly abandoned the room and tried to reach the top of the building. At the top she figured out who had enslaved all the robots. It wasnt a human neither a robot but it was a super computer. She had finally learned the truth when the computer told her what had happened. She found out that an evil human had planted a virus into her system and had turned her evil. Now she had erased the memory of all the robots and told them that the humans are bad. After the story the computer had called the robots to take Giggles away, but Giggles wasnt going to leave without a fight. Then she grabbed nd ripped out her arm and stabbed the computer. After that the computer died and all the robots returned to normal. The humans were also released.             Then the humans and the robots both decided to make Giggles their new ruler. Giggles was first a little shy but after a few minutes she had accepted their offer. A few years later Giggles city had prospered. Now Giggles city is the best place around and both humans and robots all over the world come to visit.

Item_Response: Robo, The Amazing Robot       'It's done! My beautiful creation is finally done!' Dr. Shea, a scientist, exclaims.       'You mean Robo is done?' Dr. Shea's assistant asks.       'He sure is made perfectly!' Dr. Shea pats the robot's arm.   'Let's go out and celebrate.' He says with a huge smile.       The two of them leave the robot, unattended, and go out to eat some pizza. When they come back, they both walk to Robo's room. The two of them examine him while they sip their sodas.       'Didn't I leave Robo over on that side?' Asks Dr. Shea.       'Hmm, but you don't think Robo could've moved himself, do you?'       'Ha ha, of course not!' Dr. Shea forces out a fake, little laugh.       Mr. Shea and his trustworthy assistant work on their other creation, a robot used to do all your homework correctly. When suddenly they hear a loud noise!       Crash! Boom! Robo falls off his bed. Clink, clink, clink, clink.        'Shea, w-whats that n-noise?' Asks Shea's assistant, Marx.       'Oh, Marx! Always scared about everything. It's probably just somethings that fell!'       The two of them walk over to the noise. They see Robo walking!       'Greetings, masters.' Robo says. Clink, clink! He keeps walking towards them.       'Sh-Shea, w-what's, h-how!?' Marx whispers as he gets behind Dr. Shea.       'Robo? You can walk! You can talk! How? My goodness! This is a miracle! This is just amazing!'       'Thank you master for creating me. You are the reason I'm alive. Father, Shea.' Robo stops a couples inches away from Dr. Shea.       'Call me doctor. Come lets get some tests done.' Dr. Shea says to Robo. Then he turns around and leads Marx and Robo into a testing room. 'Marx, this is amazing!' He keeps on talking about how it's a miracle.       After the tests Shea, Marx and Robo had a press meeting where all of America was amazed. After Robo's life saving skills training was over, Robo became a hero!       Robo is still out there saving lives of the ones in danger. Thank Robo for spending his life in selfless service to our world.       10 years later Marx and Dr. Shea were, yes, famous and very rich. The homework robot didn't work, but creating Robo was great enough. The two got married to kind, caring women and settled into big mansions with beautiful families while Robo spent his life saving all of America. America's safety is in Robo's hand.

Item_Response: The diary of robot girl                                             Rebecca Avila                                                                 part1                                      On the day of  the thunder storm a mad scientist was working on her creation of  a robot to renumber her daughter who passed away a few years ago. Son the unknown lighting bolt electricuting her robot , causing her robot too come alive.Earlier that day the mad scientist took  her daughter heart from the funrul home and stuffed it in the robots heart.But there was a flaw,the mad scientist didn't have unhough electristy to turn the robot on. So on that night the robot came alive.  Te mad scientist made the robot look like a real human person. With clothes and a real looking face. The only exception was she had a different heart.The scientist made a mistake.The heart was not her daughters.It was mine.I am Mary Evergreen and this is my story.                                         Dear diary, It's been two centuries since i died in a fire when I was only 15.It's been a long time since that. I r ember when i was trapped in burning house. The only thing that bothers me is I have metal legs. I haven t been trying to move because the mad scientist might tun me off. Oh no shes walking in no sudden movements. She caught me talking this is good bye again.Surprisingly she hugs me and starts saying'I never thought I've see you again'.I say ''um yeah you too''.To be my Creator I thought she be some what different.Anyway she took me to my room and there was a weird box that showed live plays.                                 Dear diary, I still haven't told my Creator that I'm her not her daughter.The reason why I barley starting to see the world. When I came to America it was nothing but dry land and Indian tribes. This is when George Wasintion was barley a teenager with his snaky mood.Now there is computers, cheese burgers, i pad s ,TV,t and his machine you use wash clothes [they don't even use lakes].I just don't want disappoint her when I tell her I'm not her duagher.Right after she walked into my room and said''I love you''.                                             Part 2 : the confession                                    Dear diary,today is  the day I am going tell my creator I am not her daughter.I step into the room. She says 'oh hi sweetie,I get more nervous. I rush and say I'm not your daughter'. She says 'what I cant here you''. I  say 'I am not your daughter I am a different girl I am Mary Evergreen and I am from the 18th century . I am sorry I should told you sooner but this much age when I came here place don't kill me''.She didn't get upset and left . she said to me  'I knew this would happen that's why installed  in your HRP-4c  a concuis'. I say I will leave  and go some where else.'' or she said 'you can be my asident in my lab'. I s aid 'yes  thank you so much'. Since that day I never doughted her.                                                                    part 3:the power                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               Dear diary, I just fond the craziest thing .For my 16th birthday I got a special power.I can play music , dance,and sing. Isn't that the coolest thing. For mt creators birthday  I am going to download her a song most people know it's called  the birthday song. I'm still trying figure out a lot of things. So far I'm having a good week being human. The best thing about being a robot  is having  a heart because most robots don't. Anyway this weeks been pretty awesome. I'll write more later.           Love, Mary Evergreen     [robot girl]

Item_Response: Cool Robots            What kind of robots do you like? I like robots that are fun to hang out with and that do   chores just like the story you are about to read. In the year of 2012 there was a girl named Katherin she was a shy girl. Everybody thought she was wierd just because she did not talk to anyone.              One day Katherin was walking in the neirborhood and she ran into a boy named Jake and then she just walked away. Jake wanted to get to know her so he caught up with her again then he said ' Hi my name is Jake and your Katherin right. ' She nodded and staded quiet.               'Sorry I don't really talk to anyone really. ', Katherin said with a small grin.   'So, tell me some thing about your self any thing like your favorite color or ' just then she stoopped him from going on. She gave an angry look.             'Why?' she asked with a wierd look on her face looking confused. then Finally she said 'Ok, do you want to see some thing? ' he smiled then nodded she made him follow her back to her house and showed him something no one has ever seen before. She showed him her robot. After that she told him all the things it can do from hanging out with it to doing chores for her.                In her opinion Katherin thought Jake would faint. Instead his eyes were wide open and looked at her with a huge smile. Ever since that day they became best friends and with the robot of course. They did every thing they even let each other borrow the robot to do their chores for them at their houses. When they went back to school she started to talk and then she finally had friends. She was happy about meeting Jake and showing him her COOL Robot. :)

So that next day he went to search for parts. He found exactly he wanted and more. That second he ran all the way home. When the man was in front of his house he trip and fell. He got up he so it was his robot. He and the robot went inside and then he charged the robot.                  He found a memory chip. He program the chip to have lots of thing on it like: calculate singing dancing pets baby's and etc.   The man called it HRP-4c. The man loved his robot. The robots first song he sang was 'BABY' by Justin Bieber.                    In conclusion the robot help the man to get pride. He said ' I still remember his first song. 'THAT SONG WILL ALWAYS BE MY FAVORITE' SAID THE MAN.

Item_Response: Once upon a time, in a village, known today as Germany, there was a crazy old man who wanted to be the world's best scientist, just like his father. Everyone said he couldn't do it, which made him try harder, which made him go crazy.  On the day of his 85th birthday, he bought himself a tool box and a bucket full of metal. He went back to his home, and got to work on a new invention that would help people all over the world.                       He worked for five years straight. The only time he stopped was to eat for 10 minutes and sleep for 2 hours then it was back to work.  After he completed his work he named his creation Quicky Stevey.  He combined all the abilities of his fathers inventions.  It could help miners underground like the Gemini Scout.  It could climb into volcanoes for research, like the Dante 2.  Also it can bring people medicine when they needed it.  The robot can do all these things by just the push of a button.  It was operated   by a remote control.                   The next morning he took his invention to the center of town where everyone could see him.  'Go away old man,' one man said.  'You are too old to be like your father. Just give up and retire all ready.'                 'Just listen to me. My father invented three robots that can help everyone, but wouldn't buying three robots be more expensive than buying just one.  Which why I took all my father's research and combined it into one.  Behold the Quicky Stevey.  With just one push of a button the Quicky Stevey can tend to any trouble you might be in.  Have a report due on volcanoes for school, know problem just push the volcano button on the remote and it find you your research in 1 days time.  Anything my father invented is right here in the palm of your hand and you don't even need the robot, just buy the remote.  Here's the best part, sell my father's robots back to me and your remote will be 100% free.'              'You are just wasting our time' said the man again. 'Do you honestly think we will buy your invention when w already paid for it.  And how do we know you will give us our money back when your father through it into a volcano for safe keeping.  Hey everyone, let's beat this thing to peices.'  That is when everyone tore the robot to the ground with their bare hands.             He tried and tried again but he ended up with the same resultes for the next 12 years of his life.  At his funreal a little girl walked up his tombstone, placed a flower on the ground, and said with a soft voice,  'I liked your invention.'

Item_Response: Robots Coming To Life.       We were at our school science fair and me and my friend had to make robots. As we made the robots my friend saw something strange but I didn't say anything I thought she  just didn't have enough sleep and was tired. I was making my robot and making sure I put all the details and wires on right. As I was was making my robot I named him Albert. Albert was coming along well and I didn't have any troubles with him. But on the other hand my friend Victoria was having a little trouble. I was watching Victoria with her robot and as I was watching her I went over there to see how she was doing and she said everything was fine.           I went back to Albert to finish him up and he was gone. I looked everywhere for Albert he was nowhere to be found I went over to ask Victoria if she had seen  him and she said no. But as I was looking at Victoria she seemed kinda weird her eyes looked red and her voice sounded different. I went back to my station and Albert was there it was kinda strange because when I left to go check on Victoria Albert was gone but I didn't worry about it. So I kept on working.               I ran out of wire so I went back to Victoria's station and as I was walking over there by her station i heard a loud noise and as I was opening the covers I saw Victoria laying on the table with a robot that looks just like her. The robot that Victoria made was trying to take her brain so I ran over by the cords but, I didn't no witch one to pull so I pulled all of them all Victoria's stuff shut off her computer, saw, lights, and over-head. But then as I turned around to go and help her Albert was right behind me trying to get me to stop. As Albert was fighting me I went behind him and pulled out his memory chip I told Victoria that we would never make robots again because they tried to take over the world and Victoria's robot tried taking her brain. As I helped Victoria up her robot was not un- plugged yet. So I plugged in the saw and gave it to Victoria and she  sawed her robot in half.       In conclusion me and my friend Victoria had a good time and we had fun making our evil robots even though we didn't know that they were trying to take over the world and our brains we make a good science fair team. I hope next year we can also make robots and I hope they will not be as evil as Albert and Victoria's robot.

Item_Response: One day when I was at the doctor because I was sick. I needed medicine because I had an ear ache. I saw a shadow coming in, and I assumed it was the doctor. but I was wrong...        It wasn't a doctor it was a robot! I was shocked I'd never seen a robot that looked like drawers or a cabinet. Then it said 'Here you go, have a nice day.'As it said that I screamed and fell off my chair, and the doctor came running. Then Dr.Sweet said whats wrong, are you all right.I yelled 'NO!!!!''The cabinet just talked and I fell off my chair.'         Dr. sweets explained to me that Mr. Gower, the robot that made me fall off my chair, just simply delivers the medicine to the patients room so other nurses and people can focus on more important things. I was more calm after she told me that. Now I wanted Mr. Gower to come in again so I could talk to him because I was in my room all alone and bored to death. Eventually he did and I was really happy. We talked for an hour or so , but then the doctor came in and said I could go home. I asked if I could take Mr. Gower home, but the doctor said no.Instead he said I could come and visit Mr.Gower any time I wanted.  Ever since then I laved going to the doctors and helping out their with Mr.Gower

Item_Response: Helping Hands (Robots)     Once upon a time there was a fifteen year old boy that always wanted a robot. On a Friday afternoon when he cam home from school and saw a square shaped box of some sort covered up in red wrapping paper. He was astonished. He said,'Could this be? Can it be?!?' He went to go touch the box. He shook thee box; heard a lot of little metal pieces move in the box. When he opened the box he saw pieces used to make a robot. There was also a little note left behind it said,'Son your mom and I have to go to a funeral, but we bought you a robot to keep you company and help you do some stuff around the house.' The boy went to sleep.         When the boy woke up he stated to build his robot. When he finished he was really thirsty so he went to go drink some water. When he came back he saw the robot cleaning his room. He was astonished again. 'What are you doing?' asked the boy. In the robot's response it said,'Well as you can see I am a robot that loves to help clean and do stuff around the house!!!' The robot helped the boy paint the house, clean the inside of his house, and the robot helped him out washing the car(s). The robot was really smart and decided to teach the boy about math and some other things you need to learn in order to graduate from high school and get a good scolership.         After a couple of hours the boy was begining to think he was as smart as Albert Einstien. The robot was happy that he could help him out. After all of that was over the robot and the boy went outside. The robot showed him his really cool tricks that he knew how to do. When the robot was finishing up his cool tricks the boy suggested that they should play catch, soccer, tennis, volleyball, or even football. They both got really tired and decided to go and take a nap. It was twelve o'clock midnight (12:00a.m.) the robot took the kid/boy upstairs into his room and fell asleep again.         It was morning and the boy woke up and heard a car door slaming in his parkway/driveway. After that he heard the sound of a key entering a keyhole in the door down stairs. When he went to go look it was his parents'. He rushed down the stairs to give them a big hug because he really missed them a lot. His parents brought him a piece of chocolate cake. They lived hapily ever after.                                                 THE END

While Brandon with his black as night scruffy hair to his intriguing eyes, I was in the back. I have ginger flowing hair with eyes the color of a four leaf clover.                As we got close enough to touch the gold paint that was on the immense object Brandon and I went around the back to inspect this odd looking shape. All of a sudden my lazer sharp vision saw a door in the back of the object. We were all looking for some parts for our robot because my dad was holding the robot wars in 2 days! As Brandon and I near the back door Brandon uses his strongest arm to try and pry open the door. As my squeaky voice slices through the air calling for Syd and Bella to come around back they reply with lower voices saying 'ok'. Finally Brandon prys open the rusty door of the object and we all take tiny steps into the dark room. It seems like forever walking into a dark room because none of us can make out what is in this room. It felt like 4 hours until we could find a switch in this historical room. But when the lights came on it felt like I had just woken up from drifting into sleep. As our not so ready eyes ajust to the light we finally agree that the object we were in came to life at one point. The reason we new that was because we found an oil deposit that was at its last drip of oil. If we wanted to enter the robot wars my dad was holding we would need a robot and I was starting to think that we just found our solution. 'Look!' Bella said a control switch! We removed the cob webs from the buttons and found out that this object really could move! All of us in unison run out of the room and spead up so we could see the front of the object.                Low and behold we could see eyes! Brandon, Bella, Syd, and I went up to the object and tried to feel out if they were apart of the object... and they were! All we needed to do was get about 50 gallons of oil and this thing would be ready to start up! My feelings about this object were clear now. This robot had been here for about over 45 years and no one had ever come to fix it! We needed to find that oil and find it quick. We don't want anyone else to come and find our robot.                We were 2 minutes from home and I was thankful. Today has been a long day and I just wanted to get home. Finally at the foot of our doorstep, (My friends lived with me because my dad was a foster dad) so we all went inside. My dad was a negotionable dad he was always there for all of us but sometimes he could get a bit anry. He sent us all to bed and in about 1 minute I was fast asleep.            When I woke up I felt eyes staring at me. I finally got my hazy vision clearer and thats right, Brandon, Bella and Syd were starring at me. 'What are you guys doing?!' 'I exclaimed. Don't you guys know I need my space from you guys sometimes and I dont need you guys looking at me the whole morning.' 'Fine'. Said Brandon we were just waiting for you to wake up so we could go get that oil today. (We didn't go to school since we didn't have any schools around us to go to.) As I hop out of bed I rub my eyes and get dressed we had a big day today. We were building our robot todady! I got on my not so clean cloths because we would be working on the robot and head down stairs. I didn't even need to have breakfast because I was in the motion and ready to go. Brandon, Bella, Syd, and I go out the front door without even saying good bye to dad and head to the department store. With our allouences we were sure to have enough money for 50 gallons of oil. We were out and out of the department store with the oil head down to the robot and start working on it. With our oil we filled up the HUGE oil tank and the pannel of buttons lit up. It was up and working. Almost done and we would have this working like a charm. We would keep the gold paint on since we all liked it. And finally the robot was up and running. It turned on and stood up to its full potential. We would name it Sibor. Brandon, Bella, Syd and I did an amazing job on Sibor and we were really wishing that dad would love it. He will love it. Sibor will be a feirce contendor at the robot wars. I was so proud of our work on this great robot. And he will be remembered forever.

Item_Response: Tap, tap, tap, tap. Someone was tapping the door! 'Why couldn't they just use the doorbell!' I said. So I opened the door and didn't expect to see a 3 feet robot there! It was so cool! I wanted to know if it could talk when it said,' Hi my name is Sally.' Then she handed me a remote. It was like a remote you use for video games. I pressed a button thinking it was for a game but then the robot moved. She said,'Whenever you want you can control me with it, but I can move and talk and everything by myself too.'          The robot told me some many things about her, like how she had dragged some people to safety, and how she gathers information for scientist! Is was so cool! The thing that amazed me the most was that she helps and works at the hospital sometimes! If I get sick I'll just go to her.          I was so intrested with playing and talking with the robot I forgot what time it was untill her alarm went off. 'Dont worry it just rings ever hour so I know what time it is. Right now it 5:00 PM,' said the robot. ' 5 o-clock!' I said. 'Yah why?' ' My mom comes home by this time and if she finds you who knows what would happen,' I said. ' I can leave,' said the robot. 'No way! We will have to think of a plan.' ' Well ok. Oh what does your mom hate doing?' asked the robot. 'Well lots of things like cooking, cleaning, gardening,' I replied. ' Good.' said the robot.          Ding dong! 'Hi mom.' 'Hi! Wow you cleaned the house and I noticed that you were gardening! Oh my god did you cook pasta!' said my mom. ' Well about that. Ok I doubt you will believe me but when you see her yourself you will have to.' I said in a anxious voice. 'Ok but what do I have to see.' she said confused. ' Ok well a robot came to our house and we both played and enjoyed our self. We thought you might not like her so she did all this work just so that you let her stay.' ' What we have a robot in our house! That's not possible!' my mom exclaimed. ' That's what I thought so I'll show her to you.'          'Sally this is my mom' I said. 'Hi.' said Sally. 'Oh my god you are a talking robot! Well definetilly you can stay! After all you have done how can I say no!' ' Thanks!' Sally and I said at the same time! 'Now on you will always stay with us!'

Item_Response: Helpful Robots                  Robots are important to everyone. They can accomplish goals that humans can not do. Some things that they can do include working in farms, helping miners stuck underground, and exploring volcanoes.               Robots that help in farms are also known as agribots. All over the country, they help farmers pick fruits and vegetables in the farm. The size and shape of the agribot depends on the type of crop. In some places, robots can also determine if the fruit is ripe or not. If a plant is dry. these robots can water them. Agribots are very useful in farms.               Gemini-Scouts, robots who work underground, are very short. This size helps them go through mines to rescue the miners stuck underground. A Gemini-Scout can go on stairs, make sharp turns, roll through water, and even carry supplies. Gemini-Scouts can also can tell if the surrounding gases are poisonous or safe. This helps the miners a lot. These kinds of robots can also sense where robots are by using their thermal camera.               Robots that explore volcanoes, also know as Dante 2, can go into active volcanoes. These robots can withstand high temperatures. While these robots collect information, the scientists can study a volcano while they remain safe in their laboratories.               I think that robots are an important part of our lives. I also think that they can help collect information and save people. Robots may even become part of our everyday lives in the future.

Item_Response: The first time the 'thing' spoke to me I was stunned. Speechless. You couldn't blame me though. For one, the 'thing' was at least three heads taller than me! And the only word I can think of to describe its voice is strange-it didn't even sound real. At first, I was terrified. I thought the thing was going to hurt me to be honest, but when the 'thing' spoke to me in its scratchy-robotic voice and told me that it was a robot that used to be a search-and-rescue robot that worked in mines to help find and save injured miners, I had a change of heart. The robot then started to tell me the story of one of his last missions when he was sent into a fallen mineshaft to try to help save a trapped miner who was on the verge of death.       'I was being oiled down when I first overheard mission control telling my controller, Luke, that my mission was official. I was going to attempt to find a trapped miner named Benjerman Stewart.       'Alright then', Luke grunted as he picked me up, 'lets get you loaded into the copter.'       Because we were on stand-by for the mission, it didn't take us long to get to the copters landing site at the mine. They then unloaded me and made sure that my controls were adjusted and then they sent me in.       They first thing I saw inside the mine was rock. Lots of rock. My data sensors told me that the rock was a type of granite, but I disregarded it and started on my search for Benjerman Stewart.       I wedged my way through countless nooks and crannies, looked through my thermal camera for hours, and then I finally found him. Benjerman was not in good shape at all. He was badly hurt from the mine collapse and was either unconscious or dead, I couldn't tell. But either way I dragged him back to the entrance to the mine where there was a medical crew waiting. I could see the medical team working feverishly on Benjerman. And before I knew it, Luke was loading me back into the copter. The last thing I heard before the copter flew away was 'we have a pulse' from the medical crew that was working on Benjerman Stewart.'

Item_Response: When you think of robots do you think of the future?  Well, you shouldn't because there are already robots everywhere today.  How common are robots?  And what can a robot look like.       There are robots everywhere today.  The whole reason you're reading this right now is because of robots.  The actual definition of the word 'robot,' is a machine that can perform the acts of a human.  So really a phone, a camera, a guitar tuner, a printer, and an electronic lock are robots.  Robots don't have to be like in movies where they try to make humans extinct.  They can even be something in your pocket.  That is how common robots are.       'What can a robot look like?' is a question that some people have asked before.  A  robot can look like anything really.  A robot can be made to look like a piece of wood when it really is a camera.  The possibilities are endless for what a robot can look like.        Those were some question that some people had on robots, and remember, the thing right next to you could be a robot.

Item_Response: Today is the day! I think to myself. I walk into the school proudly and go into my first class. The computer turns. 'Hello class,' our online teacher says. 'Today is the day that you will be turning in your 10,000 word essay on your robot pet.' I glance around the room, everyone seemed excited to turn their paper in. 'Kassie,' she says loudly. 'May I have your paper?' I look over at my friends and insert my paper into the scanner. As I sit the teacher says 'Kassie will you please go down to the boiler room and get me the screw driver?' I turn surprised and say yes.                                                                       The boiler room is very old and dusty. I slowly walk around finding the tool box easily. I explore the room trying to figure out why I was sent down here. I hear a bang coming from the far corner I haven't checked. I walk over to the corner. 'Hello?' I say. No one answers. Another bang. 'Hello!' I say again. Suddenly a robot comes swiftly around the corner and gets the tool bow and brings it over. It's  whispering something while it searches the box.I walk over to it and ask if i can have a screw driver. It happily gives it to me and follows me up the stairs and into the classroom.   When I walk in the class is discussing an issue of some sort.'What's happening?' I ask. 'Nothing of interest.' the teacher says to me. The robot rolls in. 'Where in the world did you get that, Kassie?' I explain about my experience and how I found the robot. He became our class pet and since I found him I got to take him home for a day. The days wore on and we named our robot pet Andre. Everyone got to take him home for a day by the end of the year. The next year our old teacher video chatted with us daily and showed us how Andre was doing.

Item_Response: In movies you may only dream about having a robot servent, well, that age might as well come now.Today we have invented amasing robots that  save lives, help us with everyday things, or help us have fun, but today we will look at the one that help us...for real.I bet that when you hear some of the names of these robots you will laugh...I did!You are about to enter a world filled with robots you may have never heard of.                   The first robot I am introducing you to is the Gemini-Scout.This robot is helping us do many things, such as saving lives, collecting information, and gives us the things we need most in a time of crisis.Gemini-Scout is remote-controlled.The remote is like a video game remote...so if you are constintly on the video games this is right up your alley!This robot is less than two feet tall, has wheels, and is small but strong.The tiny robot, believe it or not, rescues lost miners, and carries food,water and other suppies for them if they are starved or thirsty.Gemini-Scout can also collect information, and tests the air for poisionious gases.                    Next, we will learn about a tough robot.It is called Dante 2.Dante 2 is special because it climbs into volcanoes, and gathers information for the scientists.The robot has eight legs, sort of like a spider, and is built to withstand heat.This robot also climbs into vents, and holes to collect the gasses for information.                    Now...introducing my favorite robot of them all...Mr.Gower!Yes the robot's name is Mr.Gower.Mr.Gower works in hospitals, and helps doctors and nurses.This robot is small and looks like a cabnet on wheels, but don't let that fool you because it is strong enough to pull 500 pounds!Inside these drawers there are all different kinds of medicine!But that is not all...this tiny robot can talk too! Now how can you not love this machine!                    The last robot I am introducing you to is called Agribots.This 'little' bot picks fruit for us!This is a first for me.Agribots pick berries, oranges, grapes, and apples. There is no real size for them because the could come in any size depending on what you want them to pick. These robots are able to move around by themseves!                     See didn't I tell you there are some extradanry robots out there!So the next time you need to be rescued from a mine, need to know how big a volcano is, need medicine,or need to harvest your fruit, these bots will be on the job!

Item_Response: I'm sure people think that robots will soon take over the earth and eliminate all human kind.  Well, if you ever thought that, you were wrong.   Robots just want to help us, not harm us.              Meet the Gemini-Scout.  This is a remote control robot that does search and rescue work in mines under ground.  The Gemini-Scout is less than two feet tall.  It can go up and down stairs and even go through water without being harmed.  Wherever the Sam robot goes, it collects information.  For example, the robot will test the air for toxic gases and can tell miners when the air is safe.  The Gemini-Scout, is a very easy robot to use.  Is you play video games, then it shouldn't be very hard.          Have you ever heard of the Dante 2?  This robot has a very unique job.  It climbs into volcanos and gathers information for scientists.  This robot has eight legs that help it move around so easily.  When a volcano is to hot for scientist to enter, they call the Dante 2.  The Dante 2 looks for vents and holes in the crater.  Then the robot gathers information about the gases coming out of the vent.  Many years ago, scientist could not learn so much about volcanos. But thanks to the Dante 2,  learn more about these fire breathing mountains every day.            Mr. Gower is another useful robot that works in hospitals and helps out doctors and nurses.  He is often described as a cabinet on wheels!  The drawers store medicine, and the robot will deliver the medicine to the doctors who need it.  Mr. Gower, can ride on elevators, steer through hall ways, and move things that are in his way.  Surprisingly, this strong robot can carry up to 500 pounds.  Just like most robots, Mr. Gower runs on a battery.  Not only does he work like a human, he can also talk!  Mr. Gower had been programmed to say over 100 phrases! This robot sound like a hero to me.          As you can see, these robots aren't monsters that turn evil like the ones in horror movies.  All these bots want to do is help make this planter a bigger, better, safer place.

Item_Response: Lia stared longingly at the door enclosing the large robot that had entranced her for years. She always hoped that she would someday be able to see it.   When Lia was seven, her father had taken her to his job at the Factory. His job had always seemed boring at that point; all he ever did was work with machines. And when you lived in the year 2143, where you saw machines every day, your dad had the most boring job in the history of jobs.   But then Lia saw the small neon green door that stood out in the sea of black paint and white lab coats and silver-gray machines.   Neon green was her favorite color.   'Daddy, what's that?' Lia had asked in an adorably inquisitive tone.   Her father had smiled.'That, Lia, is the prototype of-'   'What's a prototype?'   'I'll explain later. It is the prototype of a cyborg that looks and acts like a human.'   'Can I see?'   'Maybe when you're older.'   Lia had sighed. 'Okay, Daddy.'   Now Lia was sixteen, and visiting the Factory with her IPod 300 blaring music into the earphones. She strolled down the hall to the neon green door.   There was no handle on the door, but there was a keypad.   Lia bit her lip. She didn't remember this...   She stuffed her IPod in her bag and typed in PROTOTYPE.   The door didn't open.   She tried CYBORG.   No.   ROBOT.   No.   Then she remembered Ms. Spark teaching her about robots 100 years ago.   'Class,' Ms. Spark had chirped, 'today we will be learning about agribots. In 2043, agribots were used to pick fruit on farms. They had sensors so that they could know what the plant needs.'   Yes! That could be the password!   Lia grinned and typed in AGRIBOT.   Ding!   The door opened, and Lia raced inside.   Inside a small cylindrical sleeping pod lined with pillows, a boy lay inside. Lia's only clue that he was a robot was the small wire protruding from his ear.   Lia pressed the button that opened the pod, and the robot opened his eyes.

Item_Response: The Robots Who Saved Lives       It happened many years ago, but their are still people who talk about it to this very day. It all began when there was a call at the hospital a women had picked up the phone and a old man had been coughing so the women got his location and took him to the hospital. Doctors have figured out that the man had a serious disease, the disease was very unknown know one has heard of it, but luckily for them they had a special doctor called: Mr.Grower. Mr.Grower is a robot that isn't like any other robot, Mr.Grower can bring medicines to the doctors and nurses he can steer and go up and down the elevators, Mr.Grower can even talk! The doctors were operating on the man, but they haven't found a cure so Mr.Grower called one of his robot buddies:Dante 2. Dante 2 is kind of a special robot he can go into volcanoes and collect information for scientists, the hospital has sent Dante 2 into a volcano to give the samples to scientists to figure out a cure, cause so far doctors has only found out the patient needs a lot more steam. Dante 2 was about to go into the volcano when suddenly his rope had got stuck, Dante 2 was beginning to worry because he didn't know if he could handle the job, and when he thought that out of know where Agribots came swooping in from the sky to the rescue, Agrrbots usally picks and plucks fruits and vegetables out of the ground, but in this case Agribots had to know how to pick out Dante 2's rope. So Agribots went in slowly and picked out Dante 2's rope, Dante 2 was really worried, but he had faith in Agribot. Agribot was shaking, but when Dante 2 felt the shake on his rope he told Agribot he had faith in him, when Agribot heard that he gently pulled the rope and Dante 2 has been lifted up to the top of the volcano, when Dante 2 went to the top of the volcanoe he had told Agribot that he had to go back in to get samples for the scientists, at first Agribot wouldnt let him go back in, but once Dante 2 told Agribot about the ill-ed man, Agribot let Dante 2 go in. So Dante went in the volcanoe and he had got the sample for the scientists. Dante 2 and Agribot went back to the scientists and the examined the sample and they had found the cure! So Dante 2, Agribot and all of the scientists went to the hospital and all doctors had put the cure on the illed man, the ill ed man was very happy he was still alive. The ill ed man has thanked everyone and the ill-ed man invited everyone to celebrate at his house. At the end of it all they became the best of friends.

Item_Response: J.K The Robot That Came Alive          It was a beatiful,but hot spring day. A few days before my birthday. I wanted someone to play with other than my annoying brother! I wanted someone to talk to, to laugh with,and who will treat me like a best friend should. You see, my bffwe(best friends forever without exeptions) moved away to Wasco 2 months ago. What I wanted was a 'FOREVER FRIEND' a new robot . I asked my parents for one alot of times. But what I didnt expect came to me on my birthday.April 12,2013. I had just woke up and never got up this early so ethier something was wrong or we were going somewhere. When I got out of the shower and went to the kitchen for an apple what did I see?! A robot . A FOREVER FRIEND !!!!!! She was dressed in a blue blouse and a black skirt . Her hair was golden brown and she had earphones in her ears . I said ,'Hello' she responded by saying,'Good morning my name is J.K' She was of course a robot and not real but I loved her like a sister . At night  I told her , 'I wish you were real' Little did i know she was made to obey......               When i woke up i found a new person lying in by bed fast asleep . I woke her and said 'WHO ARE YOU AND WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN MY BED?!!!!!!' The person responded, ' I'm J.K master'. 'J.K?!OH NO MY MOM AND DAD ARE GONNA KILL ME FOR TURNING MY BIRTHDAY PRESENT INTO A REAL HUMAN!!!!!!' I heard a knock on my door . 'IDALLAS OPEN THE DOOR NOW!!!'......                 So I opened my door slowly and said, 'MOM J.K TURNED HERSELF INTO A HUMAN !' My mom looked at me then at J.K and said , 'I'ts fine she is your new bff so who cares ?'     WHEW!!!!!! I thought she was going to explod . She said to be quiet and then closed my door and went back to sleep. I imeddetly got up , took a shower, and changed .We both went to Mr. Slushie and ordered to milk shakes , burgers and fries. After we ate I notecied she looked sad . I asked her why was she sad . That was the bigest mistake i ever made .....               She got so angry she ran out a threw my scoter in the trash . I got it out and said,'WHAT'S THE BIG IDEA ?! ARE YOU CRAZY!!!??' She was crying and I said sorry for screaming at you . she said its' ok   and told me why  she was crying. It turns out she loves me and doesn't weant me to get hurt.Why? because a car came and almost ran me over ! But I had biger things to worry about........                                        J.K was starting to become a big problem!!! My mom said it was best to shut her down. It was a cold Wensday, I knew I had to shut her down. It was 3:00 in the mornig the house was quiet. I ran to the kitchen , and grabbed a screwdriver. I then flipped over J.K and took out her batteries and her wiers. I started to cry after she turned back into a robot.But something strange started to happen. There in her stomach I foud all of the albums by my favorite band Marianas Trench!!!!!!! The first said m fianal gift to you. The second said thanks for everything I understand why you put me down. The final one said forever and ever i will be there for you . Then an awsome thing happened she woke up!!! My mom said I could keep her but on one condition I keep her a robot !                                                           THE END!

Item_Response: Robot Come to Live                                                                                                                                                                        One day I was just sitting in my room minding my won bussiness when i heard this reallly loud scream and it sounded like a newborn baby. It can from my computer room where I do all my projects. So i walked over and opened the door really slowly. Then when my door was opened all the way I walked in but no one was there. So I looked around the room and reliazed I had a big mess because a couple days ago I was trying to make a robot but it didnt work. So I just started to clean it up so while I was picking up the mess I heared someone say 'hello' I jumped up so high I was now not scared just FREAKED  OUT!!! So I ran out of the room so fast. A few hours later I went back in and a person was sitting on my chair!!       'Hello my name is Savannah. I am so glad u made me! ' said Savannah the robot       'I made u? ' I asked.       'Yes, well not all of me. You started me but, then gave up so I finished the rest of me my the wonderful arms you gave  me! ' said Savannah       'Wow so you finnished yourself and sorry about giving up I just got a little mad.' I said.       'A little?!? Are you kidding me you were throwing a fit! Its ok though it was hard building me.' said Savannah       'Well ok then, So my name is Hope' I said.       'Well you didnt have a lot of hope in me Hope. Do u get it hope, hope I am just kidding with you! ' said Savannah       'I did have hope in you and oh i get it.' I answred       ' Finally you are slow at jokes but its ok i will help you but,first you have to teach me.' asked Savannah       ' Hey i am not slow! Well find maybe a little but lets get to the point teach you what?' I asked.       'You have to teach me everything you know. Because rememeber you build me to help you with extra help you needed.' answered Savannah       'Oh ya thats why i made you well lets start this business!' I said.       'YAY!!' said Savannah

Item_Response: Have you ever seen a robot that can research, play, dance or even drive for you? Today robots can research, be a pet and drive by itself. Robots changed science everywhere because thay can stand heat and the cold. Robots can bring back rocks or gas for scientists to study. The Dante 2 has eight legs and can go in volcanos to gather stuff for scientists.                 Robots can also play and be pet. The HRP-c4 can dance and sing. People are testing the idea of a pet robot like a cat or dog. A japanese robot can play the piano with two mechanical fingers. Scientists are trying to make the pet robots be much like the pet it was designed for.                 Google is currently making a self robot car that can drive on it's own. Testers already like this because thay have test drived it. All you have to do is to put the gas on it. Google has tested it on a freeway and it gone 70 miles. Today they are making robots but tommarow every one will have some sort of robot of their own. I can see that the world will be in a new age of technology soon.

Item_Response: Tom woke up one day, and he saw a human like figure right outside his window in a tree, but it was not human, he ignored it and went downstairs to eat breaksfeast. When he went downstairs, his mom said, 'Good morning honey, what have you been up to, it's 11'oclock'. He answers back, 'Nothing mom, it's Sunday, you know I always sleep in late, anyway, what's for breaksfeast'. 'Oh just some pancakes and eggs'.            After Tom finishes his food, he goes to his friend, Dwayne's house. They say hello and then Tom says 'Hey dude, this morning, I saw this weird robot thing on that tree, do you want to see if it is still there'? Dwayne answers back, 'Sure, whatever'. They go to the tree and it is still there, Dwayne climbs up the tree and throws the robot down to Tom. Tom says, 'What is this some kind of robot, whatever it is, it looks like it takes batteries'. The two boys go to Dwaynes house to get some batteries, Dwaynes mom says, 'Hello Tom, I haven't seen you in a while'. Tom replies, 'Hi Miss Rock, do you happen to have any batteries'? 'Why yes we do, here are some right here'. 'Thank you'! 'Your welcome'!           Dwayne and Tom go to the park where they put the batteries in, next thing you know the robot comes alive! The robot helped the two boys for the rest of their lives and they lived happily, ever, after.

Item_Response: There was once a boy that could never find anything interesting to do. Whenever he started to do something he got bored of it. He even got bored when he played with his little toy robot, which could make noises when you pressed a button on his back.But that was all about to change.                         One day the boy was in his room when suddenly, without pressing the button, the robot said,'Why are you so sad.' The boy ran and hid under his blankets. He was scared out of his mind. The robot said, 'Why are you scared. I'm not going to hurt you.' So, the boy slowly climbed out of bed, keeping his eyes on the robot the entire time. 'I know you get bored a lot,' said the robot,'and I'm here to help. I'm going to give you the best day ever!'. The boy got really excited and couldn't wait for the day to get started.                     At first they just got to know each other. The boy introduced himself and said his name was Kyle. The robot's name was Play-Bot 9000. Play-Bot 9000 said he also had other friends like HRP-4c, who can sing and dance, and Gemini-Scout, who helps trapped miners.'Cool.' said Kyle, 'So when can we play?' 'Right now if you want. Let's go.'                     The first thing they did was play outside. Kyle had never realized playing outside could be this much fun, especially since he had a real friend now. His friends at school could never come to his house because of their parents being busy.So, he had no one to play with until today. They played football, soccer, and Play-Bot 9000 even taught him how to play kickball because they did not have that at his school. They played outside for two hours and then they went inside.                     Next, Kyle showed Play-Bot 9000 how to play video games. He got the hang of it quickly and because Kyle had competition, he did not zoom threw the game. He had to go up against a real player, not just computer controlled players. So now, Kyle had a reason to play, not just because he was bored, but because he had a friend to play with him.                     Finally, after they ate, they played with other toys. They set up a large battlefield of toys that would fight for the castle in the middle of the room. Play-Bot 9000 called it King of the Hill.They had many battles between the good and bad teams, each one a little different from the last. Eventually, the good team captured the castle and all was good in the land. Kyle discovered that playing with friends was better than playing alone.So they kept playing until Play-Bot 9000 said he had to go. Kyle wanted him to stay, but he couldn't and said he would come back and play another day, but right now he had to go. So, he changed back into a toy and the boy set him on his dresser, promising that he would play with it everyday, waiting until Play-Bot 9000 came back to play with him again.

Item_Response: Year 2019, Scientists have dreamed of creating life. Until this day, May 25, 2019, their goal has not yet been achieved. 34 year old, John Johnson, has created a machine that will live like a human being, but isn't a human being. It is a replicant. A robot that looks exactly like a human!            Chapter 1, The Prototypes.        -The first Replicant was a Mining bot PROTOTYPE, that meant, it could mine ores beneath the surface that man could not.   -The second was a combat model, designed specifically for military duties.   -The third and final PROTOTYPE was, Just a bot that could mimic all of a persons Abilities, mentally, and physically.            Chapter 2, The Functions.                (1): Miner Bot; This bot could mine with it's right hand, sharp claws allowed it to penetrate hard ore such as diamond. It's left hand had a pouch hidden from view and would open to collect materials that were mined. A body with a protective titanium layer allowed it to mine even if a cave collapsed on top of it................. ..................... .... .................................................. ........................................ ........................................... ....  (2): Combat Bot; This particular model can stand a Rocket Launcher Blasting onto it. With an Iron layer, It could punch through a wall! It is also designed to carry all types of weaponry.       (3):Human Bot; The HUMAN Bot is the most complex bot. Since it is designed to copy all of human abilities, it proved quite a challenge. The model is made of a soft material that is made up of animal skins. Scientist input all human characteristics they know of into the bot's 'brain'.

Item_Response: My head was spining, turning, and flipping. I had no idea what was going on, until I woke up. I woke up in a hospital bed, wearing one of those ugly hospital gowns. I was panting, why was I hear? What happenend to me? I lean back in the bed calming down thinking that someone would come in and tell me. I then hear a knock on the door, a nurse walks in with a robot.       'Good, you're awake' she says   'Who are you? Why am I here?' I take a huge gulp 'And why do you have a robot?'   'I am doctor fay, you are hear because you got into a little accident, don't worry I will fix you right up'   'W-Why do you have a robot?'   'Oh her don't mind her, she is one of our assistants in training. Anyway this is Sally'   'In training?'   'Yes'       I think of how bad this could be Sally giving me sugery pulling out my lungs, and ripping out my bones. 'Where is my Mom and Dad? Wait did you ever tell me what happend?'       'Look, we will do the best we can to get your parents here, okay? Oh and this is what happend, you were on the jungle gym on the slide, all of your friends were going on the monkey bars so you thought you could do it too, so you tried. You couldn't reach the first pole so you jumped reaching you thought you could get it. Well, you missed. You missed the first bar falling back down you hit your head on the metal ladder and fell to the ground. You got a concusion and you were not consious the lady who was watching you guys on the monkey bars called someone to help. They called 9-1-1 and they took you away in the ambulance. While that was happening the school tried to get a hold of your parents but they didn't pick up they didn't know who else to call.' Doctor Fay took a breath, 'How do you get home from school? Do you know where your parents are?'   'I walk home from school. My parents were on vacation...I think'   'Who was watching you then?' 'My big brother Cody'   'What is your name sweetie? You remember right?'   'Yeah, My name is Marianna'   'Okay, Marianna why don't you rest I will make sure you are safe'   'Okay, Bye Sally. Bye Doctor Fay!'       So I lay in my bed the rest of the night recovering from my accident. I soon went to bed. I know I will be fine. I know it.

Item_Response: Once a upon a time there was a girl who was turning 8 years old and she was so exited for her birthday. She could wait. She had to see what her birthday presents were so she went snooping around the house. First she looked under her parents bed then his looked in her mom and dad's closets. After she had looked for 4 hours she was ready to give up but she thought of one more place and she didn't want to give up so easily. But her mom was watching so she waited until midnight.       Midnight came and she could hardly fall asleep. Finally her alarm clock rang midnight. She hooped out of bed and shoved her robe on and flung open the white door but quiet enough not to wake her parents or baby brother. She tip toed down the old stairs and headed for the coat closet. She could hear little mice running up and down the walls but she didn't care all she wanted was to get tot her birthday present and see what it would be. She opened the dubble door closet and looked up to the top shelf. On the shelf it was filled with a huge amount of rainbow colored wrapped boxes. I got a lot of presents she thought.      She got a stool and pulled down the big purple box, her favorite color. She quietly ripped off the wrapping paper and looked at the box. It was all brown it didn't have any writing on it or anything. I guess I will just have to open it to find out what it is she thought. She opened the top of the box and she thought her present was some kind of car moder and couldn't figure out what it was so she wrapped the present back up as best as she could and trugged back up stairs to her warm bed waiting for her. She will just have to find out what it was tomorrow on her birthday.      Today was her birthday. She was 9 years old. She got up and went into her parents room and jumped on the bed like it was Christmas. But it wasn't it was better it was her 9th birthday and she couldn't wait to open up all of her wonderful presents as she would hope that they would all be as wonderful as she would hope. She ran down the stairs carring her baby brother in her arms trining to be careful not to drop him. As her parents would always tell her over and over again. But today she wasn't really thinking a out that she was thinking about somthing more important than that. Her birthday of coarse.     Her parents brought out all her gifts. She hoped they wouldn't notic the purple one being not that perfectly wrapped. But them couldn't notic they were to focisted on me the birthday girl. I pick to open the big purple one irst so I didn't have to worry about them see the it wasn't perfectly wrapped like how my mom does it. I rip off the paper not caring if I mess it up and see the huge brown box again.
