Item_Response: When I was picking fruit I had found a mysterious robot. It was picking the exact same fruit that I was picking. When I got home I gave the fruits to my mom then I went to go research on the robot. I had found out the robot liked to pick fruits. When I went to pick fruits again I saw the robot picking fruits too. I did a little more research of the robot. I found out that the robot name is Agribot. The next day I saw the robot. When I saw the robot I came up to him and asked him and said , 'Why do you keep picking fruits everyday ?' The robot had reply by saying , 'I like to pick out , fruits it is my job to pick out fruits anyway.' After we talked I left home.                   When I saw the robot today he wasn't picking fruits. I asked him why he wasn't picking fruits. It said , 'The fruits are being taken by man kind and your the only one who can save the fruits.' I said , 'How can I save the fruits your a robot can't you just shoot lasers at them so they stay away from the fruits.' The robot had reply saying , 'We robots don't have the ability to shoot lasers , we only pick fruits and that's it. So we agree we were gonna have to save the fruits together. We planned on putting cameras on trees near the fruit. Once we put the cameras on the trees we connected the camera to my laptop. We waited and waited all day but the robbers had still not came. Then hours had pass by and then we had saw the robbers. Then we said , 'Stop!' but they still ran away with the fruits. The next day we decided we put traps near the fruits so they wouldn't get away. The robbers were capture by our trap when we walked up to the robbers we asked them why they kept stealing the fruits. They said that they had a restaurant and they didn't have fruits because they were poor. We asked how you guys get poor and they said , 'We lost all our money because we were robbed.' We said , 'We could try to help you get the money back.'               We decided to sell the Agribot for 150,000 dollars and make sure the guy had a farm. So somebody had bought the Agribot and the Agribot went to a nice farm to pick fruits. The robbers had alot of money for the restaurant and I had alot of fun saving the restaurant and trying to save the fruits. I wish I can do this all over again.

Item_Response: My Robot            Hi,my name is Antonio Alvarez I had a toy robot named Bobby.This is how it started my mom and I went to the toy store and saw a robot I told my mom if she could buy it for me she said no.I begged my mom on my knees and she finally said yes she bought a robot the size of me.My robot could transfer into me and it also does what ever I want it to do.                                                                                                                                                                                           We finally came back from the store I opened my new toy as quickly as possible.I had soccer practice at 5:30 and it was 5:00 I told the robot to get my soccer shoes,my soccer clothes,a water bottle,and my shin guards.Soccer practice ended at 7:00 my back started hurting,so I told the robot to give me a massage for 20 minutes.My mom told me I had to do my chores,so I told  Bobby to do my chores.He was done like in 1:30 minutes he had to wash the car,cut the grass,and clean up the mess in my room. Item_Response: It happend in class. I didn`t expect for my creation to turn out to be so amazing  and go wacko. Of course, the teacher and my parents got furious at me. But it wasn`t my foult I used to much electrisity. I`ll explain how it all got started.       It was a super hot day here in Sacramento. My parents had the air conditioner on, but even the piece of ice I put on my forehead wouldn`t help. A day at the river? No. A shower? Not at all. Me and my friend, Aly, were sweating buckets. I thought a day in doors would help. Her house was the only cool place in this Sunday. But it was a bore. I wanted to go swimming, but I couldn`t `cause it wasn`t clean yet. The next day at school, my science teacher told the class, 'We are going to try and create a minature robot.You`ll have to find information about how to make one.You have two weeks to find some info. Then the school will pay for whatever you need for this project. It counts for 60% of your grade.You`ll partner up with one of your friends.' That was easy. I chose Olivian. She was my best friend ever sience we met. It wasn`t long, but she was a really cool person. 'Hey, Olive! Be my parter!', I yelled across the room.'Yeah, okay. Wait `till I get my stuff.', she replied. We did 'research' on the copmuter.'Hey, do you think I could come over to your place?', I asked her. I knew were she lived, I just never got the chance to actually go over to her house.'Yeah, I guess so, if my parents`ll let you.'.We made plans on when we could meet.'`Kay then, so tomorrow after school?'       'Tomorrow after school.',she replied.   ___       Right after school, I tried to consentrate on my work, but I couldn`t. Two weeks had passed, and our idea of having a robot of our own didn`t seem so good after all,What if other people had the same idea? What if there ideas were better than ours? Of course, right when we got our materials, everything went wrong... well, at least not how Olivian and I planned.We started building, but when we were about done, I asked Olive,' Dare me to put more energy on it?'       'DON`T you dare!', she warned.'You`re crazy!'.       'Now you tell me.', I muttered. But -no suprise- I didn`t listen.It did some very weard sounds, and then it`s eyes went blank.'See what you did! You are so ... ugh!', she yelled. That`s when it turned back on and said something like 'I like pizza!' and then the teacher came.' Are you two done?It ure seems like it. Is this you`re robot? It looks pretty amazing girls.', she said.       'Yep, this is our robot.And we are done with it.But something went a bit wrong.Right now it said something like-', then it got up and started going around the classroom yelling,'I like pizza! I like pizza!'. We chased it around the classroom.Now, if you ever create a robot that talks and ends up breaking your desk, I suggest for you to not go after it or it might try to 1) try to get you out of the classroom , or 2) get your best friend`s backpack torn to pieces while she`s wearing it. The teacher told everyone to get out of the classroom. As I got ahold of it, I turned it of and put it in my backpack.The teacher wasn`t very happy when she couldn`t find the robot. She wasn`t any happier when she found her sell phone broken into pieces.'Umm ... Mrs.Smelter, can I go home now.?', I asked.'Sure.I`ll have to see what else that robot did.'       As I left, Olivian wasn`t happy.'Have you lost you mind?You brought that thing to life and it destroyed my backpack!I had twenty bucks in there! You have got to pay me twenty. Then we`ll see if we get that A we want.'Then she left.As I got home I explained what happened at school.She wanted to see it.That`s when Aly came to knock .'Can you come out ?I heard the craziest knews you wouldn`t believe.'       'Sure.Let me show you something first.'I showed her the robot and she gasped.'This is what I wanted to tell you!If that`s the robot that destroyed a classroom, then you are in so much trouble.The cops are looking for this.'I couldn` believe my ears.My robot is a wild criminal now?I hadn`t even spent a day with it.'Then lets make this day last.Do you like strawberry milkshakes?'       An entire week had passed until the cops found my robot.When they took it, I was very sad.'Hey, this has been the best week of my life.You should feel happy.'I was, but I was gonna miss my robot.' okay.Lets go get some candy.I need some.'

Item_Response: The Robot That Came Alive           Once upon a time there was a robot named RC-0722 he was first built to help tutor kids.   His inventor was a teenager named Bob. Bob built RC-0722 because his sister was struggling in school. RC-0722 was incredibly smart. Ever Since RC-0722 had been around bob's sister had been studying more because she enjoyed the way RC-0722 made the classes seem fun. Everything was going fine with RC-0722, but one day Bob wished RC-0722 was more than a tutor he wished he would be he friend.       The next day Bob woke up and found RC-0722 in front of him, Bob thought his sister had put him there but when he greeded RC-0722 responded 'hello Bob.' Bob could not belive his ears, RC-0722 had actually come to live.       For the next couple of weeks Bob kept RC-0722 hidden but he knew he could not hide   him forever. Thats when Bob came up with the idea that he would reprogram the robot so he could would only be a tutor again, but since RC-0722 was alive now he also had feelings so when he heard this he got really scared and ran away. That is how this story of a robot who wondered across the united states begins.       One week after RC-0722 had left Bob decided that he was gonna give up finding him.   On the other hand though RC-0722 wanted to return more than anything. The problem for RC-0722 began when he tried to return home but since he was only a tutor robot he didnt know where to go. RC-0722 began wondering his way through a thick forest that was right next to a big city. When RC-0722 reached this city he met new wonderfull people, but the person he enjoyrd meeting the most was a little girl named vivian who offered to help him find his way back.       On their journey RC-0722 and vivian lived many adventures but it was complicated for   RC-0722 to introduce himself so vivian decided to just call him RC. RC and vivian went to many villages to ask for maps or coordinates to follow so RC could go home. But most of the time they only heard people answer 'sorry,' 'we dont have any maps,' or they would say ' leave we are not gonna waste our only maps left giving them to you.       Vivian and RC were sad drepresed and with nothing to eat when they met a 19 year old   who liked the way RC looked and capacity to learn and teach new stuff, he figured that if he sold him he would get paid very well. This boy offered food and drinks to poor Vivian and RC. During diner the three had a very pleasant conversation, but before they went to sleep the boy attacked Vivian and shut off RC. After doing this the boy left with RC and left Vivian knocked out .       When Vivian was finally able to recover RC and the boy were already very far, she   decided she had to do something and then out of nowhere Bob and Vivian were face to face. neither one  of them knew it but they needed to work together if they wanted to save RC.       Bob and Vivian had traveled a long distance when they saw the boy with RC. Bob came   up with the idea that he would go in through one side and Vivian through the other. Vivian did exactly as she was told. She went in through the left bob went in through the right and they both were ready  to fight if they had to. Surprisingly RC was still intact and the boy who had stolen him was still trying to disable him.       After this Bob learned to think about how something you say make affect others before you say it .                                          The End

Item_Response: Two years ago Sydney made a robot so he could help her with her homework.The day the robot started working she stared to get all A's and B's. Her teacher Mr.Barnes started to wonder what was going on. He had never had a student that got those good of grades.He was an expert in robots.He suspected something was wrong. So right after class he told Sydney to stay after class so he could have a chat with her.When class was over he told her that she was doing well in his class and he said that he was going to make an after school appointment with her mom.She had to do something about it,and she had to do it fast.                                                                                      Right when Sydney got home she ran to her room.when she got to the robot she freaked out and didn't know what to do she looked for an off button,but she didn't  make one. She was thinking of what to do,but then she heard it.The doorbell went off, she hid the robot underneath her bed and ran down stairs.But before she could get to it she heard her moms voice and ran faster that she ever could until she saw him walking to her living room. When she walked into the living room she was greeted by Mr. Barnes with a huge smirk on his face.She felt like she was going to barf. she sat on her couch and started to listen to the teacher.After he was done talking about how good her grades. He got to the point he told her mom that he thought she was cheating. Sydney's mom told him that Sydney would never do such a thing. Then told him to get out immediately! he walked out the house and told her that he'll get proof.Then ran to his car after that crisis was over Sydney ran up the stairs to her room thinking what she was going to do with the robot.She only had one choice. She had to destroy it.            For that she had to wait for tomorrow  she ran to the bed and quickly fell asleep.The next day she woke up and ran to school.Anxious for school to be over she got in the halls and ran into  Mr. Barnes. Mr. Barnes told her that he would get proof and she WILL get expelled from school.At school she couldn't even constraint.She was thinking about what she was going to do to the robot.She couldn't just destroy it.She had to figure out what to with it, and figure out fast Mr.Barnes had another  meeting,But this time with her Dad.          She finally had an idea what to with the homework robot.She would just turn off the robot until she needed it.Now it was time to get to work.She ran home and turned off the robot and put it into her closet and covered it with her dirty clothes to make sure her mom doesn't see it. Then she ran downstairs to make sure her teacher doesn't see her father. When she got down there her dad told her that her teacher came by and he told him to go away and that his daughter was not cheating she was so realifed.        After that no problems came up with her robot.Sydney had been good and never used it again she got the good grades by herself and she felt good about herself.

Item_Response: Ana Diaz   May 23, 2013           THE USEFUL ROBOT THAT WAS FORBIDDEN                                   PART 1           There once was a robot that all of a sudden came alive when the scientist put some   gasoline. But the scientist knew that gasoline was forbidden. When company came to the scientists home, he always hid the robot. The scientist always hid the robot until one day.       Years passed and the robot knew how to work on the scientist's mines and farms.   Company came one day and the robot knew he had to hide in the closet. When the scientists let his friends come in and sit down, there was an odd noise in the closet. This odd noise was the robot powering down. When the robot was powering down, he fell in the buckets of gasoline the scientists had left there.       His friend said, 'what was that did you hear that?' Then the scientist said, 'what do you   mean I didn't hear anything.' The scientist said he was going to the restroom, but he was going to go to the closet and check what had happened. While he was in the closet the scientist's friends saw something flowing from the closet. That something was the gasoline that the robot fell on.       One of the scientist's friends said, 'lets follow the track.' They didn't know it was   gasoline, so they followed the pathway to the closet. In the closet they found the scientist, the robot, and the gasoline by then they knew it was gasoline. One of them said, 'how could you you know gasoline is illegal. Another one said, 'I'm going to tell the policemen.' As you can see this person wasn't really his friend.       His not so really friend told the policemen by then the scientist was getting ready to go to   jail. He gave the policemen his robot and gasoline and without any complaints the scientist went to jail. He was very sad, but he knew in the first place that gasoline was illegal.

Item_Response: The Journey of NWS-12           There once was a boy named John. John was the son of a coal miner. John was a lucky child because he had his own robot! The robot's name was NWS-12. NWS-12 was the type of robot that can move around easily and carry heavy loads. It even had a two way radio. John loved to wake up and see NWS-12. One day, the unthinkable happened.        John's mother called John to come down stairs. She said in a serious tone, ' John, your father is stuck in the mine, and they don't know how to get him out of there.' John ran upstairs into his room and bawled and bawled. Then all of a sudden, NWS-12 came in and was standing next to John. John thought he heard a voice calling his name. Then he heard it again. John then realized that it was NWS-12!       NWS-12 in a monotone voice proclaimed, 'John, I will go save your father.' John at first was still flabbergasted that he was talking to a robot, but soon calmed down. John asked questioningly, ' One, how are you talking, and two, how are you going to save my dad?' NWS-12 responded, ' To answer your first question, I don't know, to answer the other one, I will use the tools I have.'       NWS-12 was going to search the mine, and when he found John's father, he would drag him out. John asked an extremely important question, 'How will I contact you while in  the mine?' NWS-12 responded in an almost snotty way, ' Why with my radio of course.'NWS-12 would go into the mine ant the break of dawn the very next day.                                                                                                                                              John and NWS-12 slipped out of the house at 6:00 AM. Lucky for them, the mine was just a few hundred yards away. John and NWS-12 went over the plan. When NWS-12 found John's father, he would radio back to John. If anything went wrong, they had a code phrase, Dying Battery. When they were done they made sure the radio was working. The battery was 100%. NWS-12 was going in.                                                                                                                                       'Everything good in there?' John asked nervously over the radio. 'All good.' replied NWS-12. It was some time before anything exciting happened. Then NWS-12 called over the radio, 'I found him!' John was overjoyed! John's father was knocked out but still breathing. NWS-12 dragged John's father out of the mine about twenty minutes later.       By that time John's father was starting to come around. 'S-son? Is that you?' he said confusedly. John replied with enthusiasm, ' It sure is dad.' When the three got home, John explained every thing. His parents didn't believe him about NWS-12 coming alive. When he tried to show them that he could talk there was silence. It was as if NWS-12 had never lived.

Item_Response: Robbie The Robot       There once was a robot named Robbie and he loved to play with kids, everyday Robbie would babysit kids like a real babysitter would but he would play with them all day and cook for them too. Robbie loved kids and he loved babysitting them.               So it all started with a good book about fifty years ago and it was called 'I, Robot.' everybody loved it and even the kids. So one day someone got up and had a great idea of trying to make a robot to experiment on and have a little fun with it too, and then he showed it to one of his good friends and he loved it, so then they called a guy to discuss this amazing creature and have him come check it out. When he got there he inspected it and loved it, and so the next morning they all had a vote on it with all the people in the neighborhood and everybody loved it and they thought it could be the next big thing.           They came up with a campaighn called Robots Forever and then everybody got to working on the next big thing they called Robbie.   They started with making all the gadgets robotic and then they made a couple robots that were staff so they could be helped, the robot staff had a special piece of  shazam in it so that they would never run out. The next morning one of the staff got really sick and had to be rushed into the hospital, the doctor said that it was just the start of something horrible: Cancer. They were all shocked to here the news about it and quickly went back to work to make a robot that could take care of the patient.       The doctor called the next morning and said that the patient had passed away, they were bumbed but that doesn't mean they have to quit now because they just got started. So they went straight to work after the news and planned the funeral and who would be coming, so they started with a list: Mom, Dad, Brother, Sister, Cousins, Aunts, Uncles, Nieces, Grandparents and Friends.                                        TO BE CONTINUED.....

Item_Response: One average Tuesday morning I was walking through my lab to check on my robots, like I do everyday. They were all oiled, clean, and shiny. Nothing strange, except for the occasional dent or bump left in the robots. I didn't think anything of the marks, little did I know that that day my life would change.          'Nothing interesting ever happens these days,' I said aloud. 'I wish I could have an adventure.'   'Going to look at the old robots always cheers me up!' I thought.   So i walked toward the back of the laboratory. I opened the stainless steel doors and stepped inside. I looked around the tiny closet like room. there were robots crammed into piles, on shelves and sprawled across the floor. I was confused, 'This room is always clean and orderly.' I thought.   I began to pick up the robots one by one placing them in one straight line. Then I began to here buzzing and beeping. I spun around and behind me was a dusty old robot. I jumped and screamed. It quickley said in a monotonous voice, 'I mean you no harm, I must find treasure.'   'But you're an oliver 2013, you were made 50 years ago! You were a defect!' I said my voice shaking.   It came toward me and I stepped back. 'Must find treasure.' It said again.   'You're the one who dented my bots, aren't you?' I inquired.   'Yes. Help find treasure.'   'What treasure?' I shouted. But no answer. Oliver 2013 just turned and walked away. I followed, He wasn't causing any trouble he just walked out of my lab and outside. He kept walking until he suddenly stopped. His hand began to shake, and it began to change shape into a spoon of some kind. Then I realized it was a shovel. 'what are you doing?' I demanded.   Still I got no response. He just began to dig. He was incredably fast. He dug until he had been comletely ingulfed in a huge hole. I cautiosly stepped closer to the hole. It was so deep I couldn't see the bottom. Suddenly Oliver 2013 shot up out of the hole. He seemed to be carrying a case. When he came closer to me, he handed me the box and said, 'Treasure!' I slowly opened it curiously, It was filled with gold, Diomonds, and money!   I stared at the robot stunned by his discovery. Then leaped to the lab. 'I'm rich!' I yelled.         I called Oliver an placed him in my car, I tried asking questions about what it was and who made him but i got no response. He still would remain a mystery. But a mystery that would bring prosperity to the world. After I did some research I found that he could find gold or burried treasure. He can dig faster than any man or machine, and will change the world forever. When I got into town people thought I was crazy about Oliver. But what they don't understand is robots can change this Earth for the better.

Item_Response: Ambush and the Science Fair       'Hey mom, Hey dad! I'm home!' I shouted as I walked into my house. I threw my back breaking bag of pads and footballs on the dish washer and continued into my house. The moment I stepped in I could already smell the fresh aroma of freshly baked cookies that have been waiting for me on the kitchen table. The smell pulled me in, closer and closer but I had to pass. Tomorrow was the day of the big science fair and I needed to get my project done. I raced through the hallways and walked down the creaky stairs that entered into the basement, or what my parents called 'Jared's Lab' because of the amount of time I spent down there to finish my project. I heard my brother, Ryan, chatting away on his X-box which made it even harder to want to work on my project. First the cookies and now the urge of me wanting to play X-box! But I promised myself to not have any distractions that could cause me to not finish. There it was, standing under my desk light. It was the robot that I had been working on and my project that I would present. I called it Ambush. The name sounds unhappy, but that just described the way it looked. I have been trying to program it to do and feel what I do- when it is turned on; like a mirror image. I put in the last few screws and pieces until it was finally finished and made a bracelet that would light up if Ambush was turned on. The only problem was I could not test it or see if it works because Ambush can only stay on for a certain amount of time and I didn't want it to burn all of its energy. Who knows- it could only last for about 5 minutes, so I did not want to risk it. I left Ambush where he was and walked back up the basement stairs. It was late now- past 11:00 p.m. I headed to my room and just went straight to bed. I could not get my mind off of Ambush and the science fair. Then my eyes saw the time- it literally seemed like it 'flew.' It was hard to make out the numbers because I didn't  have my glasses on. I did see a very blurry '1' and '2:' but the other numbers I could not see. I just hoped that it wasn't too late to be able to get up and out of bed. I still kept my fingers crossed that Ambush would work for tomorrow.   'AAAAAAWW!' I yawned as I got out of bed. I could here the sounds of chirping birds and the warm sun, beaming in through my bedroom window. 'Wow!' I thought to myself 'I've actually woke up before my alarm clock.' Within a second ,y heart completely dropped. The power had gone out! There was no alarm clock!' I slipped on some shoes and walked across the hallway to wake up my mom, so she could drive me to school. I explained what had happened and she freaked too. The only reason we were so shocked is because I could have missed the science fair. I just don't know what time it starts, but I hoped it was not right now.Once I got downstairs,  I opened the refrigerator to grab some milk. As I lifted it up, I felt that it was warm from the refrigerator not having any power; so cereal wasn't available to eat. I sprinted over to the pantry to get some protein, breakfast bars and stuffed a bunch of them into my pocket to eat in the car. I grabbed my backpack, brushed my teeth, and took off for school.   Immediately, I bolted into the M.P.R, where the held the science fair.   'Mr. Staub! Your turn to present!' One of the judges announced. 'Perfect timing!' I thought to myself. I walked up to the stage to see the many people in the crowd staring right at me. It almost seemed that their eyes were beaming through me. Suddenly, I realized that the one thing I needed was Ambush. I nearly almost fainted, but instead I started to shake. 'Any day now!' One of the judges projected into the room. 'I... I d-don't have my p-project yet s-sir.' I said to the judges, freighted. Then I came up with an excuse to leave. 'M-may I go the... the r-restroom?' They nodded their heads but were not very happy. Once I was in the restroom, I pulled out my cellphone to call my mom. I NEEDED her to bring Ambush. In the middle of the conversation, I noticed something light up. It was my bracelet, meaning Ambush got turned on at my house. I figured it was the maid probably dusting off Ambush and accidentally turned it on. Then an idea hit me. 'Sorry! Gotta go mom. Bye!' If Ambush could really do what I do, I could just walk it to school, but from the bathroom. I would just have to remember all of the twists and turns that I would have to walk in order to get out of my house and into school. The first thing I had to do was remember how to get out of the basement. I started walking side to side, pondering, trying to picture exactly how to get through the garage door. Of course the ring of my cell phone had sounded. 'Hello?' I asked. It was my mom again. 'Ummm Jared- your robot is walking side to side and it shaking the house! Make it stop please.' I stopped walking to see if it would stop too. 'OK. It stopped. Thank you!' she said in relief. 'Uh mom... sorry but I need to walk it out of the house, so there is going to be some stomping until it is outside. I know you won't be able to fit it in your car so I have to walk Ambush to school.' I replied. 'Alright! I'll help you find the door. So walk forward, a little more. Stop! You are about to hit the wall. Go left, OK perfect. Now just walk forward and you will be out side. 'Is Ambush out yet?' I asked. 'Yes. Oh, I have to go take Ryan to basketball practice so you are on your own now. You should know how to get Ambush to school from our house because we live right next door from it.' I heard her yelling for Ryan to get in the car. 'Bye mom!' I said. Then I slipped the phone back in my pocket. I pictured that I was outside of my house and where to turn on the streets. 'So I take a left, right then straight.' I whispered to myself. I began to walk him by going straight and so on.   Within a minute, I could feel the floor shaking rapidly beneath me. Ambush was in the school! I had to get him immediately because he could run out of juice in any second. Before I ran out of the bathroom, I turned Ambush off from my bracelet, so he would not move. I checked the nearest hallway. there he was, with his 'mad' face, just standing in front of the clear door. I opened the door in front of him, allowing Ambush to walk inside. I turned him back on and he walked right beside me until we reached the M.P.R. I was not  nervous anymore, considering I had a gigantic robot by my side. I took a deep breath and then walked inside.   'Sorry it took so long but I had a really bad... uh stomach ache. But I have my project right here.' The judges had all started laughing because when I turned around to point at Ambush, Ambush did the same and pointed to nothing. I joined in the laughter as well, with a tiny giggle, but continued with my speech. 'I have programed him to do what I do, with the control of this bracelet. I pointed to my wrist and showed the audience. He does what ever the person who is wearing this is doing. I have worked very hard on this project, with a total of about a year. So uh, that concludes my presentation, thank you!' They all clapped in amazement and rewarded me with a first place ribbon. Once I received the winner's prize, then I knew that a year of hard work has finally paid off.       'So what did you guys think?' I asked. One of the few people woke up and replied, 'What do you mean?' 'The story I just read to you- did you listen to any of it?' I again asked, but this time more angry. 'Your only job for this whole wiring club thing is to listen to story, and you still didn't pay attention?!' They all nodded their heads 'No.' I just handed my narrative in and headed home from the school library. I hoped that I got a first place ribbon like I did in my story. Maybe this would be something that I won't be able to get off of my mind at night- just like Ambush and the science fair.

Item_Response: The Science Fair was coming up in about a month, and  my friend Jake and I were paired up and wanted to get a head start. After school, Jake came over to my house and we were thinking of ideas.                            After about two and a half hours, I pitched an idea. I thought of we could go big and make a robot. Jake was on board. First, we needed lots of materials to get started like wires, metals, and tons of other materials. They were too expensive in stores, so we went on amazon and bought it online. We started pitching ideas on what it could be like. Maybe it could have wheels or could carry materials, it could be remote controlled                                                     The next day, the materials came. One of the problems were their wearn't any instructions and we had to either go online or figure it out on our own. Making a robot was hard but we didn't give up. We worked on it all night and we wearn't even half way done. Our parents helped us a little and it was getting easier.                                 Jake and I were working on it for five hours and we were almost done. We were about to put in a couple more wires in the robot and then charge it. After it was done charging, we were gonna test it. We were proboly hoping we need to add more wires in to it but I was wrong. It was moving one-hundred percent perfectly.                                                         Today was the science fair and Jake and I were hoping we are going to win. Later in the contest, we were in the top two. The other project was a volcano exploding chocolate. After they pronounced the winner, we won

Item_Response: The clock in the hospital ticked twelve o clock. The hospital is silent. It has been abandoned for just a week and the doctors just left a few items , a racks of doctors supplies and there Mr. Gower robot helper, he was uncharged and hadn't moved since the hospital was abandoned             Mr. Gower look like a cabinet on wheels. He had multiple locked drawers as a body. One of his wheels moved. Slowly the little robot moved inched to the door. Slowly picking up speed. Once he was outside of the room the small robot he was at full speed ready to meet the doctors, nurses, and patients.              The robot looked and looked but couldn't find anyone. The only people he saw was the people outside of the musty window. Mr. Gower decided that he was going to escape. His first thought was to turn the power supply back on. The robot swiftly went down the stairs. When  the robot reached the bottom of the stairs he saw all of the switches for different thing. None of them were labeled, they were just colored coded. The little robot went back up the stairs.             The small robot look all through the hospital for a way out. He looked and looked and looked. He finally gave up. He went back and forth  trying to see a way out. After going back and forth one hundred times the robot noticed something shinny and small in his wheel. Slowly he grabbed the shinny figure. After he removed the figured he could see what it was. It was his way out. It was a key.             He went to the door as fast as his wheels could take him. He pushed and turned the key in the slot. The door opened and the robot was free.

Item_Response: This story began at 8:48 p.m on April 12,2013 in Memphis,Tennessee.Our family,the Hutcherson family,were wandering around a toy store to buy new toys.There was Mom and Dad with Annie,my babysister,in the baby dolls section looking at toys for Annie.And then there was me,Jack,looking for awesome looking robots.About 30 minutes later,I find this dirty looking robot behind all of the cleaned looking ones.Its body is painted all black.The fact that shocked me the most was,it's the biggest robot in the toy store.Two yard tall and 1 yard wide.At first,I didn't want to buy it,but then I started feeling bad for the little guy.So,I told Mom and Dad to buy it.          We went back home.Annie was asleep,so Dad had to be careful of carrying her inside their room.After Dad put Annie to bed,they watched a movie in the living room,while I play with the old robot I bought in my room.It looks really cool.He has three buttons in where his stomach is place.I pressed the first button and the robot said,'Your the best friend ever!'I pressed the second button and its legs moved.Then I pressed the last button and its arms moved.While its arms were moving,I started to see this button in the bottom of its right armpit.I don't know if that's really where they're supposed to be but,it seemed like it was hidden in there.          My body started to get this creepy feelings I can't even explain.I started to get cold.Even though I was getting scared of what might happen,I still pressed it.It was just a toy,there's nothing to get scared of.I was wrong.The robot's eyes started glowing.I stepped away,leaving it on the floor laying down.It stood up by itself and started to walk towards me.I wanted to shout but couldn't becuase I was too afraid of what it might do to me.          It stopped walking when it was about 4 yard from me.My body started to feel a little bit less scared,but I still stayed still in the corner of the room.It finally spoke.It said,'Don't be afraid,I am your best friend.'After what the robot said,I didn't feel scared anymore.I started walking toward him.I asked him if he's alive and he responded the word 'YES'.Instead of that making me feel creeped out,it made me feel great.I have a best friend that's a robot,a robot that controls itself.I carried him to my bed and talked to him the whole night.          The next day,I woke up and didn't see him where he was last night.I looked for him and found him cleaning my clothes inside my closet.He was taller though.I told him to come out.He shrunk while he was coming out.Well,that shocked me.He played many games with me in my room.I kept it a secret from my family though.They might get scared and hit him with bats or something.I had to go in and out of my room every hour.       Every morning I wake up,I always see him doing my chores,but I'd always tell him to stop so he could play with me.My parents sometimes comes in to my room with a shocked face.They never found out about my robot best friend untill I told them the next year I bought him.I was very happy they didn't get scared and hit him with bats.I was also happy because he became my best friend.Without him,I wouldn't have a better childhood than what I expected.

Item_Response: How Robots Came Alive                                  December 24, 2053 (Christmas Eve)          Daddy tomorrows Christmas Phillip could hear his littlest daughter Sally singing over and over again. She was 7 and the most cheerful out of any of his children. Phillip loved this time of year. He loved the Christmas specials on TV, the gift exchange and most of all visiting family. He lived in Missouri where the weather is not too bad. But he heard this year they were going to have the worst thunderstorm ever in the state of Missouri. 'Go to bed or Santa's not going to come', he told Sally. As soon as he knew it she was in her bed fast asleep.                        December 25, 2053 (Christmas Day)          When she woke up she started screaming Santa Came Santa Came. Soon they started opening presents. She got a remote controlled robot. She went outside and started playing with it. About twenty minutes later it started to rain. She ran inside and then remembered she forgot the robot outside. Phillip told her its too late because it started thunder storming. She started crying. Plus Grandma cancelled Christmas dinner he said madly. He threw the phone at the wall were it shaddered into pieces. He got so mad at himself for throwing the phone that he also started crying. They both cried and cried until the day was over.                                     December 26, 2053           Sally woke up to a new voice she heard outside. She walked to the voice to see that her old robot was now bigger and made of metal instead of plastic. The robot told her the whole story about how he became alive when he got struck by lightning. After that they played and became best friends ever. Hey, Grandma even rescheduled Christmas to New Years Eve.And they all lived happily ever after... until the aliens took over, but that's a different story.

Item_Response: The Robot                                                 By: Trace Young              One day there was a kid. His name was Bob and he loved science and building. He had alot of scraps from previous experiments and he decided he wanted to build a robot. So he got to work. His plans were that the robot would play with him whenever he wanted. He tried as hard as he could because he didnt have a brother or sister so he was always bored. He worked on it for days and days but he didnt know if he was doing it right. Finally he thought he was finished.               He asked the robot if it would play with him but nothing happened. Bob got really mad because he put all his effort into the robot. He ran over and pushed the robot down. 'CLICK' he heard. 'What do you want to play, Bob' Said the robot.                'Yes!' Said Bob. It worked! Later that day Bob went on and showed the world his invention and everyone loved it.                 'Tag, you're it!' Said the robot.                 All of the people in the world wanted a robot so Bob opened a company called Robo-fun inc. and all the robot were for sale and they all looked different. But one robot was not for sale and it was Bobs robot, who he named Bobby Jr. or you could call him  John Johnny-Jo John-John for long. Bob also found another robot he named Theodore Talatae.                  Soon all the kids had a robot and they were happy. Every day of the year Bob made a national day where everyone goes to the park with there robot to play tag.

Item_Response: DING DING DING! sounded the bell. Finally, school was over! But it was not a very happy moment for all of the members of Mr. Crawford's science class. He assigned us a LOT of homework, and it was all due by the next day. What was the homewwork, you ask? We had to build a robot. A robot! I mean really, we're only in sixth grade, its not like we're engineers! Of course, its not THAT hard. All the robot has to do is move a tennis ball a few feet across the room without us touching the ball or the robot, but still, how are we supposed to build our own robot! 'Luke, aren't you going to leave?' asked Mr.Crawford. 'Wha- oh yeah! Sorry!' I said, snapping back to reality. I grabbed my things and left, thinking that I might as well start working on the robot as soon as I got home, that way I wouldent have to stay up TOO late.                 'MOM! I'M HOME!' I called out into my house after arriving. 'Good honey, welcome back.' Responded my mom. I took off my backpack, and went out to the garage to see what I could use from there to build my robot. I managed to find a bunch of good supplies to work with, and I got to work.                                                         *             *                *             Finally, finished! And it only took me two hours! My robot stood about two feet tall, with some old lightbulbs as the 'eyes', 'legs'made out of an old four wheel scooter, and a plow in the front made out of a broken shovel in the front to move the ball. I made a simple motor by the wheels to move my 'robot', and to be energy efficient, the motor was powered by a solar panel that I put on the robots head. The final thing I had to do was give my robot a name. Tobor was robot backwards, so I decided that that was a good name for it. I put 'Tobor' outside and left him there so he could charge, and then I used the rest of my time that night to watch TV then go to bed.                 BOOM! CRACK! I woke up, startled. I heard a storm brewing outside, so I started to fall back asleep. Then I rememberd Tobor. I jumped out of bed, and ran outside, but it was alredy too late. On my way out, I saw a bolt of lightning streak across the sky and strike Tobor. I figured he was a goner, but then the strangest thing happened. I saw, peering at me where Tobor was just standing, was a pair of glowing lights, about two feet above the ground. 'Thats strange.' I thought. So I carefully walked over and found that the lights where lightbulbs. Familiar looking lightbulbs... Tobor! I ran over and saw, to my surprise, that Tobor was moving towards me. On its own. It stopped right by me, and did a quick spin around as if to say 'Yay! Im alive!' 'I must be dreaming,' I thought.  So I went back to bed.                 Turns out, I wasn't dreaming. Tobor was waiting for me in the kitchen when I walked downstairs. He greeted me with that same spin that he gave before, and followed me everywhere. I took him on the bus with me to school, wich got me a very stange look from everybody on the bus. I brought Tobor with me into science class, where the robot testd were just begining. 'Ah, Luke. Your late. Since you've had so much extera time to work on your robot, why dont you take your turn now?' Said Mr. Crawford with a sneer on his face. 'Sure. Tobor, bring that ball to Mr. Crawford.' I said. Of course, Tobor immediatly drove over, scooped up the ball, and brought it to Mr. Crawford. Mr. Crawford was speechless. 'Wha- what else can it do?' He stammared. 'Anything. For instance: Tobor, go bring me those books on the floor over there.' I responded. Tobor obeyed immidiatly. 'Well done, Luke. You can get some candy from the bag on my desk as a prize.' said Mr. Crawford. Of course, Tobor got that for me too.

Item_Response: It was 12 o'clock, midnight. I had worked on him all evening, and was very tired after a hard day. I was asleep. He sat motionless in the garage, as though he were a lampost. But he couldn't do anything about it. At least, that's what I thought.              I woke with a start. Something banged hard against a wall, but I could not dtermine where the sound was coming from. I was still half asleep when I first heard the noise. There it was agin. What could it be? I thought. I couldn't really process anything. My brain was still tired. I needed more sleep. But I couldn't help but wonder, where was that noise coming from? Could it just be my father, doing some late night work? I had no idea what it was. It wasn't like me to be this curious, but I had to investigate.             I slipped out of bed and put on my bathrobe. I searched my empty floor for my slippers, but could not feel them anywhere. So i went to my doorway and found my flip flops. It was the best I could do. Our whole house was wooded, and very cold on barefeet. I twisted the doorknob slowly and carefully, not wanting to awake anyone near this hallway. I slowly walked out, tip toeing my way to the living room. I heard it again.            BANG! It went. But the sound seemed fainter. I guessed I was headed in the wrong direction. I turned back, heading toward the garage. That was usually where I found my dad finishing up projects late at night. I had just made it to the entry way.                                                                                                    There it was.                     He stood in the middle of the doorway, staring straight ahead. It was him. My creation, my robot.            Did I leave him out? I thought. Maybe I just forgot to put him away. But then it happened. barely noticable, but I saw it. His head tilted, leaving it at an angle. Then slowly, he turned himself to face me.           Was this really happening? What have I done! Then, I took one last glance at him, and ran. Back to my room. I slammed the door.           My mother woke up, and sat with me on my bed. I didnt tell her about anything that I saw. She would never believe me. I told her, 'I was just getting a drink. I got scared because I was alone, and ran back.'                 I woke up late that morning for not having slept at all last night. I went straight to the garage, but the robot was sitting in the middle of the cement, where I had left him yesterday evening. I must have dreampt it. That couldn't really happen, could it? But then it hit me. My brother!           He was only nine, but he loved to pull pranks on people. I'm sure it was him. But what if it wasnt? I would have yelled at him for nothing! I wouldn't accuse him of my dream. And besides, I am prone to sleepwalking!

Item_Response: Shadow Keeper                                                                      It was just another Monday morning on the farm, I got up, ready to check the plants, feed the cows, feed the chickens, feed the horses, check for eggs, water the garden, eat breakfast.  There were so many things to do on the farm, it was overwhelming!  As soon as I finished eating, I made a checklist of things that I need to do.               Checklist           Check plants Feed animals water garden Check for eggs                                         As soon as I finished making the list, I walked down towards the fields.  I inspected the fields and then took off towards the chicken coop.  There were several eggs, so I took one of the baskets that were right there and put them in.  I sprinkled chicken food in the coop snf watched the chickens scramble around.  I darted off to the cow pasture and poured water into the tub and put special grains in the buckets.  I then scurried off to the horse stable and visited each stall, but before I was going to feed them.  Something caught my eye.  In the storage large storage room, the door was open and something was inside.  I backed up and took a better look, but before my mind realized it, the large shadow lurched in my direction.  I screamed and fell over with a thud.  The shadow was right over me.       Before I knew it, I was in a dream.  This was no ordinairy dream, this was a trap.  I was surrounded by darkness, and out of the shadow walls came the shadow.  It's majestic sleek horse-like body glinted in the darkness.  He was tall, and his coat was a purple-black shadow color.  A sudden voice surrounded the area.    'Alice,' it said.       'How do you know my name? And who are you?' I said back.       'Alice, that doesn't matter. But I am Shadow Keeper, keeper of all secrets and shadows,'  he responded.       'Why are you here?' I asked.       ' Because, Alice, I am here to help you get through.  There is a gate opening and you   need to stop it,' he said.       ' But why me?'  I asked.       ' Because, with me and you on a team, we can stop the gate from opening,' he stepped   under a small opening with light shining on his figure.  He was a horse, but not just any horse, a robot horse.       ' Okay,' I said.       With one stomp of his hoof, a swirly portal appeared.       ' I'll meet you back there,' he said.       I leaped through the portal and in a second, I was standing in front of the storage area.  Seconds later, Shadow Keeper appeared right in front of me.  He turned to the side and I hopped onto Shadow Keeper's smooth steel back.  I held onto hid neck as he started into a smooth collected canter.  The wind blew my blonde hair back, and I straightened up and held onto the reins that I hadn't noticed.  The rush of cantering had never felt so good.       When we got to the gate, it was a swirling red and black floating circle. I could'nt see a problem, but if Shadow Keeper said it was, I was going to believe it too.  A sword appeared to my right and together, Shadow Keeper and I moved in unisin.  He lunged towards it and then turned to the left abruptly and I slashed the sword across the gate.  The gate sliced into two pieces and fell apart.       As soon as it was over, I was trrasported back to my room.  It was 8:30pm and it was dark.  I wasn't sure what had happened, but I went out to my balcony and looked into the sky.  A certain star looked like Shadow Keeper, and it glinted, and I heard Shadow Keeper's voice in my head.  It said...       'Alice, I am very proud of you.  Thank you for closing that gate with me.  If you hadn't done that, by now, your world would've probably been destroyed by now.  Thanks again,' he said.       I was happy, and now, it was time to get a good night's sleep.  In my dreams, I couldn't stop thinking about the adventure.

Item_Response: 'We should get out of here Kattie!' said my BFF Amanda.  We were at the abandoned junk yard at the end of town, and I loved going to scary places.  Amanda on the other hand, just wanted to go home and forget all about it.  'You know this place is supossed to be haunted' she said for the hundredth time.  'That's exactly why we came here' I replied in annoyence.  ' Now, first thing we gotta do, is climb that fence!'.  Being the gymnast that I am, I cleared the fence in one easy front flip.  Amanda, of course, took about a million hours just to get to the top of the fence.  'I'm stuck!!' she cried.  'Stay there, I'll get you!' I belowed up to her.  I started to climb up the fence, but then she yelled down, 'Kattie, just go without me!'.           'Scaredy cat' I muttered under my breath as I dropped to the ground.  All around me were piles and piles of trash of all kinds.  Old cars, bruised bananas, busted lamps,...and a shiny silver key.  I picked up the key.  It felt smooth and cool in my hand.  A booming noise shook the earth.  Poor Amanda was so startled, that she let go of the fence and fell to the ground.  Luckily she wasn't hurt.  A blinding light filled the sky.  I expected it to start raining, but instead, colors started swirling all around me.  In a burst of pink, blue, and green, I held in my hand a tiny, little robot.           I screamed, Amanda screamed, the robot screamed too.  I dropped the thing and took off.  .......Amanda and I never stopped running until we got home.  Maybe some day we'll go back to the junk yard.  Maybe.

Item_Response: The Robot Who Almost was Alive                      ' Tony do you actually think we should be here, because it seems wrong to be trying to steal a robot just to do our homework,' said my brother from the other side of the room.                       ' George it's, just stop being a buzz kill,' I said in a annoyed voice.                         The room was filled with electronics and dots and a whole bunch of stuff that I have no clue what they were.  I couldn't wait to get my hands on that new invention they call a robot, it's really human like but it has a computer voice.  And sometimes you can actually make him look like an exact replica of anyone you want. And guess what that's the robot that I'm about to rub my hands on!               'George I found it, it's right here. Finally after months of dreaming of it I basically have it in my hands, right in front of me,' I screamed in the most joyfull voice.              'Really? I didn't think you would find it. Actually I had no faith in you at all....in fact all my friends thinik the same thing,' said my little brother with a dumb look on his face.          'George you told your friends about this secret mission, you totally blew our cover, now the police are probably going to come searching....FOREVER! Great now we probably have the police right on our tails. But, we have to hurry if we want to get this baby home,' I said basically angrily.            All I have ever wanted (the past few months) was a robot that does homework.  And that's what I plan on stealing tonight.                'Okay George we have to get out of here before the police get here, hurry,'  I said in a low but hurried voice.              When finally we got out of that computer/electronic wonderland my brother and I got home with ro-buddy (that's my name for him, I pre-named him) I set him right beside my bed looking like I had just killed somebody and was hiding the dead body in my room, when suddenly we heard police officers and don't get me started on the lights, they were flashing everwhere, and since we live right next door to the computer/electronic wonderland we can hear a lot of stuff.  When I turned the lights on to see what was happening something miraculous happened.....               ' Ummmmm...Tony, look right beside your bed please, because I really think your gonna love it.' Said my brother.                                   So I as my younger brother said and when I turned around I saw the most marvilous scene ever, my robot was up by it's self and when I was about to say something the words just wouldn't come out. So after a while the robot said something that I could barely understand.              ' Hola, personas de tierra, puedes cambiar mi lenguage a ingles por favor?'  Said the robot that was sitting right next to me.                    ' Uhhhh, Tony do u speak spanish?' Murmurred my brother.                               ' Unfortunatly no,' I whispered in a sad voice.                 ' Okay Tony we have to get this thing back to the building before we ruin it,' said my little brother all worried.                     I kept touching all these buttons, and for some odd reason the robot kept saying stuff in spanish like one phrase he said ' AYYY,  si continuas haciendo eso voy a regresar a ser un pedazo de electrinco, por favor para.'                      Suddenly I heard a beeping voice it went like 'BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!' And that was the end for all of us, except George!                     'My ro-buddy hes gone!!!!!!  NOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!!!' I screamed so loud I pretty sure the whole world could here me.  \                           THE END!!!

Item_Response: My Day With a Robot   By: Brendon Bussiere                 Hi, I'm Ricky and I'm going to be telling you about my day with a robot.  My dad's an inventor and he's always coming up with new ideas and inventions that usually don't work.  It all started on Saturday morning when I woke up.             It was around 8:00 a.m. when i woke up and got out of bed.  I went down stairs and got a bowl of cereal for breakfast.  My dad was sitting on the couch watching Good Morning America when in came downstairs.  'Good morning' he said 'good morning' I replied.  'You won't believe what I invented this morning' he said 'a robot!' ' does it work' I said ' Uh it needs a little work' he said.  that didn't surprise me.              When i was done my breakfast I went into the garage to see the robot, it wasn't there.  'Dad i called inside 'I don't see your robot' I said ' Oh it's there all right' he said 'You can't miss it.'  I looked around and then out of the corner of my eye saw something move in the corner.  I went over to check it out and when I got there I couldn't believe my eyes I saw a real live working robot!  Then it said in a weird voice 'Hello' I said 'Hi' 'Would you like to go outside' it said' 'Sure' I said.  I went inside and said 'Dad' I'm going outside to play' he said 'OK be back before six' I said 'OK' and that's where my adventure begins.             When i went back into the garage the robot had out a bunch of balls to play with.  we went outside and started to play.  We had a blast we played soccer which he was really good at, basketball, and football.  The ball went over the fence a couple of times because the robot had a great throwing arm.  After that we went out for some ice cream and a walk on the pier.  The robot did not get any ice cream because he could not eat.  Then when we were almost home he said ' I'll race you back' i said 'Sure'.  We raced back, I'd say it was fair but he ended up winning.  We went into the garage and he said that was the best day he would probably ever have.  I turned him off and went inside.  I went and layed down on my bed and did some thinking maybe my dad wasn't so crazy after all.  I decided to name the robot Fred.  Then i thought about how much fun I had and how it was too bad the day was over.  And that's my day with a robot!

Item_Response: 'Work. Work! Come alive and do your duty,' It was 7:13 when the mastermind Dr. N. Sane shouted this from his laboratory. His masterpiece rose up from the ground in a cold stony silence. The hulking mass of steel flickered to life like a bear coming out from hibernation. It's chest glowing a very faint blue color and its eyes shaped like bananas opening up with a fiery orange color full of hatred. 'You have come here to seek revenge against the world! 'You will start out as a basic self-driving car, but when the time comes you know what to do.'            As the Dr. said he would, the robot would drive people around carefree. After he finished that job he started to explore volcanoes and collect information for the scientists, but no one knew his true plan. One day when the time was right he used his robotic drill to make a giant hole to let the lava flow out on the surrounding city. He charged into the city with nothing to stop him. Then it struck him and he had a change of heart (actually he had  change of gears).            He decided that pillaging cities and burning down towns wasn't what he wanted, he wanted to help out the kitten shelter and make friends with people and animals like othe robots. But, he sensed a problem, abut he couldn't quite put his finger on it. Then it hit him (not the idea the lava dumbo). He went tumbling down the streets stuck in the lava. He didn't have any idea how to stop the lava. He kept rolling down the streets and eventually rolled out. Having no idea how to stop the lava, he walked over to the water tower to get a drink. He took his drill and drilled a hole in the side of the water tank. He gulped down all the water he wanted to cool himself off. Then he realized that all the water pooring out would solidify the lava. He just sat back and watched the problem solve itself.            The next day when he came back he found almost everything destroyed. When he called out for people no one responded. Then, he sat down and cried. I think we have all learned a lesson here; it is that robots can help scinetists, make friends, and drive cars, but when an evil robot tries to change to these robot ways he ends up burning and suffocating people and a city.

Item_Response: BANG! Sora felt a hand smack the back of her head, in anger Sora wiped around to see who dared touch her head. She was surprised to see her bestfriend laughing on the ground because of Sora's reaction. Sora felt her face begin to get hotter, she noticed a lot of kids walking around her and Luna because of it. Luna qucikly got up and grabbed Sora's wrist, 'come on, I need to show you something cool!' Luna said as she dragged Sora out of the sidewalk and into an ally.      In the ally Luna laid Sora deeper and deeper into a darkness that seemed that the more they walked the more Sora felt the creeping eyes of cats,rats, and maybe a stalker. Sora tugged on the back of Luna's shirt, 'where are we going? its getting really dark and my roomate might lock the door on me! We're in our 3rd year in highschool Luna! I don't have time to be playing games like this!' Sore protested as she kept walking slower and slower but, Luna made sure she keptted up. 'we're only here so i can show you a Chobits.' Luna replied, Now Sora stopped completey in her tracks, 'you found a Chobits!? those robots that sound,look,act, and feel like a human!? I thought they only had those in Japan! how'd you get one?' she asked shocked yet excitly, 'easy.' she answered sharply, 'its for us. that means Igot it through my ungle!!' she snickered as Sora ran after her. Finally they reached the end of the ally, yes a deadend but Luna didn't panick, she looked up at the full moon and in a loud voice she started speaking Japanese, Sora was heavly confused but didn't know what todo so she just stood their, waiting to be told something. Finally Luna stopped, Her golden hair seemed to be glowing, and her body seemed to be glowing red like comething that had just gotten cooked but was still warm. Luna looked over at Sora and grabbed her hand, then began talking in Japanese again, Sora felt a strong warmth flowing through her body. Her brown hair glowing a different color, it wasn't like Luna's whos yellow hair suddenly turned a beasuitful gold and looked like something only a painter could make! Suddenly Luna stopped talking, a Cold rush fell right down Sora's back that made her fall to the ground, after regaining her wramth which was cruly sucked out of her Sora found a Human lying in front of her, but something about this human was different, and Luna was no where to be seen.      Sora didn't have a choice and carried the body all the way back to her room, surprisingly, her roommate was nowhere to be found either, confused and angry that Luna left her with a most likely dead body Sora placed it on her roommates bed, since she didn't want her own getting dirty.

Item_Response: Crash, went the window in my room. The glass landed everywhere in my room, luckily I was not hurt.'Matthew whats going on in your room?' my mother calls from the kitchen. 'Nothing.' I quickly answer back. But the truth was that the robot that I got for Christmas this year (BN/4c5) all of a sudden grew four feet and flew out of my window. And when I said flew I literally mean he even took his now life size jet-pack, (that came with him when I got him for Christmas) put it on and flew into my window but still made it outside.            I quickly jumped out of my window and ran after him. I passed a couple of houses and than was on Main St. I could just barely see my robot. BN/4c5 was on the top of City Hall. There was a problem though because I knew I could not get him down unless I could have some one with a helicopter to get him down. Then there lied another problem, after i got BN/4c5 in the helicopter I would have to turn him off.            I turned around and ran to my friend Anthonys' house because his father was a cop in Nashua. Anthony answered the door on the first knock. 'Matt whats up,' Anthony said 'Come in' he said without letting me answer his question. He led me to his room. 'Anthony,' I said ' You know the robot

Item_Response: All robots have a reason for their creation.Even if it is picking fruit like the Agribots,or an important job like Mr.Gower saving lives.                          The Gemini-Scout is of course to help people,but it also can save lives.It brings food,water,and other necessary needs.It can take wounded people to safety.It collects information,like test the air for toxins and tells were it's safe to explore. It is easy to use and is remote controlled like a video game.It is small but has every thing a robot might need.Like,strength,steering,talking,and climbing.                          The Dante 2 climbs into volcanoes looking for holes in the creators.It's a pretty awesome job if you ask me.It has eight legs like a spider to help it climb up volcanoes,and steep walls.It gathers data about the gases that come out of the hole or vent.So now the scientists can study a volcano up close while being safe in their lab.                           Then last but not least Mr.Gower,he is a robot that works in hospitals.   He can talk which helps the nurse's and Dr's.He is built with doors and boxes that helps him carry medicines,shots,and maby some paper work.But like I said all robots have a reason for their creation.

Item_Response: This story will be about a robot who all of a sudden comes alive. This story will take place at a science laboratory, a dump and a school. the characters will be a lively robot a young girl named Elizabeth and a mad scientist named Dr.latte. the plot will be 1st the young girl finds a letter that Dr. latte wrote. next she will go to school and keep the letter then she will go to the place described in the letter next she will find nothing but junk scrap metal then when she is about to leave she hears a rustling noise and walked to the noise and finds a old rusted robot that suddenly comes alive.                     One day a small girl named Elizabeth was walking to school and she found a letter in which contained these words 'dear whoever is reading this by now i am probably long gone but on the back of this piece of parchment is a map to get to the scrap yard please if you are brave enough take the key and there is probably still a little oil left it says it stays good forever but you might have to go buy some there is probably some at any hardware store in your area any way please go to the junk yard and fix up my little angel before Dr. latte gets her.' after that Elizabeth just noticed the key, the oil and the picture she looked on the back and in black smudged ink she should could only make out the words Dr. latte.                       after that she went to the junk yard and looked around but didn't see anything so when she started to leave she heard a low scratchy voice it sounded a lot like 'help me' but Elizabeth couldn't really tell then she walked over to the sound and saw a robot and it looked like it couldn't move so she put what was left of the oil on there and suddenly the robot sprang to life.

Item_Response: Rose the Robot                Hi! My name is Margarita Aparicio. I am going to write about a robot coming alive! Do you want to know what is going to happen? Well keep on reading!         First, it all started when a teacher said to her class that there was going to be a contest. And that the stundents had to make something for the science fair. Everbody had normal science ideas,but ther was a weird idea someone had. It was that a girl named Moncia wanted to make a robot. At first she tought it was not a good idea. But then after thinking about it she decide to do it.          Second, she went to her house and started doing all the work. Then, she had been in her room for a long time and then she finally finished the robot. So, then the next day she had to present it to the class and when she took of the blanket everybody was amazed to see the robot.So then Monica started to tell her presentation. Everbody was paying really good attention to her. Then, after the presentation was finished everybody was getting up and going to Monica's desk to see the robot.Then itn was time to go to lunch recess.Then Monica got the robot and went to lunch.            Third,while she was eating her robot was sitting next to her. So then, some kids past by and dropped a glass of water in the robot. So then the robot started to stand up and running around like a crazy person. After a few moments it stoped. Then everbody started screaming.Then, the robot started to run again. Monica went to go chase the robot but he was to fast for her!!!! Next, the robot kept on destroying things like breaking the windows with his arms and just making a huge miss. And then he stoped again a looked at Monica and Monica lokked at the robot. Finally like it was made by hand it started to run out of batteries. Moncia went next to robot and the robot said bye. Then finally, Monica looked around and saw a huge miss in the cafteria.               Finally, Monica learned a lesson to never ever do a robot again. And she also had to clean up the cafteria. Then, Monica put batteries on the robot again but in her house.Then she got use to playing with the robot after school every single day!!! And the robot was so happy too as well as Monica was.They played many things. Also, Monica tought the robot how to speak. And she also named the robot. Her name was Rose. And they were happy being toghter.That's my story.What's yours?

Item_Response: ?       My Robot Comes Alive            By: Kelly Meinhart                     It all started one afternoon when I got home from school. I decided to get out my homework and just do it so I wouldn't have to do it later. I opened my binder and started working on my homework. I found the picture of the robot I had doodled at school today. I took it out and decided it wasn't that good after all. I crumpled it up, not wanting anyone to see my robots and threw it in the trash. Then I got started on my homework. I had been working intensively for 1 hour straight, when I heard some weird robot sounds I figured I was probably holusinating from all that hard work I had done. But, no I was wrong, 'BEEP' I heard again. In my mind I figured, nothing wrong with going to check it out. So, I did and you will NEVER believe what I saw.        No this can't be right I thought. Right in front of my eyes was my diasterious robot that I had doodled. My first instinction was to run and go tell my parents, but no they would just think it was all a lie, I had to keep this to myself, no one not even my best friend could know about this. All of a sudden I heard, ' You must save me I amost just died.' I replied back, 'Yeah that was kinda the point.' We then had a whole argument about the trashinh her, and we finally got to the argreement that i would let her stay for 2 days, but then she must go back home, in other words the garbage can.        I then heard the door open, it was my mom, oh no you must hide I thought. I snached the robot ran upstairs and hide her in my closet. I then whispered, 'Don't you dare say a word, we can't let her know you here.' 'Fine then' the robor said sarcastically. I heard the door open, 'Hey is everything okay up her' my mom said anixously. 'Yep' I answered, 'Actually I am just working on a surprise for you.' 'So sweet.' 'Can I just get something from you closet.' 'NO' I screamed, ' I mean that's where your surprise is.'        Finally, it was time to get to sleep, today had been the weirdest day EVER. I really wish that robot had never showed up I thought. Of course I couldn't say anything infront of my sister. I turned of the lights and just imagined that this had never happened. It was impossible though, there is no way I am going to sleep, no way in the world.        Tomarrow morning finally came, I opened my closet door, and nothing was there, but, but, something had been there. I tip toed out to find the robot a step away from my parents bed room. 'Oh no I screamed this can't be happening.' I snached the robot and shoved her out. She told me, 'I must go home? my family needs me.' I tried telling her in the best way possible, 'You are at home.' I then saw billions of robots come out of hiding saying, 'We are here to take over, we are here to take over!' I then screamed, 'NOOOOOO'        I then woke up, my parents had heard me screaming, 'Kelly are you okay?' they asked softly. 'No i'm not these robots were about to take over, and, and.' 'It's okay it as just a dream' they told me calmly.

Item_Response: All of a sudden, Tromlopp heard a noise. Then some whirring and cracking. Then, all of a sudden, he saw two green lights from under a white sheet...        Tromlopp Qupon O'Rustivix McNeper woke up in the morning feeling relaxed and rejuvenated. It was a Saturday morning, and the sun was covered by gray clouds. It was hailing outside. Tromplopp quickly ate breakfast excitedly. There was thunder and lightning. He grabbed his lab coat and hurried to his tool shed. In there was a table with an object under the white sheet.        Tromlopp pressed a button. 'FINALLY!' Tromlopp yelled. He unveiled what was under the white sheet. There lied a robot about the size of a 2-3 year old kid. Tromlopp backed away from the robot and took cover behind a big wall. All of a sudden, lightning shot through the opening of the shed and struck the robot. Tromlopp closed the shed and quickly looked at the robot. Nothing happened. Tromlopp dejectedly walked back to his house. Then, he heard a whirring noise. Then cracking. All of a sudden, Tromlopp saw two green lights turn on from under the white sheet. He ripped the white sheet off the table, and what he saw there changed his life forever.        He put the object on the ground. It was a fully functional and working robot powered by electricity. 'What is your command,' the robot said. Tromlopp was excited. He had big plans. Tromlopp hurried to the United States of America Patent Office. He filed a patent for having the first living robot which is able to follow any command the owner gives it. He was awarded a huge sum of money for his invention. When Tromlopp got home,   he sped to his shed. He asked the robot to do all sorts of things, like make hot dogs, write down pi, teleport to Mars and back. Tromlopp's robot could do anything. Eventually, Tromlopp realized what he could really do with this robot. He renovated his house, made fake money that looked just like real money. Tromlopp was turning evil. The robot would give everything he wanted. When Tromlopp went to the grocery store to find out whether his counterfeit money worked, the store didn't realize a thing.        Suddenly, Tromlopp was going around town buying everything. He bought new land fr his mansion he was going to have built for himself. He bought the local football team (the Washington Redskins) and soon became the richest person in the world and no one knew how fast Tromlopp went from being in poverty to being the richest man in the world.        Then, before Tromlopp could do anything the police burst through the door of his newly built mansion. He was interrogated and was later arrested by Chief of Police Larry Luster. Tromlopp's patent and robot were destroyed and no one knew Tromlopp had created what so many inventors struggled to create.

Item_Response: In this paragraph the characters (or robots) are the Gemini-Scout, the Dante 2, Mr.Gower, Agribots, HRP-4c, and the Google.  The Gemini-Scout is used for finding lost miners in underground mines and communicates with the search and rescue team.  This robot tells miners whether the air is safe or not.  The Dante 2 is a robot that goes inside volcanoes and gathers information for scientists when the volcanoe is too hot for them to go inside.  The Mr.Gower is a robot that helps doctors and nurses with medicines to patients and helps doctors focus on more important tasks.  The Agribots are robots that farmers use to pick their fruit or to tell if the fruit is ripe and ready.  Farmers even use them for their greenhouses when their too busy to keep an eye on their plants.  The HRP-4c is a robot that plays with children, pets, or even itself when your too busy or your at work and need a babysitter.  The Google is a robot that drives for you and makes sure you dont get in an accident and just steers the way a human would.

So a weer later I went into that store and i saw it move. I didn't know what to do so i went up and touched it this was the beginning of a whole new world.                     This was insane this was a creature, otherwise known as a robot. I took this robot with me and it started to talk to me. It turns out that this robot was a robot who can interact with others, and play the best soccer in the world! So i named him Chuck he was pretty cool he cleaned up and did my chores for me. I didn't tell anyone about Chuck except my friend Jadenn and she promised not to tell anyone. She wanted to see what he can do so we went in my garage and his shape was like a typical robot he had a square body, but he didn't have any buttons. Chuck had a different personality he liked people who me and Jadenn liked, but the people we didn't like he didn't like either.              I figured Chuck was also good at making food. When my friend came over we watched TV until, she decided to go in the garage I tried to force her to get out, but she wouldn't. Then she saw Chuck I told her not to tell anyone and she didn't which was a shocker.              One day Chuck started saying error error so many times he exploded. That was the end of Chuck, but once I told Jadenn we started crying on the floor.
