He finishes his robot with a Gray, square tissue box with a small happy face on the front. There was a loud boom behind Ted and it starts to rain. That night Ted was sitting up in his bedroom looking down at his robot as it starts to turn into a pile of mud and cans. There was a loud crack of lightning as Ted went to sleep.              When Ted woke up the next day he looked out into the sunny backyard to see his robot scorched from  the lightning, but as he kept looking at it he kept looking at it he noticed a slight movement, I'm going crazy, he thought, but as he kept looking at it he realized that it was waving at him. Ted ran downstairs to go look at his robot. ' Where are you going?' his mom asked. But he was already out the door before he could hear her.               When he finally got outside he noticed that the robot's head had turned to metal and the bottle caps had separated into fingers and feet. The robot finally stopped waving, and in a squeaky, metallic voice he said, 'Creator, what is my name?' 'Uh... Your name is Daniel,' said Ted, thinking about his best friend. He was still amazed that a piece of mud and bottle had turned into a working robot. 'Okay! Whatever you say creator,' said Daniel. 'Can you please call me Ted?' asked Ted. After that Ted told Daniel to stay outside while Ted got some breakfast. When Ted got back outside Daniel was still in the same spot where Ted had left him.  'What do you want to do Ted?' asked Daniel. 'We can play dodge ball,' said Ted.                Daniel was amazingly accurate with a dodge ball. Every time he threw it he hit  Ted. His mechanical legs made him turn and run extremely fast. His arms threw the enough force to knock down an elephant. By the time the dodge ball game was over Daniel had one 384 games and Ted had one 16 games. 'That was 400 games total!' Ted exclaimed looking at the ground.                When night came Ted had built a shelter for Daniel on the side of his house. 'Now stay here,' said Ted, pointing at the shelter. As Ted went inside for bed it started to rain and there was lightning. The next morning Ted ran outside to see his shelter burned and a pile of bottle and mud. Ted cried out, 'Why did he have to go!' The sun shone brightly as the day began and even though Ted had only spent a day with Daniel he would remember the day for the rest of his life.

Item_Response: ROBOTS           Hello my name is Damon Brown and I am writing an multi-paragraph story about robots.Robots are really help full and fun to use.Some people use robots in hospitals, search and rescue missions,Volcanoes,and farms.Robots do the jobs that people cant do.          There is a robot named the Gemini-Scout it helps on search and rescue missions.It is remote controlled.It is less than two feet tall and has wheels.It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns.The robot is small but it is very strong.Where ever it goes it collects information.It sometimes tests air for gases for miners and it has a thermal camera that uses heat sensors to find living things.When it finds taped miners it can use its radios to talk to the rescue team.It is controlled with a video game controller so almost any one can use it.It carry's food and water.       There is another robot called Dante 2.This robot goes in volcanoes and gathers information for scientist.It looks like a spider it has eight legs that helps it climb steep walls of the volcanoes.It is built to survive very strong heat.It looks for vents or holes in the crater.Then it collects information about the gases that come out of the vents.So scientists can study volcano safe in there labs while Dante 2 is in the volcano.       There is another robot called Mr. Gover it looks like a small cabinet on wheels.It helps doctors and nurses bring medicine to patents.It has a lot of drawers with locks on it so the nurse can unlock it and get the medicine out.It can ride elevators and steer through hallways and go around things that get in its way.The robot is so strong it can carry 500 pounds.After two hours of charging the robot can deliver medicine for twelve hours without stoping.The Mr. Gower can say hundreds of phrases.

Item_Response: 'It was a hot summer day in the city of  Dallas, Texas , and I was working on my newest invention for the science fair, the 'Toy-inator 4000'. It was a small robot that was supposed to play with the you. I was putting the batteries in when the 'toy-inator 4000' came alive! I screamed for my life! I ran down stairs as fast as a cheetah to get a plastic bag so I can throw the thing away, but then it exclaimed ,'Wait! Don't throw me away!I have come alive to help you Sam.' I was in shock. The thing knew my name and I didn't even program it yet! 'Sam, if you throw me away, you wont be able to get the prize for the Dallas City Science Fair' , it told me. 'How do you know me? Where did you come from? Are you an alien?! If so then don't eat me please! There's a leftover hamburger downstairs, it's all yours!' I shouted.'Sam, I will not eat you. You have made me and I am here to serve you. But I still want the hamburger. Last night while you were sleeping, your dad wanted to help you with...well me, so he programed me. He told me everything I had to know. So then today when you put the batteries in, I came alive.' I was trying to take this all in, but I still didn't think it was possible that me and my dad made a robot! 'Okay then. I believe you. Let's go for a test run shall we? Wait. I have to name you because I can't just call you the toy-inator 4000. Its too long. I'll call you Ti.' I replied to him.                Ti and I went to the park to see what special tricks he can do,when we ran into Jamie. 'Oh hey Jamie.' I said in a depressed voice. She was the mean girl who always kissed up to the teacher. 'Hey Sam. What you got there? Is it your little toy? Hahaha what a baby.' she told me. 'No,it's for the city science fair. Ti is my robot that I'm entering.' I replied. 'Greetings Jamie. I had heard you are very mean and-' 'What did that thing just say?!?' she yelled. 'Nothing. He said your dress is nice.' Bye!' I ran home with Ti. 'Why did you say that??' ' The subject was being mean to you. I was defensing you.' 'Okay thanks. But never say that again! Jamie is so mean. Let's just test your tricks in the backyard.' 'Okay dudet.' ' Dont say that.' I replied. 'Hahaha okay sorry.' It said laughing.We tried out all the special tricks that Ti can preform. Turns out he is a good singer, damcer, gymnast, and juggler. I even taught him how to fly. We stayed up all night getting him prepared for tomorrows big contest. My mom even made him a little coat to wear.                    It was the big day and I was very excited. I was setting up my booth when a girl in a pink,flowery dress comes in. It was Jamie. I couldnt believe my eyes! She had a girl version of Ti! She set up her booth right next time. I was as red as a pepper! 'Hi Sam. I didn't see you there.' I didn't replie. It would just make things worse.A little later I told Ti I would turn him off so that when the judges come to our booth, they would see Ti the whole way through. They were at Jamies booth and when I was turning on Ti, he didnt want to turn on! I kept pressing the power button , but he was just sitting there! 'Mom!Ti isn't working!' 'Calm down sweetie.' she told me. ' I brought extra batteries. I figured that he would die out because you kept playing with him all night long.' ' Thanks so much mom. I almost had a heart attack.' The judges came to my table and I turned on Ti. ' Ladies and gentlemen, I present to you Ti. Ti is a homemade robot I made with my wonderful dad.' I told everryone at my booth. 'Greetings everyone' Ti said. He stood up and shook everyones hand. 'For my 1st act, Ti will now juggle while he is dancing on a balance beam.'Oooo ahhhh' People kept saying. Ti went through all his acts without messing up. Jamie was envious with green. ' Ti fly up please' I told him. Ti started to fly up in the air in circles and came down smoothly.' 'thank you everyone.' I told the judges and the crowd of people filmng. 'Listen Sam. You are going down. You won't win. Tirina here can do swan lake. 'Well let's just wait and see' I told Jamie. A hour passed and it was time for the awards. the judges said 'In second place is Ti... rina and Jamie!' ' That leaves us with Ti and Sam in first place! Congrats you two!' The judges exclaimed! I was so happy! I cant believe I won!After the science fair, I went to Yourgurtland with my sister, parents, and obviously Ti too.'                   'And that was the time my robot and I won the science fair' I told my creative writing club. 'Good job Sam!' my tacher told me.

Item_Response: Ticonderoga        While I was in my room working on my math homework, a strange thing occurred. Right before my eyes all of my pencils, paper, pens, and other school materials started to connect. As I was looking in awe at the miraculous sight I saw a figure beginning to appear on my desk. What was it and how did it form were the questions I asked myself as I backed away from this creature that was right before my eyes.            I had been studying robots for years and when this 'thing' appeared before my eyes, my research had payed off. 'Would it be like an Agribot picking all of my food, or a Gemini-Scout with his skill in carrying things?'What could this creature do and would it talk? Then I found my answer because of the name that was boarded on the robot, Ticonderoga. This was the pencil brand that helped create this robot, and now it believed that it's name was Ticonderoga. Still though my question was unanswered, what could it do?            As it took out a piece of paper from what I think was its stomach the robot began to write, 'I am Ticonderoga for all your homework needs.' I was in utter shock when I saw this, knowing what this robot's capability was. I began to ask the robot questions like, 'Can you talk?' and 'Are you good at algebra?' The robot named Ticonderoga then began to beep and start blinking with all of his bright lights. 'I am a great mathematician and I do talk' Ticonderoga said in his robot voice. I never thought I would have such an advantage for 'All my homework needs.'               Then a horrible thing happened, my robot began to take all of my homework and shove it into his stomach! I thought he was going to shred it, or much worse destroy it. As time was slow like molasses I waited for Ticonderoga to give me back my homework, in whatever condition it would be. 'Beep' his stomach said and I waited for the paper's that were used as his stomach to unfold and be able to get my homework back.               Then, to my surprise my homework came out in perfect condition. As I took it out of his colored pencil hand I saw writing on it. 'Hooray' I said as I used my calculator to check the answers Ticonderoga had put onto my paper. They were all correct, and in my exact hand-writing! Shocked by this miracle of a robot I had just created I wondered if I could continue to use this robot for my homework.               I came up with a solution because Teacher's Appreciation Week was coming up, and i and not got my teacher a present yet. Would my teacher be helped greatly by this miraculous correcting robot? Of course he would, what teacher wouldn't want a extra hand to correct paper's? While i was saying my good-bye's to the helpful robot named Ticonderoga I put him into a box that said 'Handle with care' and put a pretty red ribbon on the box. Ticonderoga was a great robot, but i hope that my teacher never gives him any papers to hand out, because he will stick those papers into his stomach, and fill them out with all of the correct answers.

Item_Response: Have you ever thought of seeing a real life robot ? Well I know I have. This is a story about how a robot came alive. In the story we have our main character Bradley and his friend Adam. They also have a monkey they call him Pelt and a toy robot named Ian. Well it all started when Bradley and Adam mistakingly pluged Ian into the house generator. They thought it was the T.V. that they pluged in. They were  wrong.        'Oh no! ' said Bradley ' Run for it' Then they heard the sound of lightning, but then they saw it wasn't lightning it was all the electricity going into Ian the robot!Then they heard aloud bang and Ian was walking to them 'Hi', said Ian         'You can talk?' asked a puzzled Bradley'Of course I can.' said Ian 'How?' asked Adam. They didn't know the electricity brought Ian to life.          'Oh never mind that' said Ian ' Lets just play I don't actually know what to do though'         'Don't worry we'll show you right Bradley?' asked Adam         'Right!' said Bradley. Then he ran back inside and got a remote control car and the controller, but then Pelt came out and grabed Ian!         'Hey let go!' shouted Ian as he kept trying to pry the monkey's hands off him. Just then pelt dropped Ian and Ian ran back to Bradley and Adam         'Yes we got Ian back!' shouted Bradley but then he saw Ian running away! ' Where are you going?' asked Bradley         'I heard a scream' said Ian as he aproached a building on fire! Then Ian ran in to the flaming building and came out with a man coughing because of the smoke, then they found out Ian had just saved the cheif fire fighter!Ian was then apointed chief robot firefighter.                                                     THE END

Item_Response: The Come Alive Robot                It was a scorching hot day in Lancaster, California, the sun feeling like nothing but a huge ball of fire. My friends, Anette, and America, decided to check out the new museum that opened in town just yesterday! We were all tired and without any energy, but we were desperately wanting to check out that new museum.            As we arrived at the 'Robot Museum', we noticed robots EVERYWHERE!!! Robots awaiting at the front door. robots on the roof, robots wandering helplessly around the museum, everywhere!!! As we came through the sliding glass doors of the museum, we felt a cold blast of air that rejuvenated us, but we were all still tired. We all decided to take the elevator to the second level were robots are believed to come alive. We exited the elevator and we all saw a fascinating robot with tons and tons of buttons, pushing them out of curiosity, but still tired and gloomy. America pushed a big red button, and it started to make a strange beeping noise!!! Beep-beep-boom-beep-beep-boom went the strange button. Out of the blue, green smoke started to come out of the robot, and we all started to fell as tired as ever.            After that little mishap, we realized that the robot with the big red button on it was alive, and rolling around as excited as ever. I got startled and started to panic, finding out that the robot can speak!!!!! 'How do you do?' said the robot. 'Ugh............, um............., were fine?' we all said to the robot.'' My name is Bob and i am a robot who can do whatever you wish.'' ' OK first of all, where are we and what are we doing here?'Your in Robot ville where everything you see are robots,' said Bob. 'O, about what you said, you can do whatever you want huh?' said Anette. 'Certainly, whatever you would like, in fact my middle name is Dowatever!!!' 'Well then, please take us out of....... what the city name.......oh, Robot ville, and return us to Lancaster, PLEASE!!! ' said America. 'Ok then, dipity-doo-dipity-daa, take these girls to Lancaster, yaaaa!!!!!!!!!!!!!!'            We suddenly realized that we were back in Lancaster, in the freshened museum. Anette wanted to return to the house and just have a nice lemonade iced tea, and we all agreed. As we exited the museum, we realized it was night time, and that we had only been in Robot ville for 15 minutes. It got me to thinking, and I realized we fell asleep on the museum floor, and that this was all just a dream.

Item_Response: There once was a little boy named Bobby who loved to play with tools and build things.  Bobby was out in his dad's shop one day and was trying to build something that would do his chores around the house and would do his homework so that he could build more things.  So that is when he came up with the idea of building a robot.  He built the robot in approximately a week.  Then he had to try and see if it would actually  turn on so that he could use it.  So then he tried it didn't work so he work on it a little more every night and tried again to see if it would work every night but it never worked.  Bobby had tried so hard on that little robot he was starting to get frustrated with the robot.  So he decided he would work on it in a couple nights so that he could think on it a little bit.  he thought hard and harder every night but could not find the right solution so he decided o go to a mechanic shop after school and ask one of the mechanic's if they had any ideas on what could be wrong with his robot and the mechanic said well it don't know if you don't bring the robot in.  So Booby said he would and the next day he brought the robot in and the mechanic looked at the robot and couldn't find one thing wrong with it.  But the mechanic said Young boy did you build this by your self?  Yes I did sir.  Well this is mighty fine for a young boy like you.  Well thank you sir.  But son I'll have to say i can't find the problem.  So Booby said i will just try to find it myself.  So Booby took the robot home and worked until his mother came and told him it was time for supper.  So Bobby came in and asked his father i would like you to come and see something I built after supper.  Okay his father said.  So him and his father  went out to the old shop and Bobby said dad I want you to close your eyes I think this is the best thing i have ever made so his father covered his eyes. Bobby led his father to the robot and told his dad to open his eyes.  When his father opened his eyes he was very shocked to see what he actually was seeing.  He said son did you make his all by yourself.  Yes i did but i can't get it to actually turn on but i wanted you to see it anyway.  Well i am glad you did because this is magnificent.  Do you think i can fix it if i keep trying? Of course i think you most sertainly can.  So they whent back inside and went ot sleep that night and Bobby heard something out in the kitchen.  So Bobby went out there to see if anything was there.  Right when he steped into the kitchen he heard another noise.  Then all of a sudden he saw a fast movement.  Trying to be quit so whatever it was wouldn' hear him he snuck into his parents room.                     When Bobby go in there he woke up his father and said dad i heard a noise coming from the kitchen and then i saw a very quick movement.  Ok im coming i will check it out.  So Bobby and his father went into the kitchen and then there was another movement.  Bobby father said Bobby we need to be very careful.  So the two of them snuck into the kitchen a little farther and they saw what is was.  It was Bobby's robot cleaning the kitchen from the night before.  When Bobby saw what is it was he was in great shock.  He said i sware it didn't work last night.  Maybe a fuse just started working and it wasn't working last night.  But how could it start working if i didn't do any thing to it?  Maybe it fell over and hit something and hit the right fuse.  I guess I didn't think to check the fuses.  Well it guess that was something we wern't expexting when we heard the noise.  Ya you are very right well we best get back to sleep and turn the robot off.  You still have school tomarrow.  I know i will have my robot up in the morning and he will have breakfest made and served on the plates.  So when mom gets up early to make breakfest tell her im on it.

Item_Response: Bad To Good                   On a cold windy night there was a little boy sitting in his room thinking and thinking about his dream. That little boy was Max. Max would dream about robots over and over again. Untill one day he had decided to make a robot himself. 'I'm going to make a robot that could give me unlimited wishes' he said to his parents. But his parents didnt have the care in the world to pay attention. 'Yeah yeah' his dad would say. 'Go play in your room' shouted his mother. He knew he could make them proud so when his parents went to eat dinner, he stayed up working on his invention.              It took all night but he had finally created the robot of his dreams, The Wishbot 3000. He wanted to try it out so he plugged the wires together but it didnt work. He tried to do everything he could but it was impossible. After half an hour he finally gave up and went to bed. Whir! Whir! He heard something coming from the living room. Whir! Whir! He quickly went out to bed and dashed for the living room. There stood next to the couch was a miricle. It  was The Wishbot 3000. Tears of joy were rolling down his face. finally his parents came home and nearly fainted. Now tears of sadness rolled down his cheeks. His parents still didnt care. They went straight to their rooms without a care in the world as always.             After spending a week with Wishbot and making wishes to help the world he didnt care what his parents think anymore.Weeks passed and some bad news went by. 'I'm here to take over the world' said Wish Bot. I've had a lot of fun with you but I have to complete my mission. Max was on the floor crying his eyes out. Wish Bot needed to do what he come for. So he left the house, leaving Max behind. Months had passed and Max would never forget the time he had with Wishbot. Knock! Knock! Who could it be? There standing on the porch was the one and only Wishbot. Wishbot had never forgotten the time they had together either. Max was crying tears, tears of joy. As the years passed by they have stayed together no matter what.

'Oh that's the oven the cookies are done'!So when the girls went to the kitchen they opened the oven all the cookies were 'GONE'.Then they went searching all around the kichen to see where the cookies went.they finillay found something eating the cookies it was a Robot.The girls had a questioned look on their face.After staring at the robot for so long one of them finillay aked what it's name was.It said its name was 'Sally'Sally the robot I came from the oven.           The next few weeks they had no idea what to do with Sally or what to say to  thier parents.Their decison was to hide Sally until they could think of a way to get Sally back into the oven.          It was Monday and the girls had to go to school.Sally had to stay home for 5 hoursuntil the girls came back from school.Sally had no idea what to do because she had never been at a house before so she figured to do somethings robots do.She thought maybe she could work.She worked for a little like cleaning the house and things.That wasn't very fun so she started to draw as she finished drawing the girls came home and happy to see that Sally was okay.           Destiny and Cassidy had the solousion to Sally's appearence the reason why Sally's here is because we cooked the cookies too long.Allthough Sally was a good friend she had to go back where she came from.So they made more cookie dough and put the cookies and Sally in the oven and Sally was the best cookie eating robot ever.

Item_Response: Dr. Minex stared down at the metal table. On it was a piece that he had been working on for over a decade. It was meant to be an army robot: one that could shoot and scout, camoflouge and bomb. In theory, it was even supposed to change into a tank. But it was far from being completed. In fact, it wasn't even half way done. Creating such a device that could possibly win this war that has been raging on for almost twenty years turned out to be almost impossible. There was a lot of research, building, experimenting, failing, backtracking, taking apart, rebuilding, experimenting again, and failing again over and over  like a cycle.

Item_Response: My Amazing Robot                     My name is Mollie. I guess you could say I'm just an average sixth grader. We are out from school for spring break now. We were assigned to make something for art over the break. It has to be at least as tall as us, and weigh more than five pounds.                 I have been trying to come up with something to make. I think I finally have it. I will make a robot. My dad and I are about to go to the store for my materials. This is what I got: cardboard, aluminum foil, glue, tape, markers, and construction paper. I hope that's all I need. Tomorrow, I will build it.                 Saturday. I'm going back to school in two days, and I still haven't built my robot. I went to get my dad, but he was asleep, so I woke him up! We decided to make my robot colorful. My dad had some extra spray paints and I had my markers. After he was built, we colored him. I think it looks pretty cool. We used the construction paper to cover the cardboard for my robots face. We used the aluminum foil for his body coverings. I hope my art teacher thinks its as cool as I do!                   Sunday has passed. It's Monday. My robot is finished and my art teacher loved it. The thing is, we have to present it. 'Mollie! You're next', said my art teacher, Mr.Davis. Here goes nothing. I started with some facts about robots. 'Robots can be hard-working, and they can be playful. They also can be both, which is exactly what mine is.' Okay, I'm off to a good start. 'Some robots work in hospitals (Mr.Gower), and some work in mines (Gemini-scout). My robot is not real, but a design of the robot Mr.Gower. I have her designed as a nurse and I hooked up a recording in the back that says 'your delivery Is here, just like the actual Mr.Gower.' I took off my cover and everyone was amazed! Some nerd in my art class, Jeffery, asked 'Why didn't you make it real?' My response was 'I didn't have enough time.' I think we know that's true. Thank goodness that was over with.                  When I got home, my parents asked me how it went. I told them it went pretty good and took my robot upstairs. It was late when I got home, so I just went straight to bed. Tried to, anyway. Every half-hour, someone from my school called me. I got the same question EVERY time: Why wasn't your robot real? I was ready to throw the phone! 'I wish it as real, so I could sleep in peace without people calling me every 30 minutes!',I screamed. Right after I said that, something strange happened. I heard a loud noise and it was coming from my robot. I got up and approached it slowly. It started talking. It didn't say what was on the recording, it said 'You didn't want your friends, so now you have none.' I thought I was dreaming at first, so I ran into the door. Shouldn't have done that. Now I have a black eye. So I guess it's not a dream, after all.                  I didn't know what to say. When I got to school, nobody but the teachers were there. I was worried so I called my big sister, because I knew my parents were working. It said there was no phone with that number, so I called my parents and asked them where my sister was, and they said what sister, I was an only child!!! I was even more worried now. What do I do?                 I went home and talked to my robot. She said after what I said last night, she wanted to help me because I was her creator, and she thought I meant I didn't want my friends, at ALL! I talked with my robot for a long time! She said she was sorry and that she would try to reverse it. She said all she needed was pictures of me and my friends from before they, kind of, like, disappeared! I had a bunch, so it went by fast. I just hope I get my friends and my sister back! I miss them so much. Guess what? It worked.              The only thing is that they don't know about what happened. They think they've been here the whole time, and I'm okay to think that, as long as I have my friends.

Item_Response: It all happened very suddenly that day. This day was April 8th 2013. I was doing my math homework when my Dad walked in with a big blue box. 'Honey look what I got.' He came over to where I sat and pulled out a metal figure. 'What is that?' I asked him staring at it confused of why he was so excited. 'It's a robot I bought at the convention.' 'Okay...' 'Wh...' Before I could finish he pushed a button and it turned on. 'Hello I'm Maid #3000.' After it turned on I was starring back and forth between the robot and my Dad. Why is does he like this thing so much I mean it's cool but not so cool that I think i'm going to explode cool, I thought to myself. 'Well I'm going to bring it upstairs and test this baby out.' My Dad said running with joy in every step towards the stairs. After I saw this sight of my dad looking like a kid at a candy shop, I decided to talk to my friend Ella. 'Hey' 'Hi' 'Whats up' 'My dad got this wierd robot toy and is playing with it upstairs.' 'That sounds... different.' 'Tell me about it.' After I talked to Ella I decided to go to bed.       'BOOM!' I heaed outside my room. I was scared out of my mind, but I decided to see what it was. When I looked I saw the robot smashing plates breaking furniture saying 'Robots shall take over the world' repeadingly. Then it saw me I screamed and ran upstairs. I first tried to go to my Dad's room, but he's at another convention. Hopefully he doesn't buy another one, I thought. Then I called for help but no one believed me so I called Ella. 'Okay i'll over as soon as possible.'        I had her come through the window because I blocked my door. 'What aew we going to do?' She asked. 'I have a plan' I told her. The robot has a botton that turns it off so you will distract it while I push the botton. 'Okay' she said. Then we got to the mission. I snuck out the window wile Ella unblocked my door and distracted the robot. While she was doing this I snuck through the front door and got ready to push the button. 'Hey robot I know you want to destroy me' Ella said then did some random stuff that I had to chuckle at.Then when the robot started to move I pushed the button and it turned off. 'Yes!' We both said and highfived eachother.Then we cleaned the house.      'Hey I'm home' 'Hi Daddy' 'Honey look what I got.' Then he pulled out another robot. Here we go again...

Item_Response: To whom it may concern,               I am writing to you to inform you about robots. Now robots aren't bad or evil at all. Now this brings me back 14 years. When I fist had an experience with a robot. Well, I began eating my favorite cereal, Captain Crunch.I looked in the cabinet for some peanut butter, but to my knowledge I didn't have anything. So I began my list:       Eggs Pickles Peanut Butter Waffles Jelly Etc.                  I walked a block to the market, I picked up what I needed,and then went home. When, I got home I checked the mail.Nothing. So, I put the groceries away. Then, I  went to take a nap. About in the middle of my nap, the doorbell rang. Ring, ring, ring. I got up, went to the door. And to my expectations, there in my face was a robot. He started,'Hello, my name is Wilbur. I am a mail robot. Package for Alexxa Robinette. Thank you for your service.' Well, then almost everybody on the block got a package. I opened mine to find a pink slip. Blah, blah, blah.I was ready to find out what was in the box. I pulled out some bubble wrap. It was nothing. Wow, what a waist of time. Okay, well thank you for listening to my awkward story.                           Thank you,            Anonymous Person

Item_Response: Robot Dog    There was this dog and he was a normal dog, he played fetch, he liked to be pet, he was normal except for one thing he was a robot dog. His name was Duke.       Duke was the best pet you could imagine. Nobody wanted him they thought that he would be like a remote control dog, but he wasn't. He was a regular dog. Everyone didn't give him a chance, but this one girl, Kellie Baker, gave him a chance. She bought him and she did exactly what Duke wanted her to do, she gave him a shinny collar. The tag had his name engraved in it. Duke and Kellie were the best of friends, until Duke got sick.       Kellie took him to the vet. The vet asked what was wrong with him and Kellie did not know. The vet took some blood from Duke and ran some test, but nothing seemed to be wrong. Kellie remembered that Duke was a robot dog. How did the doctor take blood if Duke was a robot? Duke had turned to a real dog!       Duke was real and living. Duke was so happy to have somebody love him even before he was real. Kellie had loved Duke for who he was.       Duke and Kellie went on adventures together, they went to France, they went to San Fransisco, they even went to Europe. Kellie and Duke had fun and Duke was beginning to get old and not as strong as he was when he was a puppy. Now Duke wished he was a robot again so he could live forever with Kellie. Then Duke relished something he ha dent relished before, Kellie was going to die and if he was a robot nobody would love him any more. The only person who loved him was Kellie, and Duke was going to enjoy the rest of his life with the person he loves.       Duke and Kellie were getting old and Duke had began to get sick wwith a disease that most dogs don't recover from. Kellie took Duke to the vet to put him down. It was hard for Kellie to let him go, but she saw that he was suffering. A few years later, two at the most, Kellie got sick too and she died from it.

Item_Response: The Technology of Today                             Back in the days, we didn't have much technology like we do today. Nowadays, we have all kinds of technological things including expensive phones with internet, tablets, laptops, computers, and other useful electronics that we use. Robots are also becoming very popular by helping to save lives, exploring volcanos, babysitting, picking fruit, collecting information, and much more things. Who knows what we will have in the future if we already have robots doing our jobs today.                   A few types of robots are the Gemini- Scout robot, the Dante 2, Mr.Gower, Agribots, the HRP-4c, and the Google car.These robots all have different and unique characteristics which now help us in our everyday lives. For example, the Gemini- Scout robot does search- and- rescue work in underground mines. The Dante 2 collects information such as going down into volcanos to explore them. Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hospitals. This robot can ride elevators, steer through hallways, move around things that get in the way, and it can also pull 500 pounds. Agribots is a farmer robot and  it picks fruit. It can pick fruits such as apples, grapes, oranges, or berries.The HRP-4c robot can even dance and sing.Last, the Google car robot practically drives you around. It is a robot car that almost completely drives itself. Those were the types of robots and their characteristics.                       There are a lot of technological devices in our world these days, and a lot of people probably wouldn't survive without them. People use technology to communicate with their family members and friends. Others use it to do research on the internet, and others just for fun. The study of science has helped us to be able to have electronics, plus robots. In the future, robots will most likely be our babysitter, employees, and our best companions.

He had two twin sisters,they were five year old.He lived in a small house with his parents. Mark's family was really poor and lazy.             One cloudy day Mark went over to his best friend's house Gael. When they got to Gael's house they saw a robot . Not those kind that move ,just a clay model.Gael's dad was a professional  person that made things out of clay.They were watching a movie called 'I-Robot'.                                                                   All of a sudden they heard foot steps and someone mopping. They went to see who it was.They couldn't believe their eyes. The robot was doing the job .They were so impressed that the robot could also talk.He did an amazing job at cleaning.Even Mark wanted to take it home(since his family was super lazy).                                                         After ten long lasting years the robot broke down and never worked again. The kids actually named the robot 'Cleaner'.'Cleaner' picked up and cleaned every single piece of garbage.Either it was inside the house or outside.Now he is remembered as a future robot system.Nobody knows how it came alive.Some say it was a miracle or magic.                               Gael's dad made another robot clay model,but nothing happened .He even tried real magic. Still no answer from the new robot . To this day many robots are made but with metal,cables and electricity.

Item_Response: What would you do if you're science project suddenly came alive? I'll tell you what I did. So it was  May 15,1972 ,Monday when it all started. I was in science class and our teacher was explaining that she assigned the whole class to come up with a science experiment for the science fair. She said it had to be involving the works of technology and it will be due on Friday. Like usual I was staring off in space when my science teacher  Mrs. Argules called my name; 'Nancy Castro'! Tell the class what will be due on Friday. I said, 'Something?' Mrs.Argules looked mad but ignored me. She repeated that this Friday we have to make a science experiment for the Science Fair. Finally class was over and I went home walking with my friend Guadalupe. Guadalupe said ' Nancy what are you doing for your science project? I said, 'I don't know whatever? '                                So days went by Tuesday,  and Wednesday. I was in Science now   Mrs. Argules asked each of us what we were doing for our project. When it was my turn to say what I was doing I got nervous and I said ' Um mm....... Robot!'Yeah.' I'm doing a robot.'   The bell rang and I went bursting out the door. Guadalupe said ' So you're doing a robot!' I said 'What?' 'Oh yeah robot.' Right.' Tonight I started on the robot  it was hard. I found different websites and books on robots and I stayed up until One in the morning working on the thing. I made a robot that picks fruit. After I went to sleep.                                In the morning I ate and went to get my robot. It wasn't there. I looked all over and I just went up to my room to get my backpack and go to school. I couldn't believe it the robot was there. It was...... Alive! It could walk, talk, carry things and read. I called the robot Rogelio. I picked that name because he was reading the book called Rogelio. I took it to school and people kept staring. I took it to the science fair and I got first place. Mrs. Argules couldn't believe I made the robot and she kept looking at it to find store tags. So Rogelio and I went home and I asked my mom if I can keep him. She was about to say no when Rogelio did all her chores, she immediately said 'Yes.' So that's how my science project came alive.

Item_Response: Scientist Robert Ellis was working on a robot that could change all of man kind. Suddenly his robot ,Gemini-Scout 2000, had awoken out of nowhere!                 'Hell-oo,' said the Gemini-Scout 2000. Robert knew from his research that robots weren't able to talk without a special piece of equipment which he knew he hadn't put in. The robot JUMPED off the table and bolted out of the room, and out into the world. Ellis knew that his robot was going to be unstable and that he had to get him back into that lab before anything went wrong. He grabbed his jacket and went out after that robot.                 'Oh, Mr. Robot!!!' exclaimed Robert. It was dead silent out in the desert, but in the distance he heard a faint whisper and knew it was the robot. He jumped into his car and drove ,over the speed limit, in the direction of the whisper.                 'I will NEVER come back until I prove myself to the world that I am more than just some metal!' The robot flew to the biggest mine in the United States of America, since he is built to do search-and-rescue in mines around the world. The mine had caught on fire and most of the workers were trapped in the mine. He flew into the mine and searched for people trapped and found no one so he flew back out. When he got outside he saw the one and only Gemini-Scout, the one that was first built had saved all the people. The Gemini-Scout 2000 was so angry he flew all the way up to outer space. While he was up there he saw a space ship coming straight for him, but he was fearless so he stayed put.                 When the space ship approached him it said,'Friend or foe?'                 'It depends who you are, if you are a human from the planet earth than I'm a foe to you.'said the Gemini-Scout 2000. The space ship opened it's doors so the robot of Robert Ellis went into the space ship. When he entered he saw another robot was smiling at him.                 'We have been waiting for a robot like you,' said the robot.                 'Who are you?' said the Gemini-Scout 2000.                 'The great and only Dark Thunder! You might have heard of me. I too was created by Robert Ellis and he made me go out of my head so I went after all the people in that world and tried to destroy them. My plan didn't work because Robert got a hold of me and had a team drop me off here. Now that I have you my army of other Earth haters will go to Earth and take it over!!' yelled Dark Thunder.                 'I'm your man. I want to show the world that I am better than the old Gemini-Scout.' exclaimed the robot. With that they all headed to Earth that's when the trouble of the robot war began. When the robots attacked the humans suited up to fight back. All the robots had one person to terminate. Gemini-Scout 2000 had to get rid of none other than his creater, Robert Ellis. He was so glad to be able to terminate Robert, and right when he was about to he saw Dark Thunder smiling at him and right then he knew what he was doing was wrong. Robert told him what he needed to do to be a hero so he flew over to Dark Thunder.                 'Your games are over! You played me and your whole army. You belong up in space.' yelled Gemini-Scout. With that he kicked him all the way back to space with the rest of his army.                 'Now there's the real hero I've been waiting for.' said Robert.                 'Thanks for creating me.' Gemini-Scout said with a huge smile.

Item_Response: In the year 3000 there was a robot named Magage was wondering what it would be like if there were humans on her planet, Hemon. Just then it was announced that there was a group of robots being gathered for training t go to Earth, the planet of the humans. Magage was excited. She wanted to go to Earth and play with the humans. She hurried to the Command Center to check the list posted on the entrance and sure enough her name was the first one there. She went inside of the vast building and down the steep ramp to the CCPR (Command Center Program Room). She was welcomed in and ushered into a room across the hall and plugged into a machine. She woke two hours later in a Launch Room with her other 'launchees.' She was assigned to a number, 123456741852963, and put into a room and shut off.            She woke and looked out of the window to see space, space, space, Earth! They would be landing soon.            When they landed the robots were split into groups of three. The names of the other robots in her group were Joam and Derlk. They were launched out into space together and instructed to go to a country in Earth call America. They did as they were told, went to America. Magage, Joam, and Derlk split up to gather the most information. Joam went to New York, Derlk to Texas, and Magage went to Michigan. Magage was too absorbed with the buildings, flying vehicles, and the people to gather information. The people oh the people were lovely! She was following a person called Jen when she was shot. She immedietly sent a distress message to the CCP to warn the others when the radio filled with them. Oh no! Magage thought. They are attacking us! This is terrible! Someone picked her up and carried her into a building. The person sat Magage down and looked at her. It was Jen! Magage thought. She thought this untill she exploded. All of her parts flew around the room. Jen jumped back and ran away. Back at the CCPR there was maddness, everyone speeding around trying to warn the robots that haven't been exploded. Out of the 150 robots sent to Earth only one made it out. His name was Gerge. He was sent back to Earth. While he was there a child chopped him in half with an ax. It was now clear to the CCPR that the humans didn't like robots.

Item_Response: Fiction                Have  you ever heard those stories, the ones that begin with 'Once upon a time' and end with 'Happily ever after?' Well my story is nothing like that. My story begins with something rather different. It goes like this.               'Mavis! How many times have I told you! You can not get another pet! Isn't one cat enough?' My mom yelled. 'But mom, Raelina is really old!' I said. I was going to say something else but my mom interrupted me before I could. 'Honey, Rae Rae isn't that old.' she said calmer. 'Yes she is! I got her when I was two when I got her. Now I'm twelve!' I yelled. ' But...' Before she could say anything else I ran out the door and slammed it behind me.               'Hi, Mavis! What's wrong?' said my best friend, Sophie. 'Nothing.' I muttered. ' I know something is wrong, you only go up in that tree when some thing is really bothering you.' Sophie knew everything about me. ' I just need some alone time.' I don't mind when she talks to me, but right now is not the time for any one to be by me. ' Well you can never be alone with that book around you, you always have your face stuffed in it. Besides, don't you have something to be doing right now?' 'What?' 'Didn't you hear the news, about  the meteorite hitting Julius Park?' 'Lets go!' I hopped out of the tree and on to the ground.              The meteor was huge! Almost the whole park was destroyed! 'Lets go closer!' 'We can't.' 'Yes we can!' Sophie was starting to get annoying. 'Fine, but then we are coming right back here!'                It took a while to get through the crowd, but we got through. There was something metal sticking out through the rock. They were trying to get it open, but could not.                It was getting dark when they finally gave up. Every body had to leave, and everybody did. Except me and Sophie. We ran to the meteor. There was something moving inside of it! Before we could get a closer look, whatever was inside of it burst out of it!                 It was a robot! I had an amazing thought. Maybe if my mom won't let me have another live pet, maybe she would let me have a robot! I was really exited!                 As me and Sophie walked home with the robot, which I had named Marley, Sophie stopped she ran away in fear, i wondered why she did. I tried to stop her, but she wouldn't, so I kept walking. I turned around and Marley was slowing down. I wondered why. Then Marley darted at me and before I could run away she jumped on me. I closed my eyes and waited to die. Then something weird happened, something was licking my face. It was Raelina. Yes, I finally woke up!

Item_Response: On Thursday, March 21, 2013 little Julia got this  toy dog robot. The only words it would say was woof and I'm hungry. The dog was about a life size adullt and it ran on batteries.  Little Julia loved it. Friday night her mom was tucking her in and right before little Julia's Mom left she said ' don't forget to turn off your doggie.' 'I just did.' she yelled. Little Julia heard a noise soon after her mom left it said ' woof I'm hungry.' in a deep voice. She just thought she didn't turn off the dog and went back to bed.           Little Julia woke up and noticed that her doggie wasn't there so, she went downstairs to her doggie flying. She got so excited then she gave it a command to make her pancakes, sure enough the dog made them for her. The dog came to life over night and turned out to be good not bad. She was just so shocked it was not  even funny.            The dog was like a car. It had a radio and a keyboard to type in your destination.So she decided to go to Hawaii, but the dog couldn't go anywhere else besides around the neighborhood and town. She was bummed but still flew to the mall and back. Little Julia had the time of her life.              Little Julia had math homework and she remembered at 9:00 at night but then out of no where her robot jumps up and eats it then poops it out all done. At first she gets really mad until she realized her dog just helped her out. After the toy dog did that she named him homework eater. The dog liked that name.               For some reason overnight the dog turned evil and went on a rampage of wanting to lock people up in jail. Homework eater went straight to the local school. He grabbed all the teachers and brought them to jail. Soon enough everyone was missing but actually put in jail..... except Little Julia and her Mom. Julia ran up to Homework eater took out his batteries then took all the citizens out of jail.

Item_Response: In Nashua, New Hampshire, there was a boy named Nick, who was 12 years old and loved robots. Every day before he went to sleep, he would say to himself that when he grows up he`ll be a famous robot creator as a career for him. Though as he got older, he realized that he`ll need to learn a lot in school to accomplish that. Item_Response: In the year 2458, there a brilliant man named Ulfred. He lived in the richest part of his town, and was known for making remarkable robots. The only thing wrong with them was that they never functioned correctly. The designs and mechanics were remerkable, though what good is that when the robot doesn't even turn on. Everyone from around came to see Ulfred's fantastic work. The robots were all different. They were different sizes, colors, heights, and weights. Though one day, Ulfred made a different robot. This robot was unlike anything anyone had ever seen before. Ulfred made this robot special. He used a new power core that has never been used until now. He used the legendary blue lyrium ore, and after that day, everything changed forever.                      'There, it's finally finished!' Ulfred had just finished making his brand new model of a robot. 'Alright then, all I have to do now is add the lyrium core and I should be done,' he said with delight. At that remark, Ulfred ran over to the freezer where the lyrium was being held. Carefully, he took the frozen lyrium core over to the lifeless robot. Though before Ulfred placed the core into the robot's head, a thought occured to him. 'Wait a minute,' Ulfred said aloud. 'I have to give this little guy a name. I've got it! Z5T3! Now, let's put this core in the robot.' Ulfred carefully places the core in the robot's head. Then, suddenly something happens that Ulfred did not expect. The robot started to glow a bright blue, and then started making beeping noises. Within just a few seconds the robot was on! It was fully functional and everything. Ulfred couldn't believe it.                     After a few minutes, the Z5T3 actually said something! 'Hello,' it said . 'My name is the Z5T3. Pleased to meet you.' 'It's nice to meet you to,' Ulfred said excitedly.'Now, I have an idea that you may like.' 'I'm listening,' the Z5T3 said. 'Well, I was thinking how I created you. I built you to be able to withstand extreme heat temperatures, have super strength and to be able to gather useful information. It might be a good idea if you could respond to any calls for help in the area.' 'That sounds like a great idea,' the Z5T3 said. 'Great, well let's just get a few things...' BEEP BEEP BEEP!!! An alarm rings nearby. 'Attention all citizens, there is a roaring fire ablaze in the city, please evacuate ASAP!' The radio blared through the speaker. 'Well, are you ready for your first test?' Ulfred asked excitedly. 'Of course,' the robot responded. And with that, the Z5T3 rolled out to the nearby fire.                      Once the Z5T3 reached the fire he was ready for some action. The excited robot rushed into the building to check if anyone was trapped inside. One he got up the fourth floor, the Z5T3 heard crying to his left. The robot rolled around until he found the source of the wails. It was a baby, no older than a couple of months old. The Z5T3 took the child outside, then raced back inside the ablaze building. Again, the Z5T3 was checking for any trapped citizens. Once he reached the eighth floor, the robot listened and heard really loud screaming up ahead of him. The fearless robot bolted for the sound, and then found the source of the screaming. An old lady was trapped under a wardrobe, and very close to the fire around her. Quickly, the Z5T3 lifted the wardrobe with ease. He then helped the old lady get outside safely. The robot searched the rest of the building but could find no one else. So, after completing his task, the Z5T3 went back to Ulfred's lab. 'You did it!' Ulfred rn across the room and congradulated the happy robot. 'Z5T3, I think this is going to be a longlasting partnership of successful business

Item_Response: Gem The Robot     Hi. My name is Gemini-Scout but everyone just calls me Gem. Here is the story about when I turn into a real girl and strongly disliked it. So is was just an ordinary day I went down a mine to save some miners you know the usual so i found this really cool rock so I kept it. Turns out it was a magic rock who knew.            So everyday before i found that rock I remember I always wanted to be a real girl I would always wish for it. Til one day it actually happen and that was one of the biggest mistakes i ever made. So the night before i have the rock right next to where i went in sleep mode. So like usual i wished i was a real life girl. Then I went to sleep i woke up to a man waking me up yelling at me to get out. So I'm wondering why he is yelling at me to get out I look down at my hands and they were human hands i was an actual real life teenage girl.             I was so happy for the first day at least. Then I had to go to school all of the girls made fun of me and all the guys just kept staring at me I don't know why though to this day. I didn't know why the girls were making fun of me because i didn't do anything to them. After that day I decided to never go back there ever again. I was already done with being a girl. That night I didn't have any where to go so I slept on a park bench.          Then i realized that I left my special rock at the factory so I had to go back. I tryed to get in but they wouldn't let me. So I had to sneak in so I did by climing through the roof and i was lucky enough to find the rock and wished myself back to a Gemini-Scout so I didn't get caught being in the factory. That has you pretty much caught up on my life so far i found out that somethings you want you really don't want.

Item_Response: The Mushroom Robots                   One day in The Brown Mushroom Rebel Base (BMRB) they were working on an experiment in the underground laboratory and were making a rebel robot so strong it would destroy the rein of King Barry (The evil red spotted mushroom) and his army of evil squids. As they were working the leader of the experiment, Triston Mushberg, came in and asked where they were in the project. 'Not so far sir'. Said John Mushinham the junior scientist. 'King Jeffery III ,leader of the BMRB, is requesting a medicine robot for the mini hospital down the hall.' Said Triston Mushberg.         Meanwhile at the Red Spotted Mushroom Base (RSMB) they are making robots of their own. King Barry is planning on making an animal robot like an ocelot or something to scare the Brown Mushroom Rebels. His son Prince Eggbert I disagrees with his fathers evil plan to enslave all of the Mushroomians. His scientists then start designing a high tech ocelot that will scare the BMRB to peices. When it was done they tested it out on Bob Van Stinklaberg (Their testing dummy). Let's just say his service was a week from then, R.I.P..Then they locked it up in a cage and left it there until they needed it.          Back at BMRB  there was a new rebel. Her name was Zoey but she was not a mushroom she was a human. She got accepted because of she was a smart girl, she was a scientist, mushroom enthusiest and an alchemist but the brown mushroom rebels didn't know about the alchemist part, they frown upon alchemy. They beleived she could help construct the robots so she accepted the challenge and got to work on the Rebel Robot and Medical Bot.           At the RSMB they were doing completely nothing and King Barry was bored so he just slept all day and when he woke up he realized he only slept for a half n' hour. So he got out of his bed and went to the laboratory they were working on a mobile that can drive its self. It was nothing that King Barry has ever seen before. Mostly because it wasn't done. So now the RSMB was just waiting for something to happen.              Now we are back at the BMRB and Zoey has finished creating the Rebel Robot and the Medicine bot. She says their technical names are Rebel Robot: Prototype 4593 code blue nick named Johnny Iron. Medicine bot: Prototype 555 code red nick named Red Five. They were done and King Jeffery III was happy with the girl and expected higher quality work from then on. He then asked her to construct a super computer in the bases only abandoned room. She then tried to find a way out of it and tried running away but a gaurd named Teep (The Mute Dinosaur) caught her and locked her in prison she then formed a band with the other inmates and became 'famous' for her song 'The mushroom prison blues'. One of the inmates was a robot named John he was made to look like a human but the scientists failed and John went bezerk and is wrapped in his robes in prison. She then escaped with a conveinent lock pick on her prison bed and got everyone else out too. She then went and hid in the secret part of her living quarters and wrote in her online diary. She had to go. She started her escape plan and then got to it. She dug her way out through the secret room in her living quarters. She escaped and lived at her friends house for the rest of her life.           King Barry was bored so he planned an attack against the brown mushroom rebels. He got his squid army their robotic suits so they could survive on dry land. He then led his army their and when King Jeffery saw his army coming he went out there with a peice treedy and King Barry refused to sign it but his son, Prince Eggbert, turned the army against his father and then King Barry signed it.            All was well in the land of mushrooms after this point. they all happily lived in the mushroom land where they raised cows and pigs and even grew farms with melons and pumpkins and wheat. King Jeffery and King Barry actually got along after that they would golf and all sorts of things. All of the scientists , not including Zoey, got together and built a car that drives itself. They called it the VroomShroom. The End.

Item_Response: Meet the Hugo       By: Sharon Wu           My dad once said to me robots are might to be treat kindly and be respect. Ben Smith, my dad was the number one robot builder. He became famous by building the world's smartest   robot, Mert. Mert was sell for billions and billions of dollars. He made so many robots rapidly, he won the Noble Peace Prize. In his twenties, he marry to my mother, Linda and he was the happiest man on the face of Earth.When I was 1 years old, my dad die and no one knows what happen. The world's face is now the saddest thing in the universe.He left a present that wasn't finished, the Hugo, for me.            Now I'm 12 and decide it was my duty to finished the Hugo. The Hugo look like it was half done and also broke. I thought to myself ' Sharon, you can do this, it was the only thing your dad left you'. While studying the Hugo, I found a dusty paper that was wrap up like it was top secret. As I open the paper, I found a letter that was written for me! Dear my little girl, It was hard to let go thing that were very important but sometime you have to. I left the Hugo for you because I trust you,my baby.There is something very crucial that I have to tell you. A group of people called Black Trade, are searching for the robot I left for you.You must completed the Hugo before they find it. Once you finished the robot, you must control Hugo. Be careful! The Hugo can go overpower and destroy the world. I love you                                                            Love,                                                                      Daddy             On the back of the letter, it had a blueprint of Hugo. It was little confused at first but I knew what was it talking about. On the first month, I finished the body of Hugo. The second month, I made the hands and legs.By the third month I made it speak, which to me is amazing! The end of the year, it was done finally. Hugo shine like the sun and it was so beautiful. I decide to keep it  safe in place no one knows about.              In China , the Black Trade is working hard to find the Hugo. After months and days, they knew where is it but don't know how to get there. Now on the plane, they arrive in America, a place that is not always safe. What will happen?               The Hugo and I was ready to fight them! The Black Trade has arrive at my home. As the front door was knock down, that made me more and more nervous and scared. Hugo and I step in front of them. They look like spy in a black suite. With one shot of a powerful, indestoryable gun, they were dead. Hurray!!    Thank You!Dad

Item_Response: ROBOT MYSTERY                                            Raul Rodriguez      '' Mom can you make a milkshake for me?''I asked.       ''Sure honey what kind do you want?''        ''What kinds are there''?in wonder.        '' There is only mint chocolate chip and cookie dough ice cream's''.she exclamed pulling out the blender.         ''Um can I have both?''        '' Coming right up'' my mom said.She put the ice cream in the blender and started to blend the ice cream up.Then for some reason the blender started to make wears sounds.My mom was holding me to back up just incase.Then she went to go stop the blender.As soon as she was about to push the button, the blender flipped and turned into a walking blender.All of the ice cream was floating out like a root beer float. I was amazed but my mom got the broom and tried to kill it.The blender ,or now a robot,was talking to us.It just spoke funny because the blade was making  a scratchy voice that gave me the chills.     ''What are you?'' my mom said furiously.         ''I am your blender havent you noticed''.       ''You have been a robot the whole time?''       ''Nahhh you think''.the blender said.     ''Well you never transformed any other time''.       ''You were never around when I  did so  you thought I was just a regular blender''. I'm tired of you I said. The only way we will  keep you alive is if you listen.If I say something to you or my mom does  and you don't do it then your dead.

Item_Response: Once upon a time there was a robot toy that came alive, Toby. He was very nice to other toys alive until a girl, Becky, found out he was living. Ever since then he had destroyed everything that made a kid happy.            Becky's mom had bought a toy for Becky's birthday. Toby was excited that someone finally bought him. Becky and Toby had fun memories together. Becky had left for vacation for about 2 weeks. Toby had the time of his life but when Becky came home she saw that Toby was alive. Toby was scared and frightened when Becky had seen him. Since that day he would hide from Becky but later on he didn't care anymore. He was mad he wanted to get revenge because Becky told her family and friends. Toby didnt want to get exposed to others in the world. Toby destroyed everything that Becky loved, so he would make her life disapointing. He wanted Becky's family and friend's life to be disapointing so he did. He threw Becky's moms' ring in the garbage disposal and he cut Becky's dads' gift that his dad had given him. Toby destroyed everything that was most important to Becky's family and friends. Becky and her friends got together and built a robot to destroy Toby. They named the robot they built Destruction 9,000. They brought a doll so Toby can come. The Destruction 9,000 and Toby had a robot war. Destruction 9,000 destroyed Toby for good!           Becky and her friends were estatic. Her family and friends had a celebration. They all missed Toby but he was rude and disrespectful. Everyone had remember that day as it was a fairytale. I would be scared if I saw a toy alive. After that day they lived happily ever after.

Item_Response: It was the first day of summer vacation and I already felt like it was the middle of it .  I was in my room but then I decided to go to the garage to get my bicycle and ride it to the park . There was this big stack and my bike was at  the top I jumped and got it but everything fell down. On the back of all that stuff there was this weird man shaped  thing  I was goin to get a better look at it but mother called that it was dinner time . I ate and then took a shower I was goin to the garage but my dad told me to go to sleep.                                                                                                                                                                        The next day in the morning before my parents woke up I went to the garage .  I went to were the robot was I turned it around where it looks like his head there was a button . So I pushed it and it started moving like crazy up and down it even hit the ceiling . It turns out that it was my dads when he was a kid , he was goin to give it to me for my birthday that was in two weeks .                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                My dad showed me how to work it .It could fly jump do all kinds of exiting things it could get little and look like a dog, cat, mouse, rabbit .All kinds of little animals and big to .I took my robot to the park ,people kept staring and telling me that what was it. I told them that it was my robot  but they dirent want to believe me  . They thought that  I was a lier making everything up . The next day I went to school I wanted to take it with me  but it was to big it couldnt fit in my backpack . Then my dad came in the room and I told him that  '' dad dirent you say tht the robot could transfer into different things. '' then he said '' son thats why I came in the room to give you this controler you can transfer him with this control. '' The boy took it from his father`s hand`s and started pushing the buttons it went outside and climbed the tree ,then I pushed another one and it came down right in front of me . I looked at one  blue button and I pushed it it transfer into a bunny . I pushed  a red one and at first it smelled like fire then it started burning  out of nowhere it exploded. Into million little pieces  I was horrified how could I just do that , I was shocked . I went in there and told my dad he made a face then went in the house, he took a trashbag and started picking the pieces of the robot  he said  ''it`s ok son I new someday this was going to happen  thanks to you it`s sooner .''                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             THE END

Item_Response: Students Directions              This story is about robots around the world. For example,they help other people doing stuff they can't do like climbing a tree and so far.But some robots got different stuff there supposed to do. And they all got different names like Gemini-Scout,Dante 2,Agribots,Mr.Gower And There's More Than just that. There Scientist name them all the time even when there about to make them.There strong and helpful. There where some story's that where just fantasy about robots but then when they read each and every one of them they started building alot of the robots making them have special abilities.            The Gemini-Scout is a remote-controlled robot that does search-and-rescue work in mines and under the ground. The robot is less than two feet tall and has wheels. It can even roll through water. The robot is small,but it is strong. Gemini-Scout carries food,water,and other supplies. It can even drag hurt people to safety. So that one is helpful for many things just for man's they cant roll through water and its not that big but it is strong. It can even drag hurt people to safety.           The Dante 2 is a robot with an interesting job it climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientists. Like a spider, this robot has eight legs. This helps it climb the steep walls of the volcano. It is also built to survive very high heat. When a volcano is too dangerous for scientists to enter, Dante goes instead. Dante 2 looks for vents, or holes, in the crater. Then the robot collects information about gases that come out of the vents. In the past, scientists could not learn as much about volcanoes, but Dante 2 is changing that. Now scientists can study volcanoes.                                              Mr.Gower is a robot that works in the hospitals, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. Mr.Grower looks like a small cabinet on wheels. The body of the robot is a stack of locked drawers that store medicine. Nurses and doctors can unlock the drawers when the medicine is needed. Mr.Grower can go anywhere in the hospital. It can ride elevators,steer through hallways, and move around things that get in the way.            An agribot is a robot that picks fruit. It might pick berries,oranges,grapes,or apples. Agribots are not yet widely used, but farmers are very interested in what these robots can do. Because picking a strawberry is different that picking an apple,agribots come in all shapes and sizes. Some have giant arms that are towed behind trucks.Others are able to move around on their own. In Japan, there is a strawberry-picking robot that can sense the color of the berries this helps the robot know when each berry is ripe.But when a robot senses that a tomato is ripe, it uses a mechanical arm to pick the tomato. Agribots may seem unusual now, but one day they nay be common farms.

When my friends saw that the robot was timing a bomb they said,' We can probably re-construct the robot not to bomb the city. I just had got my screw driver and  I saw that Elle was progrmming her self to charge. Then I quickly  grabbed my I-phone 5 in my pocket and called all of my friends to come over to look at Elle.          Elle had just finished charging when  my friends came over. My friends and I had found the re-construction manual I quickly grabbed my screw driver and took off the screws. Then I saw the bomb I took it out of Elle and took the bomb off and put it far away. Elle was shut down and the UltraMega Indusrty was sued because of the bomb and was never seen again.

Item_Response: Christopher Rodriguez                                           Freddy the robot                                     'The robot is neraly finished sir, what will we do with it again?' said John, Larry's assistant,'We will use it to help us with the study of the toxic or radiated area of the site the accident happened.' said Larry.'Why must we spend so much time on it why dont we just forget about it?' said John.'Because there might be someone or something important out there we also need to study the area and how bad its affected.' said Larry.'Ok nearly finished i just need to insert the chip an-.' John stopped.       'Greetings' said the robot.'John we did it we finally got it working!'said Larry.'Shall we take it sir?'said John.'No,we must run a few system checks on it. Get on that terminal over there see if you can get it to work by using voice control.' said Larry.'Right away sir' said John.'What shall you call me?'said the Robot.'I've been thinking about this hmm.' said Larry.'Is freddy a good name sir?'  said John.'Excellent choice' said Larry.'Lets get going we are using time to study this' said Larry.'Good I was starting to think we were going to be in this lab forever.' said John.       'Camera link establish.' said Larry.'System activated.' said Freddy    'Activate communication and thermal comms.'said John.'System activated' said Freddy.'Go in and search for survivors and useful items'said John.'Also collect samples of the toxins'said Larry.'Request accepted,commencing.'said Freddy.'Its been hours should we call it?'Said John.'Yes,it might have found something.'said Larry.'Freddy come in.'said John.       'Yes master?'said Freddy.'Have you found something?'said Larry   'I found 10 samples and an item'said Freddy.'Activate GPS and come back. Also pick up anything you see that is important'said Larry.'Good the robot is back'said John.'Here are the sanples and item.'said Freddy.'Oh my gosh wait that is the-'Larry stared at the item.'What sir?'Said John.'Its my old note and picture of my family'said Larry.'Why is this such a shocker?'said John.'Because, it was the day of my first happy,family vacation.'said Larry       'Does it really matter?'said John.'Yes and always will be.'said Larry.

Item_Response: The Robots                    It was a cold and rainy night in Washington DC, the entire city  was dark, the people, fast asleep. But there was a faint light coming from one building, the small sign above the door read, ' I Robot Labratories- Robot reaserch and devolopment building'. Meanwhile, a homeless man romed the streets in serch of food and a place to stay to pass by the night. When suddenly he turned the street corner and saw the faint glow of light through the window of the labratory, so he went to go see if anyone was there that could help him.               He approached the building cautiously, for the door was cracked open and he did not know who or what could be in it. When he got to the door he slowly and quietly opened it just enough so that he could see inside. Inside he saw all kinds of tools, pieces of metal and robotic parts. But then he saw it, a long red streak across the floor leading into the back of the labratory. He was in shock wondering what could be back there, but he slowly and quickly collected all of his thoughts and went to investigate.

Item_Response: The Human Robot   By Hudson Chomoa           I once had a robot its name was Thedore De Latte and it had a real brain. It was human! As soon as I found this out I Tweeted it and 400 of my followers saw that he was real! I originally got him at a garage sale because the owner said he was broken, so i took him apart at my house and found he had real human body parts.       I called the police and they came three minutes later with two guns pointed at him. The robot was moving it didn't have slow robotic movements it moved very quick lunged out the window and headed for town. The FBI and S.W.A.T came and tryed to stop him and as soon as we got him in a corner he said, 'So long' and flew up onto the sky!           Two years later after supper while I was watching TV the news reporter said that a meteror hit Southern California. As soon as i saw the pictures I saw that Thedore was in the old rock. I shouted at the TV yelling  his name. I remembered his name on the package was D2-7gp but I called him Thedore because that was my cats name.           I flew to California to so the bot but he was in a locked room full of rangers. I could here them talking though they said, 'We need you to help some miners out they're trapped in a coal mine just south of the Mexican border. You are going to get some heat sensor cameras for the job.' 'Ok sir' Thedore replied. 'You will need to drag the hurt people on your back. You are going to give them some supplies and food. Of he went saving thousands.

Item_Response: TROUBLE WITH ROBOTS                                     By: Grace       It was a warm Friday afternoon, summer of 1978. Everything started normal.      I got up at 9:32 sharp, I ate pancakes as usual, took a shower and headed over   to the beach to meet my friend Samantha.           We usually go for a swim till lunch, then we go to bill's hot dog stand to get something   to eat. But today was a red flag, so we couldn't go swimming. This was un-usual.          So as our back plan we went to the pool. The pool was open Monday-Saturday.   A old, creepy, mean guy owned it, he was always up to no good.       But we'd never ever ever thought he would do this.       As Samantha and I were splashing around and having a good time we heard a loud   crash in the man's shed, (right near the pool).     I got up and told Sam we should go see what it was.       We peeked around the corner. I almost screamed! DU DU DUNNNN!!!!        In the shed, large rows of Gemini-Scouts were lined up and the man was looking them over.              Gemini-scouts were helping robots why would the mean, old man be helping?          I walked in no longer afraid. Sam tried to stop me but I kept going.       'Hello', I called. He spun around fast. 'What are you doing here!!!'   'We can to see what the big crash was about.'           'Nothing now get out!!!' 'O-k, jees!'         We left and Sam had to go home. I guess that's enough excitement for one day I thought.               That night I heard a loud noise. I got and looked out my window.   I saw the robots from earlier! they were coming and invading!!!!          I had to stop it. The man must have trained them to break things!        I remembered from the book I read about them the always helped a injured person i had to pretend to be hurt.          As scary as it was I layed down in front of one and waited.   soon after he helped me and they all remembered.        I called the police and they arrested the man.   All was well, well for now!!!           i
