Item_Response: Bill's New Friend.          One day, in the city of Terryville, a boy named Bill was in deep sleep.  He was dreaming about robots and the gadgets they have.  He dreamed that one day he will have his own robot.  He dreamed his name would be Terry and they would be best friends.  Bill didn't have many friends.  He didn't fit in well with everyone else.  He had a small house and had ripped clothes.  He just wished that he could have a true friend.            When Billy woke up the next day, he went down to eat breakfast.  It was a Saturday and he had no plans for that day.  Then he started thinking about the robot.            'Mom,' Bill asked, 'can I have a robot?'            'A robot!'  Bill's mom answered.  'In what world could we afford a robot?  We can barely keep the house heated!'            'Maybe I could make one!'  Bill exclaimed.  'Please mom, can I, PLEASE!'            'What would you use to make one?'  Bill's mom asked.            'Easy, I could use my old toys and some scrap metal in the shed!'  Bill said.             'Alright, Bill's mom answered.  'But you have to pay for allof it!'             Billy got so excited, he only ate half his breakfast, and then ran to his room to find his useless toys.  He thought to himself, 'I'll use all of my legos, my army men, and my robotic dog.  Bill got all of the scrap metal in his back yard and went to work.  At first, he had to decided what to make the body out of.  He chose the scrap metal.  The body would be 4 feet in diameter.  It would have a compartment in it for anything he wanted.  He also made the legs and the arms out of scrap metal.  they could move around very easily.  He made the hands and feet out of plastic from the legos and army men.  He melted them so he could mold them.  He added wiring throught the arms and legs to the hands and feet so he could move around and pick up stuff.  Finally, he made the head.  He use scrap metal for that, but he put the battery from the robotic dog in it to act as a brain.             Bill added extra acceseries.  He added a plug inj for the battery in the back of the body.  He made a face and gave him a tie.  He added a milk shake maker inside the compartment.  It made what ever flavor you could ask for.  He added a jetpack so it could fly.  Ofcourse Bill would need to add a strap so he could hold onto it and they could fly around together.  Finally, he nemed him Terry, after their town's name, and engraved it into the top of his body.  Then he plugged him in so he would charge.            3 hour later, Bill went to turn him on.  He wouldn't move.  The robot was frozen.  'I should of known that this wouldn't work!!!!'  He yelled.  He went to bed that night.  before he went to sleep he made a wish.             'I wish that my robot would come to life!  I spent all day making it.'             The next day, Bill woke up to the sound af a weird voice.  It was his robot!!  He ran down to the shed tosee him.  His mother had already beat him there.             'Oh my Lord!'  Bill's mother yelled.  'What in the world is this?'             'It's the robot I made,' Bill answered.  'His name is Terry.  I thought he would never come to life!'             Bill became best friends.  The next day at school, he brought his robot.  He was amazed at how differently people treated him.  They were drooling over Terry.              'I want it!'  Yelled just about every kid there.  Of couse Bill would never give up his new best friend.  They were going to work together to do his homework, and to try to get other friends.  The teachers even let him into the classroom.  Bill started getting all A's in class, that they let him out of school early.  He wouldn't have to come back to school all year.            Bill would fly around with Terry and they would got to the top of skyscrapers, the mountains, pretty much where ever they wanted.  The only bad part was that every night, he would have to charge.  Bill eventually upgraded Terry and gave him wheels.  He could go as fast as 567 mph.  They entered him in races and they got rich!  Bill and his family moved out of their small house and into a mansion.             'Bill, you have made us rich!'  Bill's mom said.  'We can never thank you enough.'            'For now on, you get what ever you want!'  Bill's fathere said.            'No need for that, Terry made all of the money,' Bill said.  'You shouldn't give me special treatment.  Terry should be getting what ever he wants!'            'Beep, I Love You,' Terry said.  'You can do whatever you want with that money, besides, you made me.'            Bill kept upgrading Terry.  Soon he could dive under water, explore space, and he ran on solar power so they wouldn's need to charge him.  The family's power was out of control.  They could do whatever htey wanted.  They bought a castle, and had their own army!  Soon, they could be the richest family in the world.            Terry started to do more jobs, like taking people under water to where no submurine could ever go.  Scientists hired him for research.  Bill and Terry were getting split apart.  Bill's parents were so power crazed, that they didn's care about Bill and Terry having fun.  They just wanted money.  Soon Bill said 'Enough!'  He hid Terry in his room, where his parents wouldn't find him.  He spent all his time with him.  Whenever his parents asked where he was, Bill just didn't answer.              Every night, Terry would take bill on an exciting adventure.  One time, when they were going int space, Terry's solar panel's were hit by a meteorite.  He lost all power immedietly.  Bill was trapped in space with his best friend broken.  He was still alive, but could barely talk.  He knew he needed to get him in a charger right away.  He didn't even think about himself sufficating.             Bill kept trying to fix his solar panel, but it never worked.  He eventually started getting light headed.  Hepulled Terry back to Earth as fast as he could.  He knew if he took to long, he would die.  He made it into the atmosphere three sceonds before he ran out of air.  It was a long fall, but he landed in his swimming pool.  Bill got Terry on a charger and he came back to life.  He never wanted to go into space again.             Bill hid Terry in his closet, and because Terry wasn't doing any jobs, his parents kept moving into smaller houses because they couldn't afford the ones they were in.  Within three years, they were moved back into their house that thy lived in at the beginning, and his parents took their jobs back.  Everything was back to normal, and Bill and Terry were best friend for the rest of his life.                                                                                                   The End

Item_Response: The Robot           There once was a toy robot named No and his owner Josh that lived in Wash burn, IL. One day a kid sprinkled cheese on the robot and he came to life. Josh was so happy that he took it to his mom and his mom said he could have it programed to do whatever he wanted the robot to do. So Josh took the robot to a programer and he said to the programer, I want you to program this robot to talk, do my chores, print money, buy video games, and listen to Josh's commands only. The programer took the robot and said it would take $300 to program the robot to do so many things. Josh went home and asked his mom for $300 to  pay for the robot to be programed to do those things.       The next day, Josh, went back to programers shop with the $300 he needed to have his pet robot programed, but the programer was not done programing his robot just yet, so Josh went home and waited until the next day. The next day he went to the programer and he asked f his robot was was done being programed, it finally was. Josh gave the programer the $300 that he owed the programer to program his robot.       Josh took his new robot home and showed it to his mom and to the rest of his family. They Loved It! Josh had the robot make a lot of money and then sent the robot to the cities Walmart. The robot brought home an X-Box 360 with Kinnect along with three very good games. One of the games was called Call of Duty Modern Warfare Two. Then Josh let each of his family members give it a try.           When they were all done Josh told the robot to go and do the dishes. He did. The robot was a major achievement for the whole family. The family was always able to just sit down and relax while they watched the robot do all of the house and yard work. One day, about three weeks after the robot was programed, Josh decided to take the robot to school and show it to all of his classmates.       Josh's classmates tried to have the robot do a lot of tasks, but the robot only listened to Josh. So whatever they told the robot to do, the robot refused to do it. After a long time the robot got old and rusty so Josh had to scrap it, and he never saw it again.

Item_Response: 'Kevin! You hovercraft is here!'       'Just a minute mom! I have to pack my schoolpad!'       Kevin McFanter really wasn't packing his schoolpad, which gave him all his notebooks and textbooks that you would probably use in the 2000's. He wasn't eating his breakfast either, which happened to be a milkshake that gave you the strength of the world strongest man and the speed of the world's fastest man. What Kevin was REALLY doing was adding the finishing touches to his new robot, which was a combination of Wall-E and R2-D2; meaning Wall-2D2.   The only reason he even knew about those old stories form centuries ago was because of his grandfather, who had inherited pictures of the two fictional robots from his grandfather, who inherited the pictures for his father, a fellow named George Lucas.   Along with those picture there were blueprints on how to make a actual version of the robots, which Kevin obviously used.   'There, finished!' exclaimed Kevin. Wall-2D2 was done and ready to roll all around the house.  It had a head with two mechanical eyes that had windshield wipers, a dome body that was blue and white and resembled the head and torso of R2-D2, arms that could extend to almost 5 feet long with hands that resembled those of a Lego mini figure, treads for feet, and a whole lot of mini gadgets that Kevin added to the design. It had a cup holder, DVD and CD player, coffee maker, mini fridge full of meal milkshakes, a holographic picture device, rockets hands and, in case of emergency, a self control mode where you can get inside of Wall-2D2 and control it to your liking. It was as if nothing else was needed at all.   'Kevin, come on!' Yelled his mom, Kathy McFanter'You're going to miss the school hovercraft!'   'Coming mom!' replied Kevin, adding the 55 gigawatt batteries to Wall-2D2.   All of a sudden light comes out of Wall-2D2's eyes. The Kevin hears a voice.   'System Start Up initiated. Please adjust settings to liking of owner.'   'Wow!' yelled Kevin'That was sooooo cool!' Then Wall-2D2 says' Hello valued master. My names is Wall-2D2. Please insert you name into the touch screen on my back.' Kevin types his name in using the keyboard. ' Thank you Kevin. Would you like me to take you to school?'    'No thanks' replies Kevin. ' I should really take my hovercraft.'   'You missed it.' says Wall-2D2 'I can tell because of my data scan of a 26 mile radius of the surrounding area. I suggest you hold on to my arms'        Kevin did as he said. 'Wait I forgot my school paaaaaaaaaaddddddddddd!'   In 3.24 seconds, they were out the door and off to Kevin's school.   'Don't worry Kevin. My touch screen has all your data on it. Just pop it off my back and you will be ready for you classes.'       'How did you get all of my notes and all my textbooks on your back pad?'   '26 mile data scan remember?'       And so, Kevin went off to school, which was only two hours long because of all those intelligence chips that they have in those Thinking Caps, and went home from school with Wall-2D2 and had fun for the rest of the school year and summer.

Item_Response: Look, it is not the easiest thing on earth to be a robot.  People always asking me really hard questions and telling me what to do. Think about it, would you like to be ordered around all day. But why would you want to know how I came to be, fine I'll tell you.          I was a very little machine when I came to this earth with you  uncivilized humans. My twin brother and I were using our almost computer like intelligence since we were born. Oh wait, we are computers! So, like I was saying, I was an inanimate object until one day my heart seemed to have died, I think you humans call it a computer crash?         I woke up here and as alive as can be! So now I'm a walking, talking computer man or what you call it, a robot. Here, right now, in New York City! 'Taxi,' 'Which way to__________?' It is crazy in the BIG CITY, (Note: Read that on a billboard). So walking around and I see this guy in a hot dog! I mean who jumps into a hot dog and holds a sign? In the BIG CITY everyone is soooo rude! Unacceptable, not going to tolerate this, they called me a robot! I know I have shiny buttons and I say 'Beep Boop Bop' but I think everyone can be human if they want to.                                          'Help, help!' I hear as the building is starting to fall! I start running towards the building to save the humans but I was to late. Suddenly, I hear the voice again, 'help, help'. ' What do I do?' I asked myself. My eyes spotted a hole in the rubble. I sped as fast as I could into the hole searching for any sign of human life form. I saw her with my thermo camera. I sped into action and pulled he out of the rubble. I saved her life and she saved mine because now I am her servant and get treated like a normal person.                                                                        So to conclude I now live a perfectly happy life now running my own search web site, Google.

Item_Response: Once apon a time there was a little girl named Khewa, who was a genius. and she had to make and invention for the invention convention. So she built a little electronic dragon, it was pink and could breath colored mist, which was supposed to be rainbow,  and it could print money and could fly in the air with it's little wings. So Little Khewa was on her way to school , to put her invention at the invention convention which was taking place at school, then out of no where, this evil girl who was twice Khewa's size came and called khewa crazy, Probably because she was jealous, after all kharia's invention was a cardboard box with a face on it! Then she pushed khewa's invention into a puddle, and it was ruined. Khewa picked up the broken, wet pink dragon and carried it home while running.She was devestated.     Khewa told her mom what had happened and her mom gave khewa milk and cookies to comfort her and khewa went straight to bed. she slept for the whole day.then at around 11:50  she heard something in the closet. she  though it was her imagination. but then ten minutes later, at midnight she heard something crashing out her window. She looked, and she thought she was dreaming, it was her invention! except it was wasnt an invention anymore, and it wasnt broken and wet, it was a real, life size and it was huge! it was pink, it could fly, it even breathed rainbows and  REAL money! But however , it had magical powers , something Khewa had not put on her invention. She screamed 'MOMMY, DADDY, LOOK MY INVENTION CAME TO LIFE!' they didnt believe her and said, 'GO TO SLEEP SWEETIE YOU ARE PROBABLY HALLUCINATING.' but khewa disobeyed them.       She jumped on the dragon's back, but however , its back wasnt all scaly and rough, it was soft, as soft as baby's skin, and light pink. she put her face against it's soft back and off they went. They kept going higher, and higher and higher into the sky until they were in space. Khewa kept her grip on the dragon because she didnt want to float away because of the gravity. Then they landed on the moon. The dragon twitched her nose and then the moon became pink. then candy started coming from the sky, i mean the universe. They they lived there happily ever after. far away from mean people.                                          THE END !

Item_Response: One day while I was working on my robot Version AP341CV, I attached a powerful device called a G.E.C.K to his central nerve system and he came to life.  I would say that it was the most incredible thing that I have ever seen!  This is the beginning of a new era.         It started when I decided to modify his special abilities even though he hadn't came to life yet.  I gave him the power to freeze, the power to burn, and the power to bring back the dead as if they were young again.  I thought of something strange when I gave him these abilities.  I thought,'What if he goes mad with power and starts thinking for himself?'.  That is a common feeling for an advanced humaniod, so I also gave him a reset code and a self-destruct code just in case he does think for himself.  Now I have made a robot before, but Version 890DFW5 type robots can be easily duplicated.  If I lost Version AP341CV then all my lives work would be gone.  Everyday, I decided to work with him.  I eventually put him in a skin graph to give him skin so people didn't know he was a humaniod.        I want only the Club Members to see Version AP341CV.  He is going to help us with experiment projects that have died and assist our newest member.  He is not under anyone's command, but he is friendly if you ask nicely.  I am proud of my accomplishment on building such a great robot.

Item_Response: One day I was sitting in my tree house and I decided to do something exiciting,new,and adventurous. I thought and thought about what I could do. I thought for days straight and then it hit me.I could bulid my very own robot. The next day I started and planned out how i would make it. I decided to do something simple just use a cardboard box and piant a face on. I bulit my robot and spray painted it silver with googlie eyes on his head.   By the time I finished it was time to go to bed. Before i fell fast asleep I said I wish my robot was real. The next morning I woke up to the banging of pots in the kitchen. I went down to check what it was but i didn't see anything. I looked around some more and I saw my robot making breakfast, I closed my eyes because I thought I must be dreaming. When I opened them I saw I wasn't dreaming. I tried to hide it before my parents woke up and then I thought of what to do. I gave it to the local police station for they could use it  for rescues. The next day I looked in the newspaper and i saw a section about how a robot saved many lives. I was glad I gave it to the police station , but I still wonder to this day how that robot came alive.

Item_Response: Robb      My mom and i were in her car at the store hearing music when all of a sudden her car was moving.We both got scared and got out of the car screaming and running. We saw it transform into a gigantic robot. It was standing on two wheels which were its feet. The robot looked so scary. It turns out it was a good robot . We called him Robb.      Robb transformed back into a car and took us to our house with us driving. He could talk like a person. Robb was really strong , he was like a superhero. He helped my whole family with outdoor chores. He could turn into any shape and size. What ever we told him to do he did it. If Robb saw people that were injured. he rushed to the hospital.     Not only did Robb do that but he can also play with any kid that he sees. Robb always has enough time for adventure. He can also sing, dance,and even play music. Sometimes we have a contest of who can dance . Robb also plays the piano, he is a really good robot for me.

Item_Response: I was sitting in my basement and I just finished my school science fair project.I was doing a project with my two best friends: Zoe and Izzy. I had decided to build a fake, non-working robot I saw on my favorite TV show. 'I wonder if we'll win!' I said to myself.       Soon after that,  Zoe called me and asked if  I was ready to hit the fair. Zoe, Izzy  and I set up our booth. Although we hadn't been very clever with the booth title, it was more creative than most of the other names. Before the judges started judging us we had a little time to scope out our competition. ' ATTENTION! Attention student scientists, please make you way back to your booths so judges may begin.' Shouted our principal Mr.Henry over a mega phone.We started to head back our booth when the judges got to the first project.       By the time the six judges got to us, I had pretty much chewed my nails down to nubs. They asked A LOT of questions. I was pretty disappointed... the judges didn't seem impressed at all. Maybe two minutes after they were done, my robot, just CAME TO LIFE!! ' OH judges!' Izzy yelled. ' Pipe down! This is NOT supposed to happen.' I chimed in. I could tell Zoe was just thinking Jenna! This could really help us! Just once, let Izzy use her big blabber mouth! So I sat back and let Izzy run the show. 'JUDGES!! COME BACK!' she yelled. The judges came back to 'rejudge' us. I'm pretty sure they liked it.       My robot coming to life actually helped us. Surprisingly we came in second. Going original there huh Lisa Collins, stupid paper matte volcano. I guess if I'm EVER in a science fair again I'm definitely going with a come-to-life volcano.

Item_Response: Once when I was sitting in my room reading a book, I heard a loud thump. I thought I just might have been my dog jumping off the couch until I went into the living room. It was my robot that I tried to build one day when I was bored. I thought I did a pretty good job. The robot was standing up looking right at me not moving at all. Now you probably think this sounds weird but I couldn't get the robot to actually work.         All of a sudden he just walked away and started cleaning the house. Now this is what I programed to do. I followed him and he said something but I just couldn't make out what he said. I asked him to repeat what he said and he said 'My name is The Fred Bot.' I named him that because I never thought that he ever would be able to talk. 'I didn't program you to do that Fred Bot' I said. 'I programed myself' Fred Bot exclaimed. Then out of no where Fred Bot busted through the door and scurried away.          I was going to run after him but I just let him run free. I didn't really know Fred Bot that much bu I think we would have been best friends.

Ramos                                                   The year was 2025 and the year was big for robots and one specific person named Jesse Ramos never knew that his life would change.He woke up one morning deciding what materials he should build his robot out of.He finally rested his mind on steel so he got to work.The day was hard (well hard for him) he cut himself many times and burned himself.He was completed but he did not have a power source and it turned out to be a stormy night.A bulb went off in his head he suddenly had an idea.He would take his creation out on to the roof of his house and let the lighting hit the robot.But instead of that happening his mind was put inside of the robot.                 He suddenly woke up it was a dream but he really did have a robot to build.But a big noise was heard on top of the roof.So he went to inspect and what he saw was unatural, his robot was moving around.The robot finally saw him and strolled foward.the robot said:hello master Jesse was astonashed.Jesse was very happy to see that his robot was intact.The robot was tolled to do all of his chores and other things to do.That was until a ufo abducted jesse and thats when the robots journey begins.                    The robot was built with jetpacks inside his body so it did not take long for the robot to reach the ufo.He devised a plan which was to sneak inside the ufo,kick some alien but and be out with jesse.He got inside super easy thanks to his super strenght jesse put in.He threw out all the aliens and saved jesse, got off the ufo and gave jesse a space helmet.They got home around 9:00 they decided that they had a long day so they hit the sack and lived happily ever after.

Item_Response: One day a little boy named Tom lived in a very small town. He always watched TV and one day a commercial came on that showed a robot building kit. Well Tom also loved building cool gadgets, and he never built a robot before so Tom asked his mom if she can but him the robot kit she said ' right after you clean your room.' So tom got really excited ran upstairs and started cleaning his room.           Once Tom got done he went down to his mom and told her he cleaned his room. so she said 'alright a deal is a deal.' She got on the phone and ordered the robot making kit. A few weeks later the package arrived. Tom picked up the package on the way in his house from doing chores. He started unwrapping the tape and opening the box. All of the parts fell out on his workbench.                   Right away he began building and after a few days the robot was built. Tom loved the way the robot looked and how small he was. Tom said 'I think I will name him Tom Jr.' That day all Tom and Tom Jr. did was play catch. But what Tom didn't know was that he was in for a surprise tomorrow. That night Tom and Tom Jr. were in Tom's bed looking out the window when all of the sudden a shooting star flew by the window.                       Tom said 'I wish Tom Jr. was really alive and he could play with me and help me do chores.' After that Tom got tired and decided it was bedtime so him and Tom Jr. went to bed. The next morning Tom got up and Tom Jr. wasn't their Tom started freaking out and started saying Tom Jr. Tom Jr. Well what Tom didn't know was that overnight Tom Jr. turned into a real robot that could actually run play and talk clearly. Well Tom Jr. got up and stared at Tom, Tom said 'are you real like really real?'                           Tom Jr. answered back 'yes Tom' Tom started screaming and running into the kitchen. But no one was home because everyone had gone to work. So Tom was cornered and said 'Tom Jr. don't hurt me please.' Tom Jr. said 'hurt you why would i hurt you, you are the one that made me real' so tom started to feel a little better and said 'do you want some cereal?' Tom Jr. laughed and said 'sure buddy' that morning Tom and Tom Jr. ate cereal but Tom Jr. didn't really eat it. The cereal kinda went right through him and out his back. Every time that happened Tom giggled then spit his cereal and milk  went everywhere.                       That night when Tom's mom and dad got home Tom showed them Tom Jr. But his mom and dad weren't to excited about the whole live robot and they said what is that. Tom said ' It is my robot Tom Jr.' They started to calm down and accept him into the family so from that daya on Tom Jr. lived a happy life and did everything with Tom.

Item_Response: ROBOT ALIEN INVASION                                                 Alex is on his way to his house when all of a sudden he hears a loud 'boom' on the other side of the gate.He thinks its strange and goes to check it out.When Alex gets there he sees a big spaceship on the ground.He gets scared when he sees big robot aliens with weapons come out of the spaceship.Alex hides behind a bush and he could hear them talking,but he couldn't understand their language.The robot aliens start walking to Alex's neighborhood,Alex gets worried so he calls his mom.'Mom its Alex, I need you to get everybody out of the neighborhood now','Why what's wrong','There are robot aliens coming to the neighborhood','Alex don't be ridiculous','Mom I'm serious get out now','Sweetie i can't I'm cooking right no............','Mom are you there','No let me go, let me go....... Alex get the others out...'.                             Alex was crying, his mother just got kidnapped by aliens and he doesn't know anything about aliens.Alex is worried sick for his mother right know.Elena calls Alex.Alex tells Elena that there are robot aliens coming to the neighborhood right now and that to gather everybody else to get out of there.Elena already knew that this was going to happen because she's been studying the robots.She is a scientist.And she was the one who awoke the robots.And she knows exactly how to put them to sleep.Just then she made a robot 9000 weapon that can put them to sleep forever.She calls Alex again to tell him to come over to the lab and got the weapons before there are more robots to come.                                By the time Alex came she was packing up the weapons for him and her.They get to the neighborhood and start shooting at the robots.The robots start shooting back but don't get them.By the time Alex and Elena shot all of the robots,they had to put them back in their spaceship and ship them back from where ever they came from.When Alex and Elena are done with that they head back to Alex's house.When Alex enters the house he sees his mom tied up,so he unties his mom and goes up stairs to see if they did any damage.And when Alex gets there,he sees 3 robots talking so he starts shooting at them.The robots are dead.And so Elena says that they can't ship them back without their spaceship.And so Alex starts digging up a whole in the middle of nowhere.He dumps the bodies there and then leaves.Alex and Elena are the only ones who know where the robot's are at.Elena says that they were robots,but Alex calls them robot aliens.And that what they've been through right now is called 'Robot Alien Invasion'.

Item_Response: How Robots came to life              A man was working on a robot and he did not complete it because the robot lacked energy. The mans name was Dan. Dan one day gave up because he tried and tried to make his robot come to life but he couldn't because no where in his village has the proper energy he required. One day Dan sent his robot in a rainy day above his ceiling and the robot was covered in a tarp. The robot was hit by a strip of lightning and he came to life!.       To begin with, when Dan woke up in the morning he saw a plate of scrambled eggs, bacon , and juice on the table and he was puzzled. Dan did not know who made this breakfeast meal so he looked around the house but he found noone. When Dan finished his meal the robot appeared and scared the living daylight out of Dan. Dan asked the robot and asked him who he was, the robot said i was created by you master i was hit by a strip of lighting when you put me up the cieling with a tarp and i came to life. Dan was surprised and he decided to name his robot Fred and Fred liked his name.           In Addition, Dan asked the Fred the robot if he can do anything in the world like make a time machine or even make a watch the talks and tells what time is around the world thats has Satalite Gps. Fred the robot said yes i could but what i really want is have a family and experience the real world. Dan said sure but he said to Fred, Fred im sorry but your family i must need time and collect metal iron and steal to make your family because it took me almost 3 years to complete you. Fred understood and he asked if he can help him build his family and experience the real at the same time. While Dan and Fred go around the village buying parts they had fun like going to the beach going to town and also playing video games which Fred pretty much won because he knew everything about video games.          Furthermore, Dan and Fred spent alot of time with eatchother and sometimes Fred gets lonely because it has been 2 years since Fred and Dan first met each other and Dan is busy making his family because Fred wants to expreince being a father and having kids. One day Dan said to Fred, Fred i almost completed your family and by this two weeks i hear were are going to have rain and thunder so im going to need you to stay in the house because you can rust if you go outside and in the rain. During the time it rained Dan completed Freds family and now fred had a best freind (Dan) and a family Fred had lots of fun with Dan, now he can share his experience with his family. Dan has getting old and Fred was sad because Dan was only 48 when they met and Dan was getting tired and sick, and Freds family was getting sad because they barely knew him. 3 years past and Dan was on the verge of death because of the melted smoke and smog Dan inhaled while completing Freds family and Dan had lung cancer and now he was weezing and he couldnt breath and then he passed away while Fred and his family watch Before Dan passed away  but before Dan passed away Dan asked Fred If he could bury him in his lab so he can remember the good times he had with Fred and his family, Fred said yes and when the time came of Dans Death the robots were heart broken and devastated.           In conclusion, Fred the robot and his family have been living together for a long time and having a memory of Dan. Sometimes Fred is lonely but is cheered up when his family comes back from walking and playing on the grass where Fred the robot and Dan had first been when Fred was alive. During the time Dan and Fred Spent together Fred felt like a normal human. Fred decided to do something special and he went throught Dans robots blueprints and build himself a new robot Dan!!. Now Fred and a best friend that is now a robot and once was a human, now with Fred his Family and Dan the robot They lived a happy and peacefull life in Dans house where they spended the rest of their live together frolicing in the meadows and playing in the grass. The End.

Item_Response: One day I had gotten news that my doctor had died inexplicably. The doctor was like my father, I knew him since I was born. When I went to go see it I saw that he had been pushed out of the window in his office. It was really weird because the window couldn't be broken unless it was a robot. We had some robots that we were still trying to make them come to life but we hadn't succeeded, or that's what I thought. The doctor left a hologram that said, ' I know you must be mad that I am dead, but I did this for a purpose. I made a robot that could change the future. This one is different from the ones we are trying to make, this one has feelings and dreams, he acts like a real person. I told him to do this. This is good bye.' then the hologram shut off. I went to go look for the robot, but to do that I had to ask the doctors assistant what he had done with the robot. The assistant said she didn't know where he was. I had little time to find the robot to tell me what the doctor had told him.   I saw a robot that was trying to run away from me so I had to shoot one of its legs off. I caught up to it then started asking it some questions he told me that the doctor was teaching how to write and talk like a human being. He told me he knew where he needed to take me and took me to the top of the tallest building ever, he said that here he would find another hologram from the doctor. When I found it he had said, ' When the robots come to life you will have a war with the robots trying to save all of humanity. You are the only hope for saving us, take this robot to help you battle the robots and destroy them. They will soon think that humans are not worthy to tell them what to do. Be careful, they are very dangerous when provoked.' then the hologram shut off again.   The battle was very bloody, we kept fighting losing some of our people. We managed to get past the evil robots When 30 robots surrounded us. It was a good thing I had my shotgun to kill half of them. We had to get inside the main hallway of the control system to shut off the evil robots. When we got there it was surrounded by robots so we took the vents. When we got in we got to the controls and shut them off for good. We then tried to fix them to be more peaceful. After two years we made it possible to live in peace with robots.

Item_Response: The Nitro 360            In the year of 2094, a girl named Aurora went up to her bedroom after her tenth birthday party to put all of her new presents that she got from family and friends, away. What she didn't know while going up the long pathway of stairs was that, sitting at the foot of her bed in her bedroom, was one more present from her parents. When she saw how big it was, she gasped. She hurried to put all of her presents away then went to the foot of her bed to open her last present of the day. She tore off the bright red wrapping paper. It was a new robot. One that she had been wanting since she was about 5 years old.       She screamed in excitement. She took it out of the box and put the given batteries into Nitro 360 and tried to turn it on. It wouldn't turn on. She tried and tried but it just wouldn't turn on. She went downstairs to the kitchen to tell her mom and dad that the present that they had bought for her had not been working. Her dad went up to her room to find out what was wrong with the new robot, but couldn't find out what the problem was.        That night Aurora went to sleep disappointed. But while she was asleep, in the darkness of the cold night, there was a loud sound coming from her room. The robot had turned on. Aurora woke up surprised, scared, but also excited. 'Hello. I am Nitro 360. What may I do for you?' it asked, staring straight towards her. She hesitated on saying what she wanted. She just sat in her bed staring right back at the robot for what felt to her like forever. 'Well, can I have a glass of water? I am thirsty.         She watched as the Nitro 360 suddenly shook, creating a loud buzzing sound that reminded Aurora of a bee. In just a second, the giant robot held a cold glass of water with ice cubes out to her.          She was fascinated. She drank the water then went to sleep. Soon enough, Aurora and the robot became friends. Aurora was thankful to have received such a wonderful birthday present from her parents. Aurora enjoys having the best birthday present she has ever received, the Nitro 360.

Item_Response: There was a town in Nevada called Robotown but surprisingly, they had no functional robots. People came excited to Robotown but left unhappily, probably because they expected to find robots everywhere, but found none. The city was constantly trying to make functional robots, but only succeeded in making toys. Their problem was that they had no small sources of power.            But one day a young boy named Ethan was playing with his toy robot, which he named R9-27J, and accidentally made him touch the power box. There was a bright flash and a loud ZZZZZZZ!    'Whoa. What happened?' Ethan exclaimed.   'Ethan, what are you doing?' called his older brother Zachary.   'Nothing!' replied Ethan.   'Hmm... No you're up to something!' said Zachary. Ethan went to barricade the door but Zachary was much stronger than him until.....            'Beep, Beep!' beeped a voice, 'whirrrrr.' Suddenly the door started to close! It was just then when Ethan realized that a robot was helping barricade the door.   'Ahh!' cried Ethan, jumping back from the door.   'Do not worry, I will not hurt you.' said R9-27J. But Ethan was   still afraid of the now-alive robot.   'Worry not little master, I will get rid of this other being.'said   R9-27J. R9-27J made some more beeping and whirring noises and suddenly, Ethan didn't hear his brother outside the door.   'What did you do with Zachary?' asked Ethan.   'Simple. I teleported him.' replied R9-27J.   'Oh tele-wait what did you do!?' yelled Ethan.           'I told you, I teleported him.' replied R9-27J. R9-27J was obviously very futuristic, but TELEPORTING PEOPLE!           'Ok, let me get this straight, you are a robot that came to life from my power box?' said Ethan.   'Yeah, that pretty much sums it up.' said R9-27J.   'So, where is my robot?' said Ethan.           'I am your robot! What would I be if not your robot?' asked R9-27J.           ' Uhh....' said Ethan.           'See? YOU DON'T EVEN HAVE ANY IDEAS!!!!!!!!!' yelled R9-27J.           'Okay,okay,okay. I said OKAY!' yelled Ethan as his robot started to do the things he liked making him do.   ' Anyways, where is Zachary?' asked Ethan.   'Who is Zachary?' asked R9-27J.   ' The 'other being', the person you teleported!'           ' Oh, he is in South America on one of the jagged rocks in the Strait of Magellan.'   'WHAT!!!!!'   ' I said-'           'No, what meaning.... WHY DID YOU TELEPORT HIM THERE OF ALL PLACES!!!!!' yelled Ethan.           'Fine. now he is in a bear's cave in the Appalachian Mountains.'   'No.'   ' Now in the ruins of the ancient city Jericho.'   'Gah!'   'There is no place called 'Gah'.'   'Bring him back to Nevada.'   'Okay, he is back.'    'Where?'   'Lake Tahoe, Nevada.'           ' Fine. Robotown, Nevada. 9497 Turbo Street. In the foyer of the house.'           ' Request granted, very specific request granted.' R9-27J chuckled.           'Can you teleport me and you anywhere in the world?' asked Ethan.           'Yes.'           'Then teleport us to F.R.C., Colorado. The Failing Robot Center, that won't be failing anymore!'           'Request....granted.'

Item_Response: The robot that came alive    Scientists were trying to make a robot that came alive so that we wouldn't have to do a lot of work. So they kept trying and trying and then... it turned on 'WOW' said the scientists,then it shut off they were devastated but they did not give up yet.The next day they tried again then it turned on again then it stayed on .They finally made it work. The robot said'hello'.One of the scientists asked 'what are we going to name it?'. The other two asked each other the same question. How about 'Zion?' asked one scientists. The two scientists said 'Maybe that might just be it!'       A couple of mouths later the scientists came back and had decided on a name for the robot they were going to name the robot Zion.That was the one they could not get that name out of their heads for mouths. The next day they made a couple more Zions but they did not work out as well as the first Zion.The scientists went home and then came back the next day and noticed that the robots were gone.They had wondered where they had gone then one of the scientists was being really quite.'It was you who let them out how could you they were supposes to be in bed like us!' said one of the scientists.'I know where they are.' said the scientists.'Well where are they then!' said both of the scientists 'They are at my house safe and sound.'. 'Safe in your hands i doubt that  nothing is safe in your hands!'  'Why do you say that?'asked the scientists 'Because everything that you get is broken within in five minutes!' 'OK what ever say what you want to say because it is not true.'       The next day they went to find the Zions.After a long while they finally found the last of the Zions and made them clean up the city.The Zions did not like to clean up they want to go play but,they had made a hug mess so they had to clean it up.The scientists made the Zions go to the lab and sit in the corner and think about what they had done.That is the story about The robot that came alive.

Item_Response: I found it a few weeks ago, when I was at the carnival. I came to the carnival with my friend Jacob. It was a Saturday and we had nothing to do so we Jacob's mom decided to drive us to the fair, she thought it would be a good idea. When sehe left we forgot to bring money and Jacobs mom wasn't picking up. There were some awesome rides that we both would've died to go on, but we didn't have any money. I never really focused on the games considering they were all rigged and there was no point in wasting your money on them. We decided just to wander around and look at some stuff. We tried to sneak onto a ride but we got caught. Fortunately the guy running it was cool and let us go with a warning. We were dying of thirst and hunger and still Jacobs mom was not picking up. Then we saw double doors that had 'Do Not Enter' on it. It was like putting a sign on a door that said 'FUN Inside' oon your door. We tried to hop over, and even with the help of eachother we could not get over that 15 foot door. Then , dying from exhaustion, I leaned against the door and and it opened. We felt like such idiots. whhen we wnet inside there were at least 20 trailers all lined up. Some of them looked new and shiny, while others looked like they've been there for oveer a century. It smelld of mildew and dust everywhere. We snuck around so we wouldn't ge caught, and then we saw it.          Jacob pointed at it and said, 'Look at that! Wait, what is that? Is it a robot?,' 'I'm not sure.,' I said. We walked closer to it, and the closer we got to it, the more I could make out the details of it. It had wheels on the bottom and was about two and half feet tall. It didn't have a head and its body was shaped like a rectangular prism. The rest of it was so badly rusted that I could not make out its details. Instantly Jacob said, 'Lets take it.'          I wasn't so sure that was a good idea, but I was so hot and tired at the minute that I was brain dead and just said, 'Sure.' I took it by it's legs and he took it by it's body and we ran off, but not before we heard someone shout 'Hey!' We ran as fast as our legs would carry us. Jacob called his mom and she finally picked up. He told her to meet us in the front of the carnival. We dashed in and out of stalls trying to lose the man chasing us, and when we finally did, we went to the front of the carnival and instantly got into the cool car. Jacobs mom turned around and was suprised to find a robot in our hands. She asked, 'did you win it?' I quickly answered, 'Yes'          Now, as I finally finished polishing the last of the rust off, I could completely make out all its features. It was

Item_Response: Different types of robots!                   Have you ever thought of  robots that could do things not even the most of us humans could do, well your wish has come true! There are many robots that can do things that we can't but they can also work with us. One of the robots the work with us is Mr. Gower, Mr. Gower is a medical assistant robot that brings people medicine it can also work an eleavator and carry 500 pounds. There is another robot that help and save lives , its less than two feet tall, it's the Gemini-Scout! The Gemini-Scout is a miner helper bot that can find trapped miners, bring them supplies and even warn miners about dangerous air. The Gemini Scout is not the only robot that explores and gathers info , this robot gets info about valcanos its a robot called Dante2, Dante2 climbs in to volcanos when it's dangerous it collects gases while scientist are all safe.                                  Robots arent always about research and info many people play with robots   or keep them as pets. There are copy's of animals in robot form people either choose these over real pets because of allergyies or the benefits of not taking much care of them. More than pets robots can also be performers a Japanese robot can play piano with two maniacal arms , a different robot called HRP-4c can sing and dance.    Some robots can play sports perfectly fine for example college students in   Orgean have created Hockey and Shuffleboard playing robots. I know it sounds fake but due to the sattelite laser on it's roof it knows where to go! While testing the car evereything went fine, the vehichle matches the traffic for perfect driving. One of his friends Shauna liked to study alien activity so Charlie thought why doesen't he join her so he did in the RV there were blinking lights different computers UFO toys. Charlie touched one of the figure aliens Shauna came out of no where and slapped his hand 'OW' Charlie said 'what was that for' he exclaimed 'Dont touch what is not yours ok' Shauna said 'Alright, so whatcha look,in at?' 'Some alien activity is going on out here the trees are not around just one big burn mark' Shauna showed him a picture of a burn mark in a circle near the american flag 'WOW' Charlie said 'I know right this is great i might be able to catch a real alien and prove that they are real' Fauna said it so quick in her excitment. Charlie just went with it and said that he was proud of her and then he hugged her 'But i hope the aliens arent harmful right?' Charlie asked 'I don't think so, or maybe.....' 'anyways' Shauna said lets go and see it right now' She exclaimed 'OK LETS GO GRAB YOUR COAT' Charlie said but they were not expecting this horrible thing coming. Soon they found it but there was this giant ship on it 'WOW'Shauna took pictures of it with her camera and said 'Lets go print these out' 'OK' SO they went back to the crazy RV and printed them when they came out there was nothing just the burn mark 'What?' Shauna said 'Whats goin on?'Charlie asked 'Their is nothing but the burn mark why isnt it there?' then suddenly they heard a wierd noise more like a squiking sound they looked out the front sheild then 'AAAAHHHH' they both screamed the purple creature ran and went to the forest 'What was that?' Charlie asked turns out Shauna was a good drawer so she asked Charlie to describe it to her so he did 'it had big green glowing eyes and yellow pupils and purple in its skin with wierd writings on it' 'Can you describe what they looked like' Shauna said 'OK OK it was like jiberish' and they left it at that but it still roams around looking for its invisible ship.

Item_Response: Barkul the Robot was a failed attempt at a robot that is supposed to do your homework but apparently spoons and other kitchen things aren't 'robot approved' he was a pile of scrap. That all changed last month when ball of buzzing light touched barkul a loud boom shook me and the house I thought I was done for I was out of bed but it was as nothing happened I decided to go to bed. that night I had a dream that barkul came to life but died soon after by a passing dump truck it made me realize that Barkul would be a great deal of help to me. The next morning I went to work on Barkul while my parents were in bed but the kitchen was in shreds chairs smashed food strewn across the floor that was when I found Barkul under a pile of bacon he was talking saying 'I need food' I was shocked I almost fell over i tried to tell him he was a robot and couldn't eat anything.       Mick whats all the racket it sounds like a robbery, my dad came down the stairs and didn't even notice the mess or Barkul. Dad its barkul he's alive and working, He is, show me. I picked up Barkul and held it to my Dad he must've thought i was mad he didn't see anything. Mick is this one of your stupid tricks again. I coulden't belive it my Dad coulden't see Barkul or anything Barkul did that would explain why he can't see the mess. I responed with yes (it sounded very scripted). Through the next few days I found that Barkul can instantly put answers down on paper this made quick and easy to 'do my homework'.

Item_Response: Robots Narritive PerformanceTask                      You might think that robots are a thing of the future, but you are wrong robots do many things today. They assist Scientists and even explore volcanoes.                  Today I am in my creative writing club. I have been working on my Robot all week long, finally I am going to be able to present my robot that I worked on so hard all week.                  When I end up going to the front of the classroom I feel like I am ready to present my robot. I am about to press the button on my robot to turn it on and wait for it to start moving. I have not pressed the button yet and it starts moving. I am freaking out inside and my classmates in the club of the creative writing think that I have already turned it on, but I know that I didn't. My friends in the class are saying things like, '' Hey that's such a cool robot how cool.'' When in my head I'm thinking what am I going to do!                    The presentation was finally over, and it felt like it had been for hours! I was so nervous because what if the robot did that again. Even worse what if it did that during class! Everyone would start freaking out and not know what to do. I decided to go and tell the teacher.                   When I finished telling her what happened she went to her desk and looked inside. She pulled out a remote, and said that I used the remote to make your robot move. So it turned out that the robot wasn't able to move by its self after all!

Item_Response: There was a kid named John who got a robot for Christmas. One night, John put batteries in his robott without knowing that the batteries were magical. In the afternoon John put his robot in the basement because he had to go to a soccer game.            An hour passed and John went to the basement to go get his robot. When he saw that he wasn't there, he told his mom if she had gotten him. she said ,''No.'' John went to his room and saw the robot walking around his room.            John screamed. His mom came up and said,'' Whats wrong?'' John just looked at his mom. She turned around and saw that robot that he was walking around his room. She started to scream and garbed John next to her.             Robot came near them and they backed away. Robot said,''Im sorry scaring you. I didn't mean to.'' She came near it and touched robot. Item_Response: My Robot is Alive        It was four in the afternoon and I was still working on my science project for the science fair. For my science project I was making a robot that can help you with your homework like a: teacher or tutor. While I was working on my making my robot suddenly it worked it came to life. I was shocked ,but interested in how it came to life. The robot I made could talk it told me that when I connected the two wires in his control pad it made an electrical shock that made it come to life. I named Carl. Carl was very polite ,but it was time to check if he was made for what he was suppose to do. I asked Carl a few questions, 'Carl what is two plus two?' and he answered correctly he said, 'Four and you know you can count on your fingers.', I giggled yes I know. 'OK Carl what is matter?',I asked Carl answered correctly and I asked him a couple more questions and he got them all right! OK Carl lets head to the science fair.        Carl and I head to the science fair on the way there the school bullies showed up and were bothering Carl and I. 'Leave us alone!' ,I yelled. 'Let's see if this thing can actually work' ,said one of the bullies. Carl grabbed one of the boys and throw him with all his might. Once Carl throw one of the boys the other one ran off scared. 'Carl no that is wrong!' ,I yelled at Carl. 'I was only trying to protect you.' ,said Carl sadly. 'It's OK just don't do it again.' ,I said to him. While we were walking to the science fair i was thinking if  Carl is strong and smart and got mad because that kid was bothering me what would he do if there was a bigger problem than that.        When we finally arrived at the science fair there some kids that had some really great project too ,but I was sure that with Carl's help I can leave this science fair with a gold metal in my hand. I waited for the judges of the science fair to come to review and judge my project. The judges came up to me and asked a few questions. 'What is your project do?' ,one of the judges asked. 'Well this is Carl and I made him to help students when they are having trouble with thier homework.' ,I said. Does it work? Yes of course watch. I grabbed Carl's control pad ,but it didn't work because the school bullies broke on our way to the science fair ,so Carl went crazy and started smashing the other kids projects. Everyone screamed in terror and kids ran out ,but the judges couldn't run out because Carl had them rapped in wire. Then I had a idea when I saw the wires. I am at a science fair ,so there must be spear part around here. I finally fixed Carls control pad and shut him down. I let go of the judges and they gave me the first place metal for saving them and they were inprested that I shut him down so quickly and easly. They congratulated me and I went home thinking what would happen to Carl I guess I will never know. Maybe.

Item_Response: One day in the middle of the night I heard unusual noises under my bed where I had left my robot. I slowly went under the bed to take a peek. A bright light shone in my eyes and I could see my robot swirling around in circles like crazy. I grabbed the robot out of the under and examined it closely.There seemed to be no problem until it talked! 'hellooooooo,' the robot said in a thundering voice. I looked at it, stared, then fainted.          The next morning I scented eggs and bacon coming from the kitchen. I went downstairs and saw that robot cooking and saying'good moring.' I looked surprised but said good morning. It offered me some food and I ate it. I wasn't sure what kind of robot it was. It seemed like a mix of every kind of robot. When I was sick it would bring me medicine. It could do cool tricks like climbing,steering, and talking. When we went to the park it would pick fresh apples from the apple trees. This robot is excellent.

He would wish SOOOO hard for him to have a robot and one day that wish came true.              One day on a bright sunny morning there was a little boy named Drew. This was his morning rutin wake up, eat breakfast, draw, play outside, eat lunch, draw, play outside, eat dinner, draw, go to sleep. But today was different. Something was different about today. But Drew still did his morning rutine, when he drew though something happend!!! The robot he drew came to life!!!!!               Drew was scared but excited. The robot said 'hello.' Drew was amazed at the robot. 'Who are you?' Drew asked. The robot said 'I am fluffy bunny bot.But my friends just call me bunny.''Why are u here?' said Drew. 'You called me here i got your wish and I am here to stay forever as long as you want but I warn you if you wish me gone I can never come back...other than that im here and I would like to go with you everywhere and be with u as long as I can.'said bunny. 'Good we have alot to cover I have been wating for this day for a long time I have made a list of what I want to do if I ever get a robot.'said Drew.            After they got done with all there stuff they wanted to do it was time for dinner. They ate luch at the mall in the food court. Drew ate pizza and bunny just had nothing for lunch. When they got home they sat down at the dinner table and ate but when Drew's mom turned around....SHE SCREAMED!!!!! She pulled Drew over to the side and said 'what is that thing doing in my house?' Drew said 'Mom that is my pet I was drawing and he came off my papper and he told me his name was fluffy bunny but his friends call him bunny.' 'Well how long is he staying then?'mom said. Item_Response: Gemini-Scout is a robot that works in the mines and helps the workers.  It can pull the hurt people to safety, and it can carry food, water, and other supplies. It can also collect information. It can check the air for gases. And it has a thermal camera it uses to find the miners. The miners can use Gemini-Scouts two-way radio to talk to a rescue team. It is built to be easy to use. It is like a video control.       Dante 2 is a robot that climbs up the side of volcanoes. It is a helpful robot that can go inside of the volcano and gather information about the gases in the vents for the scientists. It can survive very high heat. Dante 2 looks around to find vents,or holes.       Mr.Gower is another robot that works in hospitals helping doctors carry medicine. It has locked cabinets that lock up the medicine and only the doctors and workers can open the cabinets for medicine. It is a very smart robot that keeps all the medicine safe so nobody else can get to it. It is also very strong, it can pull up to 500 pounds. It is very helpful to the doctors.       Agribots is a robot that can pick fruit. Some fruits it might pick are berries, oranges, grapes, or apples. Agribots come in different shapes and sizes. They can extend their arm to pick a fruit or vegetable to high for them to reach. It can tell if a fruit or vegetable is ripe enough to pick. I think that it is a helpful robot to farmers.           Some robots play well with others. I think that robots that play well with others are great. They keep people entertained. Some that are helpful and play well are Robbie the babysitting robot in the story 'I, Robot.' The story is about a robot named Robbie that babysits a child and the child likes him but the parents don't because the child spends a lot of time playing with Robbie and have fun adventures.              I think that robot controlled cars are a very good idea. It can sense everything around it and know things that a human wouldn't know. It is very helpful to drivers. It steers, drives, and it knows when someone is turning in front of them. All of the robot controlled cars have to get a permanent to drive. They are very smart. They are a very good invention.

Item_Response: THE DREAM           'Alex, it's time for bed!' Sophie called. Alex was in his bedroom reading The Robot War. It's a story about three kids battle robots to save the world.       'Ok mom, let me get to a good ending point.' Alex answered. That meant read another five chapters before falling asleep, only Alex shouldnt fall asleep because in his story one of the kids died in battle. Alex got scared easily. He will get nightmares tonight.       In Alex's dream he started out in his bedroom, getting ready for school. He was eating breakfast when his mom walks in the dining room, her hair all frizzled.       'Good morning mom.' Alex greeted his mom.   'Good morning Alex honey. How did you sleep?' She asked.   'Fine, but I had a nightmare.'   'Was it the robots again?'   'Yea. I'm fine though, oh, look at the time. Gotta go to school.'   'Love you hon-.' Thats all she got to say to him before he got swooped up by George, the biggest, deadliest robot of all.       DAN, DAN, DAAAAAAAAAN!

Item_Response: Gemini-Scout's Mine Adventure                                 The mine was cold and quiet. The rocky walls and floor glimmered slightly from jems and minerals hidden within the rocks. It was quiet and serene, save for the constant 'drip,drip' sound of a trickle of water hitting a small rock. Suddenly there was movement in a far corner of the cave. A silver robot crawled out from under a pile of rubble. Amazingly, there wasn't any damage done to it by the rocks, except for a couple minor scratches. The words,'Gemini-Scout' were engraved on it. The rather small robot looked around.' Where am I?' It asked itself.          Gemini-Scout realized it was in a large mine. However,it did not remember how it got there. 'Maybe if I escape, I can find someone to help me.' it thought. Gemini-Scout turned and realized it had food,water, bandages, and a rope tied to it. 'That will be useful.' It said. With that, it wheeled further into the mine.             The robot traveled for three days, and still had not escaped. It seemed as if Gemini-Scout would never escape the mine. It had spent some time mining though, and it now held jewels and minerals (and a lot of plain rocks). Suddenly, Gemini Scout heard a sound. It sounded like a mixture of a screech and a squeak. Quickly it wheeled toward the noise.         In a few minutes it had found the source of the noise. A small bat had hurt itself by accidentaly flying into a stalagmite, and it was trying to call for help. Gemini-Scout took out the bandages it hadn't used and helped the bat. Soon it was better,but it could not fly. It had a broken wing that needed time to heal. 'Do you know where I can exit this mine?' Gemini-Scout asked the bat. The bat surprisingly understood and started to hop in the direction of a chamber. Gemini-Scout followed.        The chamber the bat had led the robot to was very bright. The jewels sparkled and shimmered, and the rocks seemed to be brighter than the sun. Gemini-Scout was confused. It had been in this chamber before and hadn't found an exit. 'I don't understand.' It told the bat. The bat shook it's head and pointed with its wing (the one that wasn't broken) to a hole in the roof of the chamber. The hole was the source of the light. Sunlight from it streamed in and bounced off of rocks and jems, making them appear to be sparkling. Gemini Scout launched a rope up to the hole,then it hoisted itself up. The bat decided to stay in the mine, but it seemed to wave goodbye to Gemini-Scout.       When Gemini-Scout got out of the mine,it was as if it was in a whole other world. There was green grass, and the sky was a bright blue. A city appeared in the distance. Gemini-Scout noticed a dirt road leading towards the city. It started to wheel down it. Gemini-Scout wasn't sure what it would find when it arrived at the city. 'I hope I can find someone who knows where I am.' It said. Would Gemini-Scout's hopes come true? Was this the end of his adventure? Or was it only the beginning?

Item_Response: 'And now, the moment you've all been waiting for. Ladies and gentlemen, I present to you....... Alpha2.0!' the director of the robot academy yells. All the other people attending the academy cheer. But to be honest I'm not really impressed. The 2095 robot academy was suposed to be amaizing. All I really see is a shiny figure made out of wires and bolts.       Then all of a sudden, the robots eyes go from electric blue to blood red. As the robot lunges I barely have time to jump out of the way. In about five seconds the robot has changed from a glorified vacume cleaner to a full blown war machine equiped with a full arsonal of deadly sharp or explosive things. Before I know it  I'm sprinting down the academy halls for my life.       As I'm hiding in my dorm room shaking with terror, I hear the screechy sound of a voice saying 'Come out and play!'. Then I see it. A metalic hand punch through the door(the end of me). As I see the robot I start lauhing and so does it.       Turns out the chase was all a prank. Alpha2.0 isn't deadly, it wanted to play. Alapha2.0 is a prank robot built by my friend Arnald. I just didnt know it would prank me.       Alpha2.0 is a robot that has many puposes. It can protect, carry things, drive, and many other things. And what I just had personal experiance with...pranking.       Tonight I am getting him back. I have already desined a robot to look like Arnald's biggest fear. A clown. So lock your doors Arnald, Clownbot1.2.3 is coming after you!

Item_Response: Roberto the Robot           'Kylie!' screamed Elliot. 'What?' answered Kylie. Kylie was Elliot's older sister and she had to watch him while their dad was at work. 'Roberto isn't here, I saw him here yesterday.' 'Maybe, you should look harder!' shouted Kylie. Roberto was a robot Elliot tried to create with his mother. The robot was supposed to do  chores, care for people, and talk.       Elliot worked hard everyday to try and finish the robot. It was difficult for him, sometimes his dad or sister helped, but that was rarely. He wanted to finish the robot and make it a memory of his mother. Their mother had passed away in a car crash a few months ago.       Elliot was always having a hard time since she passed. He always thought that maybe the robot would help him. His dad and sister were no help. His dad was always at work because he had two jobs and they needed money, but when he was home, all he did was yell at Elliot and Kylie. Kylie always was in her room, probably on the phone or something because she was fifteen and was older that him by three years. She sometimes made him food when he was hungry, but he could tell she was also struggling without their mom.       Elliot was still looking for the robot and heard a noise. There was a thumping in the bathroom. 'Thump, thump thump.' He was afraid, but kept going toward the sound. He opened the door and was so surprised. There was the robot, standing two feet tall cleaning the bathroom. Roberto turned around and said,'Hehloo, Elliiiot. ' Elliot didn't answer, but just stood there staring at Roberto. Roberto did the same.       Elliot finally talked to Roberto. Roberto was very smart. He knew things from the past which Elliot had created him to do. When Elliot was sad because of his mother, Roberto always comforted him. Roberto did most of Elliot chores and cooked for his sister, his dad, and Elliot. The robot became Elliot's best friend.       Roberto helped Elliot through all of his difficult times. After three years had passed, Elliot didn't get as sad anymore. His father became more supportive and quit his jobs to work in one he liked and they paid him more, and his sister came out of her room a lot more. Elliot also could tell that she liked the robot because it made Elliot happy and she didn't have to cook anymore. The robot was a good memory their mother.

Item_Response: I have been working on my robot for the last 20 years. My labortories are covered with rejected projects and parts of robots I have never used. Many people believe I am no longer living, I have been working on my fixation so long. My house is quite pleasent, from the outsided, a bright, sunny yellow with multicoloredflowers dotting   my garden. But I can't my job is enjoyable, working in a muggy, dark basement 12 hours a day. But I am determined my newest model will turn out right. I have been working on it for 13 months, 16 days and 24 seconds. Although it is smaller than an apple, it is extremely powerful. For my robot is designed to do anything from getting something from a high shelf, to communicating, to exploding at a single code word. It looks like a small calculator, a light blue colour with a tiny microphone and speaker set, for commands. But there is just one problem. I have no way to power it up.          Maybe, if I could harness the suns ultraviolet rays, that would be enough power. Or be able to snatch lightning the moment in hits the earth. But the most garenteed answer would be to dig a deep trench, low enough I am able to see a churning, underground, river. I could set my little robot in there, and the water would hopefully be powerful enough to charge it. That's my other project. I have been digging for about 6 months and it is finally deep enough where I can see the river. I slowly walked up to it, my little blue calculator in my hand. I flung it hard, deep into the planet. I waited. And waited. Nothing but the sound of the river. I layer down flat on my stomach, and peered into the hole. I could just make out my robot, bobbing and twisting and turning. I sighed, disappointed. Just as I was waking away, I heard a small beep. Then another one, followed by faster clicking sounds. I sprinted back to the trench by my oak tree, and saw my robot had come to life!           Reaching down the deep, it sprung into my hands on legs it had apparently unfolded. I had done it! Now I could do anything! But just as I was running inside, a black car with darkly tinted windows showed up. A large, muscular man stepped out, and, wordlessly snatch my robot. I seethed with anger, 'give it back!' I shouted but the man just replied that, 'no citizen should have this amount of power. The government is taking it. We are going to send it into space. ' I was no longer mad. Just curious. 'Well, ok as long as it gets used.' The man stepped in the car and drove off. I stood there, dumbfounded, as I watched it increase speed. But wait! They had no idea what it could do! One wrong push of a button could send the in tire building sky high! I hopped in my little, solar powered car, and drove full speed down the street. Item_Response: Meet the Robots!       Mr.gemini-scout  is a remote controlled robot and does search and rescue work undeatr mines under ground.The robot is less than two feet tall and has wheels.It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns,and even roll through water.The robot is small ,but it is strong.Gemini-scout carries food,water,and other supplies.It can even drag hurt people to safety.       Donte 2: dante 2 is a robot with and interesting job it climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientists,like a spider this robot has eight legs and climbs up steep walla it can stand the heat. When a  volcanoes is to dangerous  for a scientist do go into they send Donte 2 instead.Donte 2 looks for vents ,or holes,in a crater:Then the robot collects information about the gases that come out of the vents.In the past,scientists could not learn as much about volcanoes ,but Donte 2 is changing that.       MR.gower: is a robot that works and helps patients and brings thing to nurses and doctors.he looks like a small  cabinet nurses and doctors unlock him when they need things,not only does he work on long days but he also can talk he has been programed to say hundreds of phrases, for example, it can say (Calling elevator) or(Your delivery is here).Mr.gower  does work that doctors, phasitions,and nurses used to do.This allows them to focus on  other important tasks.       Agribots:An agribot is a robot that picks fruit it might pick berries,oranges,grapes ,or apples.Agribots are not yet widley used,but farmers are very interested in what these robots can do.Because picking strawberrys is different than picking an apple,agribots come in all kinds of shapes and sizes.Some have  giant arms that are towed behind trucks.Others are able to move around on there own. Item_Response: The Nice Robot             In the beginning, scientist made a robot so it could be a decoration in their office or use as a statue.But the next morning one scientist came in the office to check the robot and it was gone. The scientist Andrew wondered if it have been stolen or it came to live and started to roll around.So Andrew went to go look around for it in the lab before the other scientist got there.Finally Andrew found it.The robot was in the experiment lab doing all kinds of different experiments.          Next,the robot saw Andrew and took off rolling away again.Then Andrew went off running for the robot and finally caught up and stopped him.So Andrew started to talk to the robot and said 'are you able to talk?' but the robot didn't reply so he asked again and then the robot said 'yes.' I cant believe your alive and can talk said Andrew.          Then, Andrew said 'we will keep this our secret and wont tell anyone now lets get you back in the office.' Then the robot replied and said 'okay.' So Andrew took him back to the office and the robot played as a fake robot again.The other scientists came in the office.One of scientists which was Albert saw the robot blink.Then Albert left with the other scientist but Albert ran back in and saw the robot gone!He wondered if it was remote controlled or it was just all magic.He looked all over the place for the robot and found the robot back in the office.             In conclusion, the robot just decided he will stay in the office no matter if they leave or not.So at the end Albert just gave up and went outside with the other scientist.But overall the robot wanted to leave but he never did.All of the scientist came back in and the robot was just standing there where he should be and smiling.

Item_Response: p                                               pp                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         I woke up to the smell of my mom's fresh warming cake, she would only bake it if there was a special occasion going on, but I had nothing in my head that I knew about today. I got off my bed and started heading down stairs.  When I did I just heard a burst of people saying ' Surprize.' I just relized it was my birthday, everyone one remembered but I couldn't myself. My 2 best friends were here my Grandpa, Grandma, Mom, Dad, and everyone else I could think of. About ½ of the cake was done after we all at least took a slice out of it. After the cake we went straight to opening presents, but it was the same thing I get every year : a pair of socks, couple of video games, a huge book that would take me a year to finish, and a movie that I've seen a billion times. I thhoguht that was all, but at the last second when I was going back upstairs my mom took out a 5 foot and 5 inc wide robot.             This stunned me, it took me at least 10 sec to close my mouth again. I looked at and back at my mom. ' What can this thing do?' She replied back saying ' It's remote controlled and you can do anything you want with it.' I didn't say anything after that and just went straight outside in the neighbrohood to play some football with my friends. After a long day of running and laughing I went home. I got home and I saw the robot still standing there, I didn't say anything and went straight to my room. I watched some T.V and played some PS3 and went to sleep.            When I woke up there was something staring right at me, this freaked me out alot. I thought it was my brother because I still was sleepy from having a long day. I got my vision back and I noticed it was my robot I got yesterday. I was thinking that my mother put it up here so I can play with it. I looked at the robot and it looked at me, I was waiting for him to move, but I knew he was remote controlled. Right when I got up the robot asked me if I wanted something to eat. I sayed '  How are you...' Then the robot sayed he didn't need some foolish remote to controll him. This was probably the happiest day of my life. Now I had something to get me anything I wanted. I went straight to my mom telling her of what happened. She didn't believe me but I dragged her up stairs. When she got there the robot was gone.            She said ' stop playing with me I'm busy. I was confused, how can something so big get somewhere without anybody nowing. I was probably dreaming about it, but then I found his tracks leading outside. I followed them all the way until I saw it broken to pieces. I thought to myself and it was probably better that this happened so that I wouldn't become laziy forever.
