Item_Response: Hi, my name is Lucy Okumura and I will be telling you about the weirdest thing that happened to me. Keep reading to find out what it was!       One day, I was in school during science when our teacher, Mr. Rick, told us that we were going to be crafting a home-made robot. Half of the class shrugged, and some did a silent cheer. I was not sure about my feelings about this, but I knew I had to get to work quickly. 'Class is dismissed.' said Mr. Rick. I was still thinking about our assignment and was beginning to get stresse out about it. The rest of the day went by quickly; we ate lunch, had Physical Education class, and then went home. When I got home, I told my mom to take me to a store called Home Depot. It's a really handy store that has everything you need. When we got there, I went into the building isle, with all the nuts and screws and stuff. I picked out all the tools and working materials that I needed to build this robot and went home. Since it was already late, I decided to build the robot later and went to bed. I had slight butterflies in my stomach, wondering how I will complete this big project. Wanting to get away from it all, I closed my eyes and went to sleep.       I woke up to the sound of my annoying alarm clock. The sun was just above the hills, and the sky was blue with a few clouds. I did the usual morning routine and headed to school. When I got there, my friends were standing in front of the gate and talking. Noticing me, they ran up and all asked the same question, 'Did you begin on your robot?' They all had baggy eyes and an expressionless face. I shook my head with grief. When the bell rang, we quickly went to class and began the lesson. It was another stressful day, but I survived it. When I got home, I began on my robot right away. It took all night to make, but it was definitely worth it. The finishing product looked like a short, colorful unicorn.

Item_Response: Dan was planing to make a robot that talks,moves,and helps people with their homework. His main focus was to get it done by the 19th of June,that way he could get it to the teacher for his project and it wont be late. That would give him at least two days to get it done. Before he went to bed, he wanted to make sure all his plans we secure. As the morning came, he stared working on the robot. He graded his bolts, screws, and tools. Finally he was done. He named his robot Nancy.                         He went to bed when all his work was finished. The only thing he didn't do was put the motor and speaker in. That night his mother went down stairs to put everything up, and take a quick look at the robot. She was amazed at what he had done. She put his motor and speaker on the robot and went up stairs for bed. That night he woke up and heard glass breaking and doors slamming. He went down stairs,and he saw his robot in full action. He ran up stairs and got his mother. He asked 'Why is my robot moving and talking!' 'All I did was put your stuff away, and put your motor and speaker next to your robot.' his mother said. 'Did you put it next to my robot or on it.' he said calmly. 'I put it on it.' his mother said getting out of bed and running down stairs. As they were trying to stop the robot, Dan realized that he put an on and off switch on the robot. 'Distract Nancy while I turn her off.' His mom was distracting Nancey. Dan turned her off. He didn't know that once he turned her off he would never be able to turn her on again.                                              As he was going to school, he was thinking of a good way to tell the teacher what happened. He walked into the classroom, and he was the only one without a robot. He went up to the teacher and said,'My robot broke it turned on,and broke everything on ascendent.' 'Well all I have left to do is give you a zero.' his teacher said. Dan walked away with disappointment. He got called up to the office. When he was there Mrs.Taylor handed him a huge thing that had a sheet over it. He was walking back to his class. When he got there he pulled the sheet off of the huge thing. It was the robot, Nancy. He went up to his teacher and showed him the robot. He told Dan to present it to the class. He was scared that it might not turn on and it might mess up like it did at his house. As he turned the switch to on excitement filled the room. It turned on! He continued on with presentation. Luckly he got a 100%.

Item_Response: THE NEVLINATOR,THE LIVING ROBOT                      As Dr.Nevlin worked on his new robot he had been thinking of how the robot will act and what its name will be so he started brainstorming. He started with how he acted. Dr. Nevlin was a young man and he was overall nice. So he thought that his robot would be kind and generous. So he began thinking of names and these are the name he came up with :       The terminator The inator The Nevlinator.           Then he finally figured it out His new robots name is going to be The Nevlinator. So he stood up from the table to finish his new and approved robot. As soon as he put his last touches on the robot the robot woke up.             'The Nevlinator at your services sir',the robot spoke out.            I might as well test it out and see its abilities, Nevlin thought.             ' Nevlinator will you go give me the screwdriver from at the top of the stair case?'Dr. Nevlin asked the robot.            'The Nevlinator at your services sir', The robot shouted.            Then as the robot climbed up the stairs grabbed the screwdriver off the stair case Nevlin was amazed. Then he thought, He climbs, talks, carries, what else should he be able to do?. So Nevlin thought that The Nevlinator could help him at work. Nevlin works at a store as big as Criegs cruisers. After a big day of work Nevlin put The Nevlinator to bed, tucked him in then Nevlin went to sleep.            'UP, UP', The robot yelled as the alarm went off.            Nevlin woke up to a jumping and noisy robot. That's not gonna be a good day for him. So Nevlin went to the kitchen for a cup of coffee. When he walked in the kitchen he wanted to scream. The floor was covered in coffee. He turned to give the robot the stink eye but the robot was gone.             So instead he screamed 'let's go', The Nevlinator followed. They got in the car Nevlin in the drivers seat and the robot in the backseat ( for safety). As they pulled in the parking lot of Chuck 'e' cheese the robot saw Chuck, the mouse waving to people as they walked in the place.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        'What am I gonna do here?'asked the robot               'Help me!'yelled Nevlin.               They both got out the car and walked/rolled to the door as Chuck stared at the robot. The robot got scared and rolled back to the car. Then Nevlin thought of something and drove back home. They ran in the house and Nevlin turned The Nevlinator off and thought that this wasn't gonna work. Then Nevlin stopped making robots and stuck to working and getting paid.

Item_Response: 'Finally, my invention is done! My robot 520 is finally finished. 'I am gonna be famous! The one and only Mr. DingleHimor! Now lets see what it can do. Flying, check, walking, check, And lazers, check. Now go get me a soda robot 520!' 'Yes sir' the robot said. 'MMMM thats a good soda' he said while drinking his soda. 'Now go get me some pizza'. 'Ok' the robot said in a techy voice. 'May i have a slice' the robot murmmerd. 'No you are just some stupid robot who should follow my orders' he said while eating pizza. The robot then walked away and just stood there in silence.             'The morning is here' Mr. DingleHimor said while stretching. Then the robot wasnt in Mr. DingleHimors lab. He called out 'Robot 520 where are you!' Then he soon heard a loud BOOM! outside of his lab. Mr. DingleHimor soon went outside to see what what happening. Then there he saw robot 520 10 times the size he used to be! 'He must have got my size changer posion from my lab' he said to himself.            Mr. DingleHimor saw robot 520 destroying cars and buildings. He was a monster!            So Mr. DingleHimor went back into his lab and was crying like a little baby because he was so scared. But then he started to remember that he has a potion that can make you small, but for robot 520 it would make him his normal size because he was large already.            So he snatched the potion and ran straight outside of his lab. Then put his shoes on and sprinted outside to find robot 520. He soon found him in the middle of the street. Then he soon saw his friend Mason in his large hand and was squeezing him like a tomato. Mason was a professer like Mr. DingleHimor was, but Mason was a lot more nice then Mr. DingleHimor.            Then Mason called out ' Dingle!' that was his nickname for Mr. DingleHimor. ' Come help me!' 'OK!' he said. 'Now robot 520 no need to hurt him hes a nice guy' he said in a scared voice. 'Never! you called me a stupid robot!' the robot called out. 'I didnt meaan that, now just drink this and everything will be ok I promise I will treat you like my best friend, and Mason can come hang out with us to' as he called out. 'Ok just hand me the potion and i will drink it' he said while dropping Mason. As he drank it he began to shrink into his normal size and evrything was ok.            Then soon after that they all just had a great time and were all friends.

Item_Response: Robots Today               Scientists have discovered and made robots for many purposes, such as the Gemini-scout, Dante 2, Mr gower , and agribots. But these robots are not just chunks of metal. They are very realistic and have human and animal qualitys.           These robots help people when they cant get the job done. For example Dante 2, researches volcanoes when scientists cant. It collects information, and goes into volcanoes. Another good example is Mr gower. Mr Gower helps out in hospitals. It delivers medicine to nurses and doctors when patients are sick. It can go in to elevators and make turns to get around objects.        Thease are all great quality's of robots, but is it safe? Will robots take over everything ? Is the next generation going to be all about robots and will humans not have to do anything anymore? If we continue to find uses for robots will we have any work to do? In my opinion i think it is dumb for people to use robots to do everything for them. why cant people pick their own berries and fruit? is the whole world going to revolve around robots?

Item_Response: It all started at the science lab with the rookie scientists. They were sitting in their chairs ready to experiment with the new robot their boss had created. The robot was not meant to come alive. All he was meant to do was sit there and look good for the Museum of Science and Industry in Chicago, Illinois.             Okay, back to the story. So there were these rookie scientists who had no clue how to work with robots. They were just supposed to fix up the nooks and crannies in the robot's outside frame. Those were the directions from the head scientist, Lenny.             Lenny was the meanest guy you could ever meet. He was only about five feet tall with a beard taller than he was. He only had one tooth but he was the best living scientist. He was in the newspaper even in Djibouti.             The rookie scientists had no idea what to do with this robot so........ they started playing with it. They laughed because they were actually having fun. They pretended that the robot was alive. They pretended that the robot was a puppet and they had a puppet show (he was the only character in the puppet show). And, they may or may not have pressed a few buttons.......           'What is all that racket,' Lenny asked as he scurried in to the lab.           'N-n-nothing sir,' said Billy (one of the scientists).           'Yep, absolutely nothing!' Exclaimed Bob (the other scientist)           'Alrighty then. You guys get your butts back to work, or I'll whip y'all,' Lenny remarked.          'YES SIR!!!!' Screamed Billy and Bob synchronized.          Lenny bobbled out of the room on his short and stubbly legs and walked and walked down the pin strait hallway until his shadow vanished.          Billy and Bob started to close up when they heard a strange noise coming from where the robot was sitting on the table.         'Did you hear that?' asked Billy.         'Well I sure did,' responded Bob         They shuffled over to the table but everything was just normal. They checked the electrical wires all over the robot. Everything was just fine. They checked the outside of the robot. Just fine. They even took the whole robot apart to check the 'brain' of the robot (like I mentioned before, these scientists are just rookies so they have no idea what to do). Everything was just fine.         'Well Billy, I don't see nothing wrong with this robot here, but I do know that we better get a move on. It's gettin' really late'        'I agree, lets get out of here'          They turned around and left the building safe and sound, and as quiet as a mouse. Well, not quite....           Not quite.           As soon as that door slammed shut behind Billy and Bob, everything started to get BAD.          Bad.        The robot that was sitting on the table right next to the window sprung up from the table and started, well, he kind of started dancing. He looked like he belonged in a boogie parlor. He did every possible dance move there was.... from the sprinkler to the worm. He was having a lot of fun. He danced and danced and danced until the morning when the rookie scientists came into work.....          Their mouths dropped open.          They went crazy when they saw the robot. Billy dropped to the floor and started crying because he knew he had done something wrong and that he was going to get in A LOT  of trouble. Bob just started dancing with the robot as if he didin't have a care in the world.          Just then, Lenny came running in....        'WHAT IN THE NAME OF SAM HILL ARE YOU WEIRDOS DOING!!!!!!!!!!'        Nobody said a word. They all just stood there in silence.       'WELL, IF NONE OF Y'ALL ARE GONNA SAY SOMETHING, I'M GONNA HAVE TO EXECUTE THIS ROBOT!!!' Screamed Lenny.              'No Lenny No! Please don't hurt him, he's our friend!' Said Bob.        'Ok, but whatever this thing is doing, it better be gettin' outta' here soon!' protested Lenny.        'That will be just fine' said Billy.       'Okay nerdheads, you may take him home,' said Lenny.         From that day on, Billy and Bob still have the Robot in their house doing normal people things. They all lived happily ever after.

Item_Response: Micheal Jackson the Robot version!           One soggy, misty night Franky a twelve-year old braniac was sitting in his room making a robot. Not just any robot but one that could sing and dance just like Micheal Jackson! 'My robot is complete!' Exclaimed Franky.       Now, what Franky planned to do with his robot that he named: Micheal Jackson II was to show him to Rock records one of the most famous record companies in the world at the time, and have Micheal Jackson II tour around the world dancing and singing for all the countries in the world to make money for Franky! 'Tomorrow we are heading L.A. to show you  to Rock records!' said Franky excitedly.       And before you knew it Franky snuck out of his house and was on a non-stop flight to L.A. with Micheal Jackson II! ' I am so excited!'shouted Micheal Jackson II as they boarded the plane.(i know what you are thinking, wouldn't it be kind of weird to see a robot in a airport? well everybody thought it was weird but Franky got permission from Rock records to come to L.A. to show them Micheal Jackson II)As soon as they got on the plane Franky emmediatly fell asleep because he knew that there was a long day ahead of them.       As soon as they got to L.A., they took the first cab they saw to Rock records. They arrived at Rock records at about 5 o'clock sharp. Both of the boys walked in and were amazed by how fancy everything was in there. Then the boys were greeted by a welcoming shout. 'HEY BOYS!! Are you Micheal Jackson II? asked the bald, fat short man that was staring straight at Micheal Jackson II. 'Why yes i am.' said Micheal Jackson II boldly. 'Well, show us what you got!' Said the fat man. Two seconds later, Micheal Jackson started killing the dance floor singing smooth criminal and doing the moonwalk! Then the fat man said with his fat rolls hanging out: 'Will you please work for me and travel around the world doing what you just showed me?' Then the room became quiet and Michael Jackson II said: 'Why not?' And in the blink of an eye Micheal Jackson II's career was under way. 'I'm so proud of him!' Whimpered Franky in the back of the room.       'Ok we are going to Djibouti in Africa for your first live performance and the show was sold out so you better impress them.' Said the fat man smiling. And before you could say: honey i shrunk the kids the first performance begun. The croud  loved Micheal Jackson II, but there was a problem  just as Micheal Jackson II was walking off stage  there was a big puddle and he sliped the old robot who had made it so far was broken.       So Franky was sent home crying and started building another robot. This robot's name was Elvis Presley II who could dance and sing just like Elvis Presley. And Before you knew it Elvis Presly II and Franky were on the first flight to L.A.                                                                To be continued.......

Item_Response: The Helping Robots                           Are you interested in the fascinating details of mechanical robots? In my opinion I just adore the idea of robots. They're so interesting to learn about.                    First off, the genetic engineering of robots contains a lot of parts. Parts that are so small that you can lose them without a doubt. After you put the parts together you have to make it work and turn on. Our future as we speak is getting harder and harder by the minute. We need to have some sort of machine that helps people through there day to day lives. Then that's when robots come in handy.                       If you think your job is challenging imagine thousands of robots all over the world doing the job that millions of people do! While people are relaxing and taking the day off robots are working as hard as they can trying to please you. We can even give them names so that we can make them fell better. The better you are to the robots the better they are to you. The perfect name for the robots would be the NSS national saving service. With every robot you have you get to chose their name like Tom,Kaylee,Mike, or any name you want.              If you want a search and rescue kind of robot the robot you'd want would be the Gemini-Scout. The Gemini-Scout is a remote-controlled robot that does search and rescue work in mines under the ground. The robot is less than two feet tall and has wheels. It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, and it can ever roll through water. The robot is small but it is strong. Gemini-Scout carries food, water, and other supplies. It can even drag hurt people to safety.             If you want a smarty pants robot then you would want Dante 2. Dante 2 is a robot with an interesting job it climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientists. Like a spider, this robot has eight legs. This helps it climb the steep walls of the volcano. It is also built to survive very high heat. When a volcano is too dangerous for      scientists to enter, Dante 2 goes instead.                   If you are interested in a robot that works in a hospital then Mr. Gower is the robot for you. Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hospitals, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. Mr. Gower looks like a small cabinet on wheels. The body of the robot is a stack of locked drawers that store medicine. Nurses and doctors can unlock the drawers when the medicine is needed.                 If you want a robot that picks fruit then an agribot is the robot for you. An Agribot is a robot that picks fruit. It might pick berries, grapes, oranges, or apples. Agribots are not yet widely used, but farmers are very interested in what these robots can do. Because picking a strawberry is different than picking an apple, agribots come in all shapes and sizes. Some have giant arms that are towed behind trucks.Others are able to move around on therie own. In Japan, there is a strawberry picking robot that can sense the color of the berries. This helps the robot know when each berry is ripe.

They had all kinds of things everywhere on the ground, on chairs , and on rails.  Becky asked them 'Excuse me but what are you guys doing?' One of the workers told her 'We are adding new things to the museum and today will be the grand opening.' Becky was really pumped up. Maybe two and a half hours had past when Becky saw a big crowd of people.  Becky hurried over to see what was going on. then she saw a big short man in a white suit with a microphone.  Becky new it was time for the grand opening. The man said 'Welcome everyone to our grand opening of  SKY HIGH!' Everyone was totally excited.  As soon as the curtains went up everyone went in with such excitement. Becky went on in and started seeing all these fabulous items in all different sizes and colors.  Becky went for walk inside to see what she could find. She probably walked half way through went she saw the most marvelous object that caught her attention. It was Steve Jones as a model , he was Americas best sky diver, he was Beckys hero. Becky asked 'How did you guys make him like that? And they told her 'He is a robot , but don't worry he all he does is light up and says his famous catch phrase once in a while.' That totally surprised Becky , but she was okay with that.  Becky was getting hungry so she decided to get some food.  She went to the McDonald that was inside the museum. All of sudden Steve Jones started to move. Becky didn't know what to do , there were a lot of thoughts going on in Beckys mind.  Becky started to climb up the rail so she can help Steve Jones get out of the rail and on the stand he was standing on. Steve Jones thanked Becky for letting him out. Becky told Steve ' No problem.' Becky had second thoughts of letting him out. Becky told Steve 'Okay Steve listen here , you are a robot so that means that I am in charge not you , okay?' 'Okay.' Said Steve Jones. Becky took Steve Jones to the gift shop to buy some things that will hide all the gadgets , screws , and queismos that were on Steve Jones.  Steve Jones didn't like that idea so he dug his heels in the ground so that he would not be able to move. Item_Response: In the Diamond Miners Mining company, there was an employee named Bill. Bill was just a miner like the others, but Bill had a robot arm. Bills robot arm got him the nickname Cyber. Cyber was mining in the Marcelline Mines, a mine rumored to have diamonds and rubies in it's depths, and got a call from the head of the Diamond Miners Mining Company, Mr. Gremlin.'Cyber,' Mr. Gremlin said,'I have a proposal for you and I need you down here quickly.' So Cyber went quickly to the Diamond Miners building and found Mr. Gremlin's office. 'Sit down Cyber,' Mr. Gremlin said, 'I was wondering if you wanted to have a promotion.' Cyber replied,' Yes please sir, but what is this promotion?' Mr. Gremlin stared out the tall glass window of his office. 'We need you to deep into Turnover Mines.'               'The Turnover Mines!' Cyber exclaimed, Those mines are the most fragile mines in the world!' Mr. Gremlin sighed, 'I know, but we need a group of people to go into the mines to search for gold to fund the company.' Cyber thought for a moment and replied, 'Whats in it for me?' Mr. Gremlin was quick to reply, 'Five percent of the treasure you find is yours.' 'I'm in.' Cyber said, and then Cyber left the office to go home and rest for his big day tomorrow.                  The next day Cyber went to the Turnover mines with ten other miners. Mr. Gremlin wished them good luck and they went down deep into the mines. On there way down, they saw a rusty Gemini Scout 1.9. Two of the miners were looking at it when it sprung to life. Unprepared, the two miners jumped backward, knocking over a large boulder. 'No!' Cyber and the other miners exclaimed as the boulders crushed the two miners an blocked their way back.                 The remaining miners sat in a circle wondering what to do when they heard a small electrical hum. The Gemini Scout! The robot, everyone knew, had a built in radio that could be used to contact the outside! The Gemini Scout had also brought a rock tumbling down. Cyber quickly grabbed the Gemini Scout and ran deeper into the mines. Cyber ran until he couldn't run anymore. When he looked around he saw a miner collapsed on the floor. 'Are you okay?' Cyber asked. The miner didn't respond, he was dead. Cyber quickly turned on the radio said one word, 'Help.' The Gemini scout watched Cyber collapse. Cyber was still breathing, but unconscious. Cyber awoke suddenly and looked around. He was in a hospital. 'About time you woke up' Mr. Gremlin said,'good work.' Cyber looked at him in a confused look and Mr. Gremlin said, 'That Gemini Scout of yours not only brought you to safety, but brought up two million dollars worth of gold. Cyber and his Gemini Scout were on the news and newspapers for three months. Cyber still got promoted and went into dangerous mines. Cyber always brought that Gemini Scout with him for the rest of his life.

Item_Response: The Awakening   By Emily Ritchie   Introduction      Meet Kate she is a Finder. Her job is to hunt lost things, dead things, or broken things. Her world will change after she finds something she thought she would never find.   The Meeting      I was running out of time when I here something behind me. I turned to see Kate standing behind me.      'Hi, you're late.'      ' I know. Had 'too' much homework.'      ' Sorry, let's go.'      We ran until we met up with the other Finders.We turned a corner and there he was standing there with a dead rat. Luke turned and threw the rat to Kate, his sister, who filed it  as killed in action.       ' You girls are just on time.'       'Yay us' yelled Kate.       ' Where is everyone else?' I asked.       ' On the mission we put them on, why?'       ' Help!'       ' Who was that?'     ' Not me.' yelled Kate. We looked around, but couldn't find anybody all we found was a robot that s been dead for so long I can't remember how long ago it died all I remember is that was my first mission, but now I'm the going to be the next leader.      The Awakening        At my house I heard a howl and thought it was my dog, but then I remembered my dog was at the groomers. I look around my room where I was finishing my homework, then I looked in the kitchen, and heard the howl again and turned to the door. There it was again. I look through the crack  in the door. There was Kate and Luke. I opened the door and automatically asked what was wrong. The said that Peri, my sister, was intured. This was her fist mission I knew I shouldn't of assigned such a hard mission for he rshe's only 10.         ' She's around back. She's the one making the howling noises.'         ' Thanks.'                      Help!          Peri and I get to the meeting on time in our teleporter.Kate runs up and says that Peri's first mission was success. She said that without Peri getting hurt someone else would of died. I looed at Peri and gave her a thumbs up. Kate also told me they had found a lifelike robot of me. 'Emily it even feels human. Are you sure you don't have a twin?' I shook my head and looked at hte robot. I poked it and it said 'Who's there?' Kate says ' Oh it can't be not you.' 'What ' I say.' you are the one who saves robots you're the seeker.'says Kate.                              Look Out !' Wow' I said,'That can't be true.I mean I'm just Emily not a Seeker, Emily.' 'Then explain how you just woke up that robot.' says Kate.                                 Goodnight Forever?   'I ran away from sme man that just tried to shoot me with a crossbow tell me whats happening?' I said  in a scared voice.' Oh no. Charlie knows. He will try to kill you every chance he gets. For now just stay in the headquaters.' Later that night I snuck out of haedquaters and am now dead.

Item_Response: Humans and Chris       In the spring of the year of 2396 A.D. on an uncharted planet, a science experiment has gone dreadfully wrong and no one civilian will risk taking chances with the destruction of this disaster. All the universe is in jeopardy, in jeopardy of a robot named Tootles. Who will be the valiant hero of all and all within?       It all started one day when a young boy of the age of twelve went to school. Chris disliked school and often skipped class or made lame excuses about illness. But today was different, his mom made him attend school and he couldn't come up with any severe, hospital worthy disease. Chris picked up his worn tattered book bag and went to the bus stop, his mother keeping an eye on him. Finally when the bus arrived, Chris got on and sat as close to the back of the bus as he could.       They arrived at another stop and two large boys with sun glasses and 'gold' necklaces around their necks got on the bus and sat beside Chris. It was Harry and David, the meanest kids ever (at Chris's knowledge) to attend St. Carmichael's. Whenever Chris did go to school, these two would always pick on him. For some strange reason, for the rest of the bus rode, they didn't do anything rude or selfish to Chris.       Once they got to school and they disembarked the hunk of yellow metal, Harry and David put their arms around Chris and said,'Chris, we realized that we have been bullying you for a while now and we want to apologize. We also decided to make you our friend.' At this Chris was scared but thought about what they said, and decided that it would be OK. But this decision of Chris's was unintelligent for he hadn't developed a sense of sarcasm due to the large amount of school skipping he had done over the years. So when Chris agreed to what they said, David mentioned to Harry something Chris didn't hear. Harry said,' Sure David. Hey Chris, since you're our friend now, you need to go through a test that proves your worthiness of our friendship.' Again Chris thought and agreed to it. They picked him up, and carried him off to an unused janitors closet. They then tied him up and threw him on an overturned bucket. They both shouted in unison,'See ya lata' sucka',' shut the door and left! And then Chris thought,'Dang it!'       While Chris was insulting himself for being such a numskull, a huge hole suddenly opened in the floor. All of his bindings flew upward as he fell down in the bright tunnel. It went straight down. Chris was just falling, falling, falling, falling, and falling. The drop never ended. It might have been easily an hour before he slowed down a lot it seemed and the tunnel curved out to the side. A flap opened and he tumbled out of the tunnel, and onto the hard land before him.       Then there was a huge explosion in front of him, a rock disintegrated, then another, then another. No, he was just imagining, his hard fall made him woozy. Chris gathered his bearings and observed his surroundings. Flat dusty land stretched on forever it seemed. Sharp jagged rocks stuck out of the ground. In the distance there was a tall tower that seemed futuristic almost and so did the landscape. Nothing could have been to weird though, it was only the winter of 2396, or was it?       Immediately he made a plan to head to the tower, for that was the first sign of civilization. Hours later he arrived at the tower and before he entered, he heard a kind of wincing, he walked over and saw a creature with red liquid coming out of one of its ligaments. Chris reached his arm out to touch it and it was soft, like human flesh. Chris had just broken the number one rule of artificial intelligence robotic humans, DO NOT TOUCH HUMANS OR HUMAN BELONGINGS. Chris felt his code glitch up. The human was wounded, his body juices were low, according to his sensors. He assisted the human. Once the human was recovered fully, he pulled out what seemed to be a weapon of some sorts and hit Chris with it.       Everything went black, he couldn't see....hear....,'my world is gone,' he thought,'goodbye.'

He could design a robotic human and download his memory into the robot. from then on he would be called Luc-B.

Item_Response: I never really thought that a robot would come to life, but one day it actually happened. I was asleep on a Friday night until I heard a loud noise. It seemed to come from downstairs. When i got up and went down to check, I turned on the light and suddenly saw a robot in front of me! At first I got scared but then I thought it was really cool! Also, it started talking to me! I wasn't dreaming for sure. The robot and I sat down and talked about why and how he got to my house. He told me that he saw that the window was a little open so he opened it. I was still confused on why he came to my house. He explained that he came from a machine and that now he is like a real person, except he's a robot! This robot said he came to my house because it was the first house he saw with a window opened. He is able to do a lot of things that normal people can do. I named him Bob and now he lives with my family and I.

Item_Response: No one really knew how it happened. It all seemed sudden and strange. He was shocked but immediately convinced himself that he did it and took the rewards. What he doesn't know was that he had nothing to do with it. It was marvelous, oh so marvelous but... Not everyone was convinced. They ignored his praise and found more interesting things to do. At first it was a miracle, It walked, talked, could do everything s human could, it even had emotions. Some saw it great others were in fear. No one really learned how it happened, but it was quite strange.       It was his birthday, he was turning 10. his father wanted to but his mother said they couldn't afford it. They got him a broken one instead and told him 'Don't be sad know when you fix it you'll know how to make more!' That was a lie. He hated them for it. getting him junk but, found curiosity took him over. He started working on it his parents almost sad knowing that it was missing too many parts to ever work. The boy was able to read about them and found the parts he was missing, well make-shift versions anyway. He tried everyday, but with no luck. He even got his parents to help seeing how badly he wanted it to work. After 5 more days, he gave up. He was planning on throwing it away but when he tossed it in the trash, the unthinkable happened. A single bolt of lightning came down and hit the robot. The boy screamed and ran home in shock but, stopped himself when he heard a noise. As he tuned he saw. The robot was working! He was so startled, but how? did the shock of electricity start the battery? He had no idea but his parents came towards him thinking he got hit, only to find him crying in joy. It was named Tom for his deceased brother.       He was so happy and was even able to activate the voice. He told everyone and eventually the media found out. The next week front page was labeled: April 15th, 2257 Young boy Makes talking robot out of scrap that can talk. He was given an award for youngest inventor and never mentioned the lightning. Eventually The robot and him were on TV and they found that Tom had emotions. Tom was brought into a lab to be studied and they found the makeshift parts and cracked up. The boy had used the joints from toys he had to make the arms work. Tom was famous but then there 15 minutes of fame ended (not to say they were only talked about for 15 minutes, it was almost 7 months before people stopped caring about Tom, i meant 15 minutes in a figure of speech). Tom also could do a lot more than humans could like run faster, withstand colder and hotter temperature, and he had 26 more joints than humans so he easily moved plus he never got tired. Eventually Tom was Lost while being sent to see if Earth was finally safe for humankind to return too. The last thing he every was seen doing was Passing the moon and right as Earth came into view, They lost communication. Some say Tom just came out of range, some say someone didn't want to ever find out if we can return to Earth but mainly i believe, That Tom didn't want them to see what really happened to Earth, so he cut communications. Tom was lost forever and the boy once again, 11 now was without a friend.

Item_Response: The Robot That Came Alive                 Imagine, in the middle of the night you wake up due to this loud noise you hear coming from downstairs. You are scared of what it is but you are going to be surprised of what you are going to see.                      It all started on my 10th birthday, when I wanted a robot set so I could build it.             'Mom, can I open my presents!' I blurted out at three in the morning.            'Honey, it's three in the morning and we agreed that we would open your presents when everyone was up. Go back to bed until eight o'clock' my mother said.            'Fine' I said in a pouty way.   I had to go to bed for another five hours. I set my alarm clock and went back to my comfy bed.            'Beep, Beep, Beep' my alarm clock screamed in my ear. I hopped out of bed and ran downstairs. To my surprise, when I stopped at the end of the stairs, I saw bunch of presents and my whole family was standing there. I jumped for joy. I ran like lightning to my family and gave them all a hug, even my dogs. I slowly opened my presents one by one and I didn't get a robot until I saw the gigantic present. I opened the present and their was a robot kit. I was so happy I got the robot, I kissed everyone on the cheeck.             A few hours later, the robot was done. Then all I had to do was program it. The things that I programed it to do is:   Do my homework and chores Be compatible with my xbox To persuade my parents to get something for me Speak              I played with my robot all day, I even jumped on the trampoline with it. Then it was time for dinner and I ate with my family, including the robot. After that, we watched a mocie and had cake. By that time, I had to go to bed. I shut the robot off and went to bed.              'Bang, Bing, Smack' I heard dramatically downstairs. I ran downstairs with my eyes half clothes and I peaked around the corner. I saw the robot destroying the garage. The robot has gone rogue!!! I had to do something. Just then, my parents appeared behind me. I ran and dogded through the garage to the robot. Then, I opened the back plate on the robot and pulled out the batteries.             'I broke a sweat there' I said releived. My parents both laughed. Since the robot went rogue, I had to disable my favorite birthday present.                                                                THE END

Item_Response: The Robot in the Attic                   We lived in a village.We live in a big house with four rooms.I live with my mom Julie, my dad Mark, my big sister Clara, my little sister Mya.My mom and dad have a room to share with a bathroom, big bed, desk, and a tv.I sleep in a room with both of my sisters.we have a bathroom, desk, 1 bunkbed and a big bed for my big sister.I have to sleep on the bottom and my little sister sleeps on the top.I woke up this morning before anybody else.I made my bed and went to the kitchen.I opened the cabinet and screamed really loud.My family came down and they all said ''What's wrong Lea?''Well i opened the cabinet and i went to graba bowl and there was a robotic arm in there.My mom grabbed it and gave it to dad and whipered something in his ear and he just left.I was wondering why my dad and mom have been acting strange ever since we got this house.So i followed dad after they went back to bed.He was up in the attic putting something away ina box.When he turned around i ran to my room and got in the bed a pretended i was sleeping.After he got in the bed i got my sisters up and made them come look what was up there.When we got up there we saw a big box like thing with a blanket over it.My big sister walked over to it and pulled the blanket off.My little sister ran to her room and it was just Clara and me.When she pulled it off sure enough it wasn't a box, it was a robot.It looked really old but cool.My sister turned it on and the eyes turned yellow and it said ''Greetings.''Clara and i both ran to our rooms and got under the blanket.I dont ever think i have been that scared before.A little later in the day Clara and i went back up to see if it shut down, but sure enough it was still on.My dad and mom were at work so we were alone.The robot rolled to us and said '' May i assist you in any way?''Well let me tell you something, me and clara weren't gonna let that go by so my sister said ''Go get me a drink, orange juice please.'' Sure enough, 5 minutes later, he came back with orage juice and handed it to my sister, then said ''How can i assist you again?''I asked him to go get me a snack like crakers.He came back with my favorite crakers.''How did you know these are my favorite snacks?''He said my dad and mom told him what we like and everything.I was suprized.Why did my dad and mom not tell us we had a robot?When mom and dad got home and i told my little sister to not say anything about the robot to mom and dad.We hugged them and asked how was your day and all.When we were eating dinner my little sister asked ''Why is there a robot in the attic?''We all froze and mom said ''What do you mean a robot in the attic?''My sister just ran off to our room and started to play with her dolls.I said what all happened and stuff and they just sat there staring at me and my sister.My mom looked at my dad and said ''i think it is time to tell them the truth, they are old enough now.''I said ''Tell us what?'' My dad looked at us with his guilty look and said ''Girls, me and your mom haven't said anything about where i really worked.'' ''I worked at a Machine and Repair center and i built robots, well when i built my first one i didn't ship off i took it to my house, but after awhile i got bored with it so i sold it to a man named John Marcus.'' ''I got a lot of money and i didn't spend it on you girls, i spent it on a tv. i was very selfish with the money im sorry girls.''

Item_Response: JERO                        There once was a child that played with his toy robot which could not do anything special. One day the boy saw a shooting star. He wished is robot could come to life and do anything he wanted. The boy went to sleep and when he awoke he saw his robot playing his video games. The boy asked the robot his name and he said Jero. The boy asked Jero what he could and he said anything you want me to do.                 The boy took Jero to school. While at school the boy was being picked on by the school bully named Mark. The boy told Jero to help him so Jero beat up Mark very bad. After school the boy asked Jero if he could build him a super fast car. Jero said yes and so they started to build the car.  When they had finished building the car they drove it super fast over a ramp and went into outer space. While in outer space they traveled to the moon. they got out of the car and started to play a game. During the game a evil robot 4962-H attacked them.                  They hopped in their super fast car and took off. 4962-H chased Jero and the boy and started shooting rockets at them. Jero jumped into the back of the car and opened the window. 4962-H began to shoot missles at Jero. Jero turned his hand into a huge rocket robot destroyer. Jero shot a missle at 496-H and destroyed him. Jero flew the little boy back home on his jet pack/car.                   When they got back home they went to sleep. In the morning they looked outside and saw 4962-H destroying the city. They went outside to save people from getting killed. Then, all of the sudden 4962-H shot a missle and killed the little boy. Jero was fierce with rage and attacked 4962-H. 4962-H killed Jero by cutting his head off with a lava sword. 4962-H destroyedd the rest of the town killing everybody and when he was done made factories for building Bomb Robots to take over the rest of the planets.                  While 4962-H was destroying another planet millions of Jeros attacked and defeated him and his army. Earth and all the other planets were rebuilt after the war of Robot 4962-H was over.

Jakobe now has met his favorite basketball player and has fulfilled his dream.

Item_Response: One day there was a little boy named Robbie, his parents were always away on work trips. When his parents were away, his grandparents would come and watch him. The only thing was when ever his grandparents would come over, they would sleep. He never had anyone to play with, except his cat. He decided to watch TV, and later when he decided to turn it off, an advertisement popped up, for a build your own robot web-sight. When Robbie saw they web-sight right away he went to the computer and typed in the web-sight. When he got to the home page he clicked on 'build your own robot'. Robbie made his robot to be programed with the ability to play with him and cook. When Robbie was finished he typed in his address and clicked create.         About a week later Robbie got a package, so he ran up stairs to open it. When he opened it he saw the robot, but when he took it out it did not work. Robbie was very sad, he kept thinking to himself, 'why doesn't he work?'. It was getting late out, so Robbie grandparents sent him to bed. The next day he woke up by a big bang sound. He didn't know what it was, so he went downstairs to take a look. When he walked down the stairs, there he was making breakfast, Robbie's robot had came to life while Robbie was sleeping. The robot rolled on over to Robbie and gave him his favorite breakfast. Robbie was so happy he let out a little scream. When he did, his grandparents came right out of the bedroom, because they didn't know if he was hurt or not.         When the grandparents saw the robot had made breakfast they were happy, and were wonder what was going on and who the robot was. They didn't know anything because they were sleeping when Robbie ordered the robot. After breakfast Robbie and his robot went outside to play hockey. When Robbie's parents got home he told them all about how much fun he has been having with his new friend. His parents were so glad that Robbie found a friend to grow up and play with.

Item_Response: Roy              Charlie had been saving his money for the new robotic dog that everybody in his class had. Finally after three weeks of doing chores he earned $35.00 and the dog was exactly $30.00. Today was Sunday and his mom was taking him to the toy store and he was ready to go as soon as she woke up. He had breakfast ready to go for his mom and they were leaving within 10 minutes, Charlie could hardly contain his excitment.          When they got to the store Charlie ran to the doors and burst into the the robotic isle. There was 1 dog left and Charlie grabed it and ran to the cashier. He took out his money and he was ready to leave and almost forgot his change. As soon as he got in his car and was ready to leave he decided to name his new friend Roy.          The entire day Charlie spent playing with Roy. He played Outside, in his room and even in the kitchen. By the time it was bedtime Charlie was asleep in less than 5 minutes, but in the mourning Roy had changed.          Charlie felt something wet licking his face and suddenly woke up and realized it was Roy! Roy had become a normal dog and Charlie was so excited. his mom never let him get a dog but now his robotic dog was real! Sadly today Charlie had school and he couldn't let his parents see Roy they might get rid of him! Then Charlie remembered that his parents were working today and he could keep Roy in his room until he got home.         While Charlie had been thinking Roy had been running around his room barking and jumping.          Charlie's school day had seemed like it lasted forever and he couldn't wait to get home and see Roy. By the time he did get home he forgot that his dad was coming home early andsaw the front door open with his dad holding Roy. 'Oh... Dad you found Roy, please don't make me get rid of him I'll train him and take care of him I swear!' said Charlie. Charlies dad didn't understand what Charlie meamt by say that his toy came to life but he thought that it would be good for Charlie to have a pet, he said, ' Charlie don't worry me and your mother think your old enough to have a pet, so you con keep Roy. But only if you promise to take care of him okay.'          Charlie couldn't believe it and swore to always take care oof Roy, and new that they were going to have great  adventures.

Item_Response: 'Imagine a world where robots cater to you every wim. Well that world is finally here. With modern technology and an industrial revolution we can now make the robo-maid,' said a tv spokes person. I quickly turned up th volume to learn more. 'Now for a limited time offer you can get your robo-maid for 299.99.' I was heart broken 300 dollars was way more than i could ever save up. I knew my parents wouldent get me it and the odds of me winning the lottery were about the odds af super man eating kryptonite for breakfast. I Tonny Smith would never get that robot.    Later that year three days before my birthday i went to school and it was official i was the only one in the entire world who didnt wave a robo-maid. If only i knew what would happen next. The very next day there were reports of strange disaperances. The next Day it got even worse now not every body whas at school and nobody knew what happened to them. Then on the day of my birthday i went out side and the town seemed deserted. Nobody showwed up for my party either. Then when i unwrapped my moms present i knew what happened. The second i opened the box the robo-maid inside started to say 'terminate all humans.'I ran for it but my marents were to slow the robot shot a vaporizer ray and poof they were gone.         I have been running from those robots since then. As i  know it i am the last human on earth. I have been trying to fight them ever since. My effort will probably be in vain but if somehow i do manage to win i hope that somebody finds these notes i have compiled. If you are reading this please never make a robot or things might not turn out quite how you like them to.

Item_Response: The Robot the Lived       This was my final exam for my robot class in colege. All year we worked on a robot that could do various tasks like cooking, playing, and driving, and now we have our final results. I'm Grover who's so nurvous that he sweated through his fourth jacket. The reason I'm sweating like a dog is the winner recives a twenty-five thousand dollar award. That would be amazing for me. Why, because I'm broke, spending my time on this robot a little to much, and by a little i mean i don't have power anymore. But forget about that, right now I have to win this.       As I make my way to campus I see some of the other competators, Becky Sherly the one who spys on you through the bushes, Adam Wisenberg the guiness, And Carl, we don't know his last name, why because he's a crep and never tells anyone anyhting. we're not even sure his name is Carl. But anyways back to the robots. As I'm waiting for the judges to come around in class I notice the other robots have issues, Becky's has bolts flying every where, Adams has an oil spill, and Carls is a banana, how he got here I don't know. As they aproach mine I feel quite scared, what if mine breaks down, what if mine doesn't turn on, what if... No what if's, I lost power for this so it has to work. And I was right a 100% sucess. he drove acceptionaly well, made an amazing sufley, and can throw a football 83 yards, I feel confident. And i should've because I won, I get the prize, my power back, and I can take a shower again. Life is good. Untill I got home that is.       It was 11:30 PM when my life changed forever. There was a lightning storm and my robot was outside on accedent of course. Lighning sturck and my robot was making noises I never could have beleaved were posible, but I ignored good thing to it, it was my cat making the noise.       As my life felt great, I have my matsers now, I have twnety-five thousand dollars, and my robots alive. Wait, hold on a minute My robots alive! I don't beleave it he's making me eggs and bacon, with toast and milk. He says to me , '' Hi, my name is Phill, that stands for pyhsical, hybrid, industrial, lifeliving, robot.' I can't beleave my ears, a robot that had no programed speeches actualy talking like a person. '' Breakfest is ready sir' he said. I had no idea this was posible who knows what will happen. Phill said, '' Ready to drive to school sir?' ''I would be, but I don't have a car.' '' You do now.' Then in the drivewat he turned into a jet, who knows what will happen.       Well, here's what did hapen. I won several prizes, became the 5th richest man in the world, and had two great kids Philles and Glen Jr. But thats all for know anyways. See you next time, lets go Phill to the country club, away! Actually, we were never seen by anyone again, why you may ask, because they all wanted to ''borrow' Phill, can youy beleave people these days I mean gosh what next, They'll want to take him apart. They';; want to, 'Glen, I think thats enough ranting, don't you?' '' Yes I agree, lets go.'

Item_Response: I've got a question for you. Have you ever been so bored with no one to do anything with. Your parents are busy. Your friend won't answer the phone and you don't have a sibling to play with. What are you going to do? That's the thought that little Jake had. What am I going to do? He thought.           'MOM!' Jake yelled.           'WHAT!' she yelled back.           'I'm bored!'           She handed him a cardboard box and some markers. ' Use your imagination.'           He looked at the box like it was brussels sprouts. What am I supposed to do with this? He sat on his bed and glared at the box. He layed back and looked at the posters on his walls. He saw a picture Yosaine Bolt running. He saw Le'bron James dunking a basketball. Then he saw the rover on Mars. He studied the rover then looked at the box. He went into the kitchen and grabbed the scissors. He ripped the poster off the wall and put it on the floor to use at an example. Then he started cutting and coloring and cutting and coloring until he was finished.            The box was transformed into a cardboard robot. It had blue arms and green hands. It's body and head was bright red. It's big square cross-eyes were black. He had an antennae that was orange and a big 'J' on his chest.            'Jake 2' he smiled. Jake spent the whole afternoon playing with Jake 2. When dinner rolled around, Jake brought Jake 2 to the dinner table. They played until bedtime. Jake got a pillow and a blanket from the hall closet an tucked Jake 2 in. Then he climbed in bed himself.            'Goodnight.'            The next morning Jake woke to a beeping sound. He opened his eyes to see a tray with scrambled eggs, toast, butter, juice, an orange slice and 3 slices of bacon laying next to him. He smiled.            'Thanks Mom!' he yelled.            'For what?'            That's when he noticed that Jake 2 wasn't under the covers where he left him last night. He got worried. Had Mom thrown him away? Then he screamed. Not a scream that you might hear coming out of someone on a roller coaster, not a scream that you might hear when someone wins the lottery. This scream was a terrifying scream. It was a scream that sounded like feedback from a amplifier. This was a scream that hurt your ears.             Jake 2 was under the tray of food. Suddenly Jake noticed his little green hands under the tray. Jake lifted the tray and Jake 2's little body was alive. His eyes were adorable. They were big and black.             'Can I help you, Jake?' he beeped, 'Would you like to play?'             'Wow', Jake smiled, 'Yes, you can help me. I would like you to get me my laptop. And some chocolate chips. I will eat my breakfast while you read to me. Then, and only then, will we play.'             'Yay.' Jake 2 beeped, emotionless, 'What book would you like me to read to you?'             'How about One Foot, Two Foot, Red Foot, Blue Foot by Dr. Seuss.'             'I shall go get that for you, Master',  and he rolled out of the room.             'Master!' Jake whispered, 'Cool!'             After breakfast and reading Jake and Jake 2 finally played. They played until lunch. Mom came in and saw that Jake 2 was alive.             'Aaaaaaaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!' she screamed, 'How.......what......JAKE!' she was baffled.           'It's okay, Mom. He's only alive.' Jake acted like it was the most normal thing on the planet.             'No! It is not 'okay'! This is a very impossible thing! I'm calling the police department! Or whoever will take this....thing..... away!' she stormed out of the room.             'When Mom is set on something, she won't give up. It's no use trying to stop her,' Jake thought to himself.             'I guess this is it, buddy.' Jake cried, hugging the metal bot.             When the department came to take Jake 2 away, Jake clung every limb to the robot.             'No! I won't let you take him!'             Mom pried Jake off and embraced him in a lock-hug, so he couldn't run for the bot.             'This is for your own good. This was not a normal event, what happened today. It'll be okay later.'             'No! It won't! He was my best friend and you called the police on us!' Jake screamed. He ran inside sobbing.             Mom sighed, 'Let me have him', she said.              'But Mrs. Carigon, we can't let you just have him. He could be greatly used in studies and saving lives.'              'Let me have him', Mom sneered, giving the police officer a deadly look.              After a few seconds of the 'death look', the police officer said, 'Give him over.'              She brought him inside, looked at those big, black, rectangular eyes, and apologized.              'It's okay.' Jake 2 said.              Jake ran into the living room, 'You saved him! Thank you!' He grabbed Jake 2's metal hand and started dragging him back to his room.              'Ahh ahh ahh.' Mom said, moving her first finger from side to side, 'It's my turn to play with him.' She said.              'Ugh, fine.' Jake said shuffling back to his room.              'So, Jake 2, how are you with painting toe nails?' Mom asked Jake 2, escorting him into the kitchen.              Jake heard this and smiled.

Item_Response: Alive       by Jonathan Lee           The year was 3033. A scientist just finished his latest creation. It was a play-bot. He had built this   play-bot because, he didn't know if he was the last human on the planet after the meteorite the size of Mexico had hit Earth and wiped out almost all the living creatures. The play-bot was nearly finished but, the scientist   died before he could finish the play-bot he had named, Pixel.           The planet had not had any precipitation for a very long time, until suddenly in the year  5061, there was a big rain storm with thunder and lightning. It just so happened that the lightning had struck Pixel. It looked like   something was happening. Pixel's eyes were starting to glow bright green. He started to move his limbs. He got up and looked around. 'Where am I? ', he thought to himself. He scanned his surroundings. 'No plant or animal life found.' , his sub computer, H.A.L, told him.            He yelled as loud as he could, 'HELLO!... IS ANYBODY THERE! ' Of course nobody answered. After that,  the first thing he did was build himself a shelter out of the debris that the meteorite made so he wouldn't   rust. 'As soon as this storm is over, I'll go search for living creatures.            A couple of days later, the storm had stopped. Pixel noticed this right away as eager as he was to get out of his little shack. He went outside and activated his flight mechanisms. He flew away towards the west. He soon found himself over the Pacific ocean and at the islands of Hawaii. He landed on the sub-island of Maui. He scanned for any living organisms. 'Living organismis found sir.' , H.A.L said. 'Identify them.'

Item_Response: Once there was a kid named,Jonathan,who always wanted to build a robot. Then, he started getting tools and things that he could use to build a robot. He asked his father if he could help him,but his father had to work and his mom had to take care of his little sister. Jonathan went to his room got the stuff he had gotten from his garage.He was working on it and he thought it was going pretty well, then he checked his watch and saw that it was already 11:30.He freaked out and said,'Its late I should be in bed!' Jonathan then went to bed.                    The next morning, Jonathan woke up. He looked tired;he went downstairs and ate breakfeast. Jonathan went to school while his mother was watching his little sister. After school, Jonathan went home and went straight to his room. Once he got to his room, he was working on the robot.Then, he finished. He tried to turn it on so it could work,but it didn't turn on. Jonathan said,'Man I give up! I can never build anything!' He started to do his homework, Jonathan checked his watch,it late again! this time it wasn't 11:30 P.M, it was  12:00 P.M.                    Jonathan went downstairs, he told his mom he didn't feel like eating today either. She asked,'Why?' He just left to school without telling is mother about the robot. He came back from school, did his homework,and then ate dinner. Jonathan thought it would be good for him if he went outside. While he was outside he told himself,'Playing outside is a good idea.' He checked his watch it was already 8:30 P.M. He went upstairs went to bed and wished that his robot worked because he missed it.                      'Today is Saturday.', Jonathan said with a sigh of relief. Jonathan checked on his robot and turned it on. It was walking he was so happy he told his dad, mom, and sister. They congradulated him and they spent the whole day playing with it.

Item_Response: Khrystianna Edwards                                           5-23-2013   The Special One                        Sally was a very bored and dull girl. She thought she had nothing to do with her life. She had no friends and would sit by herself at school. She never wanted to do anything. Once she did one thing she wanted to stop and change the activity.                               One day when Sally came home she saw a mysterious package in her room with her name on it.                               ' What is this? It has my name on it, but I dont want to open it. Well I have nothing else to do.' Sally said as she tiredly walked over to the package.                     When Sally opened it a human shaped figure pushed its way out the top of the box.Sally started to scream as she was frightened.                     'My gosh i have been in that box forever!' The human like figure said in robot language while Sally was screaming.                      'Who are you and what are you doing in my room?'                      ' I am a robot and my name is Tundra.' Tundra said as she made her way out of the box.                     As Tundra gazed around the room, Sally was on her bed slightly underneath a pillow. Tundra seemed nice to Sally after a couple of minutes so Sally asked her alot of questions.  Tundra ansered all of her questions and they very soon became good friends.                     Two months later Tundra and Sally were doing everything together. Playing sports, exploring caves, driving to places in the area, and even doing farm work with eachother. The activities they did seemed like it went on forever.                    Everybody in town knew about Tndra. She was one of the nicest person of all. Even scientist knew about her, but a new scientist planned to steal Tundra away from Sally.                    Dr. Smith was the new scientist in the lab. He had recently read about Tundra on the front cover of the news paper.                    ' Thats quite a robot we got in town,'Dr. smith thought aloud,'I must get it.'                    On a beautiful Tuesday afternoon the two friends were playing baseball outside. Dr. Smith was driving by, examining the robot. He took notes and pictures. He finally parked his car and headed out for the robot and the girl. He asked questions, but Tundra was unsure so they decided to go inside.                    'Sally, may i speak to you please?' Dr. smith asked                    'Yes?' Sally said as she went back over to him.                     Dr. Smith bribed Sally with money for the robot, but she said it was her best friend and no amount of money can replace her. So the scientist understood and drove back to the lab.                    In the lab, Dr. Smith called court and negotiated about why a young girl as Sally shouldn't need a professional robot like Tundra.                   'She could be very useful here in the lab.' Dr.smith said                    The court agreed for the lab to take the robot. Dr. Smith planned to take the robot sooner than later.                       The very next day Dr. Smith went to the court, got a signed paper saying he can take the robot. He drove to Sally's house and showed her parents the signed paper.                    ' Sally!' Her dad yelled upstairs,' the Scientist are here to take Tundra.'                    The next couple of minutes were the worst for Sally. Her best friend was just tooken out of her life. How could she go on? The good news is that she did.                    Sally had later accomplished many things that Tundra tought her and she became a scientist . she went to the same lab Tundra was taken to and the two of the lived the rest of their happy lives together.                                          THE END

Suddenly it started talking to me.At first i was scared because I've never seen anything like it before.He said,'I AM BOB,I HAVE COME FROM THE FUTURE TO SAVE YOU.'   Too scared to say anything,I nodded my head.I took him to my room,not letting my parents notice him.As soon as he entered my room,he transformed into a human.He had blue eyes,fair skin,and brown hair lying on his forehead.He was the cutest 'human' I'd  ever seen.As a human,his name was Justin.          I told 'Justin' to play outside with me,and he did.He transformed into many things like:unicorn,penguin,butterfly,a hippo,ect.After that amazing week he told me he had to leave Plant Earth and go back to his plant,Planet Robotomy.He transformed back to his robot self and told me his good-byes.Then he left me all alone in my cold,dark room.          Then,i told my  mom what had happened and she didnt beleive me so she sent me to the doctor's and the doctors didnt believe me either.After nothing worked out,she sent me to a mental asylum that was around the corner.I couldn't stand it so Bob came back to Earth to same me from everyone.He met my mom,and my mom fainted because she didnt believe her own eyes.But,long story short we all became friends and lived happily ever after.                                                                 The End
